10;31-11,1</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GUTHOMA KUUMA MARUA MA MUTHERU PAUL KURI ANDU AKORINTHO MARIA MA MBERE </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ariu a ithe witu, tondu ucio-ri riria mukuria kana riria mukunyua , </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ona kana undu ungi o uriku uria mweka ri ,</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ikagai maundu mothe mukiendaga, kugocithia Ngai namo . </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tigagai gwika undu ungihingicithia ayahundi,</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kana ayunani, ona kana kanitha wa Ngai,o ta uria nii na nii </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ngeragia gukenia andu othe na maundu mothe,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>itegwicariria undu wa kwiguna nii mwene, tiga o uria </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ungiguna andu aria aingi, ni getha mahonoke</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>inyui tuikai a kwigerekania na nii , o ta</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>uria nii na nii ndiigerekanagia na Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kiugo kia mwathani. (NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>RWIMBO RWA ALLELUYA</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mwathani ekuuga atiri; andu aria agima matibataragio </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ni muthondekani; nii njukite gwita andu aria ehia. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GITHOMO KIA INJIIRI 
Mariko 1;40-45</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE MARIKO</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hindi io, mundu wamukorire waruarite mangu ; </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agiuka akimuthaitha , agituriria Yesu ndu na akimwira atiri;</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ungienda-ri wahota kuhonia there. Nake agikiringwo ni tha </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agitamburukia guoko , akimuhutia akimwira atiri;</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ningwenda therio. Na kahinda o kau agithiruo ni mangu; agithera .</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake akimukania na hinya agicoka o hindi iyo akimwira oime </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ningi akimwira atiri: menya ukera mundu na withiire,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ukeyonanie kwi muthinjiri Ngai, na arute indo cia uguo atherio,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o iria Musa athanire ituike kimenyithia kuri andu.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>no we agithiira akirika kuumbura muno na kumemerekia uhoro ucio,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Yesu agikiremwo ni gucoka gutonya ituura thi-ini akionagwo ni andu, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agaikaraga o kuria gutaari micii,kuria gutaathiagwo </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nao andu makamukora kuo moimite o kundu guothe. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
