Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>WIMENYEREREI mütigekage ciiko cianyu iria njega </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbere ya andū, ni getha muonagwo nio: ni gūkorūo, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mweka ūguo, mūtiri na ngatho mūkona hari Ithe wanyu wi igūrü.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ūndū ūcio, riria ügwika ciiko cia tha, tiga kūhuhithia coro</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbere yaku, o ta ūria hinga ciikaga thunagogi-ini, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na njira-ini, ni getha ikumagio ni andū. Ngūmwira atiri na ma, ati, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>niirikitie kūgwata mücara wacio. Nowe-ri, riria ūgwika ciiko cia tha, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndūkamenyithie o na guoko gwaku kwa ümotho ũria guoko gwaku </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa ūrio gūgwika: ni getha citko ciaku cia tha ituike cia hitho-ini : </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Thoguo ůria wonaga hitho-ini niagakūhe ngatho.</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na hindi iria mūkūhoya, mūtigatuike ta hinga;</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondü cio nīciendaga kūhoya irūgamite thunagogi-ini </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na magomano-ini ma njira, 
ni getha cionagwo ni andū. </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngümwira atiri na ma, ati, niikitie kūgwata mūcara wacio. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No hindi iria ūkūhoya, tonya nyůmba yaku thii-ini, na warīkia gwitiiriria, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ühoe Thoguo ûria wi hitho-ini, nake Thoguo ūria wi hitho-ini niagakūhe ngatho.</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ningi riria mūkuihinga kūria irio, mütigatukie </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mothiù, ta hinga: tondū cio nitukagia mothiū, </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha cionagwo ni andū ati nīciihingite küria irio. </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngūmwira atīri na ma, atī, niirikitie kügwata mücara wacio.  </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nowe-ri, riria ükwihinga küria irio, wihake maguta mūtwe, </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na withambe ni getha ndūkae kuonwo ni andũ </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ati niwihingite kūria irio, no wonuo ni Thoguo uria wi hitho-ini</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake Thoguo uria wonaga hitho-ini niagukuhe ngatho</s></f>"},{ID:92,
