gwīkaga o maūndũ ma ūhoti! </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ gūkua-rī, ndigūkua, nī gūtūūra 
ngūtūra muoyo,ng'anage </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mawīko ma Mwathani. Kūherithia, Mwathani nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aherithītie o ma,
no ndandekereirie ngue.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Wee Ngai, nĩ tütaranītie magegania ma rwendo rwaku.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ihiga riria rīaregirūo nî aaki nĩrio 
rītuikite o riria inene ria koine. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ündū ücio umīte kwĩ Mwathani, 
na nī ūgūtūgegia tūkīwona. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mūthenya ūyũ nĩ Mwathani ūtūmīte ūgīe: nĩ tūcanjamūkei tūkīūkenagīra.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Wee Ngai, nĩ tütaranītie magegania ma rwendo rwaku.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOM0 KĨA IGĪRİ 
1 Johana 5:1-6. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA MARŪA MA MŪTHURE
JOHANA MARĪA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariû a Ithe witū, mūndũ o wothe ūrĩa wĩtikītie ati Yesu nīwe Kristū, nĩ aciarītwo nĩ Ngai; </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mũndū o wothe wendete mūciari, 
endete ürīa ūciarītwo nīwe o nake. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ūndū ürīa tũmenyaga naguo atī nī twendete ciana cia Ngai nĩ ūyū:</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twakorūo twendete Ngai, na tũgekaga maathani make. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu kwenda Ngai nĩ atīrī, nĩ tũmenyagīrīre maathani make; </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo maathani make matiri thĩna. Nĩ gūkorūo kĩrīa gīothe gīciarītwo ni </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai ni gītoragia ühoro wa gūkū thĩ. 
naguo ūtoria ūrīa ūtoretie ūhoro wa </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩ nĩ atiriri, nī gwītikia gwitù. Ūrĩa ûtoragia ūhoro wa gükū thĩ nũ, tiga </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūrīa wītīkītie atī Yesu nīwe Mūriū wa Ngai? We nīwe wokire ūhoro-inī wa </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maaī na thakame, o we Yesu Kristū; ndokīire ūhoro-inĩ wa maai moiki, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>okīire ühoro-inī wa maai na thakame. No Muoyo nīwe mũira, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gūtuika Muoyo nīwe ūhoro-ūrīa wa ma.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Ciugo cia Mwathani.
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RWÍMB0 RWA INJIRI 
Johana 20:29 </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya. Wee, 
Thomas, tondū nĩ ünyonete, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nikīo witikītia; gūkena-rī, ni aria matonete, na no metikītie. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KĨA INJIRI 
Johana 20: 19-31</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA M</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>Ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>THURE JOHANA:</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Müthenya o ūcio wa kwambiriria kiumia, gükinyīte hwai-ini, na mirango </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikahingwo kūu arutwo maari, niundu wa gwitigira Ayahudi Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agiuka akirugama gatagati-ini kao akimera atiri: Giai na thayů. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na aarīkia kuuga ůguo, akimonia hi ciake o na mbaru. Nao arutwo </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mona Mwathani magikena. Yesu agikimera ringi atiri: Giai na thayū; </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ûria Ithe andekirie, noguo ndamurekia inyui. Na arikia kuuga </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uguo akimaheherera akimera: Iyukiai Muoyo Mutheru: andu aria </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe mwarekera mehia mao nimarekeruo. Na aria othe mwarega </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kurekera mehia mao maguikara matarekeirwo. </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩrĩ, ũmwe wa arīa ikūmi na erĩ, na nĩ Thomas üria wetagwo Didimo, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio ndaari nao na hĩndī io Yesu okire. Tondũ ūcio arutwo aria angi </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makimwira: Nĩ tuonete Mwathani. 
Nake akīmera atīrī: Itonete irema cia </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>micumari hi ciake, na ngatonyia kiara 
giakwa irema-inī icio cia mĩcumarī na </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngatonyia guoko gwakwa mbaru-ini 
ciake-i, ndingitikia o na hanini. </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi matukū maathira mana, arutwo ake maarī kuo ringi kùu nyümba thiini, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maari na Thomas. Nake Yesu agīiüka, mirango iri mihinge, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīrūgama gatagati-ini, akiuga: Giai na thayū. Agicoka akīira Thomas atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rehe kiara gīaku haha, ůrore hi ciakwa; na ùrehe guoko gwaku, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūtonyie mbaru-inī ciakwa; na ūtige gūtuika wa kūrega gwitikia, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ûtuike wa gwitikia. Thomas agicokia akīmwira atīrī: Mwathani wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai wakwa! Nake Yesu akimwira atiri:
Wee tondũ nĩ ünyonete, nīkīo wītikītia, </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūkena-rī nī arīa matonete, nao no metikitie. Gwi ciama ingí nyingi Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ekire arutwo me ho, itaandikirwo mbuku-ini: no icio ciandikirwo</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciandīkitwo nĩ getha mwitikie atī Yesu nĩwe Kristů, Mũrũ wa Ngai, na tondu </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa gwitikia mügie na muoyo na ündū wa rĩitwa rīake.</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Injiri theru ya Mwathani. 
(NI TWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
