Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmaigue makĩaria na mĩarĩrie iitũ, o mũndũ na mwarĩrie wake wa kũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aaciarĩirũo? Aparti na Amedi na Aelamiti, o na arĩa matũũraga </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mesopotamia, na Judea na Kapadocia, na Ponto na Asia, na Frijia na Panfilia, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
