Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo waku.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ ũkahitha ũthiũ, cio igagĩcanjama; ũcokagĩra mĩheehũ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
