kĩruru-inĩ kĩaguo nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hagatũũragwo nĩ nyamũ ciothe iria irĩ 
mathagu cia mĩthemba yothe;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kũu kĩĩruru-inĩ kĩa honge ciaguo-rĩ, 
nĩkuo igatũũra.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nayo mĩtĩ yothe ya werũ nĩ ĩkamenya atĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani hometie mũtĩ ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũraihu na igũrũ mũno, ngatũũgĩria mũtĩ ũrĩa mũnyinyi mũno; ningĩ nĩ niĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyũmĩtie mũtĩ ũrĩa mũruru, naguo mũtĩ ũrĩa mũũmũ ngatũma ũrure </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wega; niĩ Mwathani nĩ niĩ njarĩtie ũhoro ũcio na ngawĩka.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani 
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                        Thaburi 92:1-2;12-13;14-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Nĩ wega mũno gũcokagĩria Mwathani ngaatho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ wega mũno gũcokagĩria Mwathani ngaatho, o na gũkumia rĩĩtwa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩake na rũĩmbo, wee Wĩ Igũrũ-Mũno; nĩ wega kũrokaga </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuonania ũhoro wa ũtugi waku o rũcinĩ, na kuonanagia wĩhokeku waku o ũtukũ o ũtukũ.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA; Nĩ wega mũno gũcokagĩria Mwathani ngaatho</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũrĩa mũthingu we arĩhambaga ta mũkĩndũ, akũre o ta mũtarakwa wĩ kũrĩa Lebanoni. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Acio ahande nyũmba-inĩ ya Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ kũhamba </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩhambagĩra kũu nja-inĩ cia Ngai witũ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA; Nĩ wega mũno gũcokagĩria Mwathani ngaatho</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magatũũra maciaraga maciaro o na marĩ akũrũ; magatũũra maiyũire </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngogoyo, maikare marĩ o aruru; monanagĩrĩrie atĩ Mwathani nĩ mũrũngĩrĩru, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we ndũmba yakwa ya ihiga, thĩinĩ wake gũtarĩ kaũndũ ka wogogi</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA; Nĩ wega mũno gũcokagĩria Mwathani ngaatho</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRI
2 Akorintho 5:6-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ,  ũcio-rĩ, tũikaraga hingo ciothe twĩting’ũrĩtie, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũkĩmenyaga atĩ hĩndĩ ĩno tũtũũraga thĩinĩ  wa mwĩrĩ ta arĩ guo mũciĩ witũ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũikaraga tũtarĩ hamwe na Mwathani, nĩ gũkorũo mĩthiĩre-ĩni </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iitũ tũthiaga na ũhoro wa gwĩtĩkia, ti ũhoro wa kuona na maitho. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nguuga rĩngĩ atĩ tũtũũraga twĩting’ũrĩtie, na ũrĩa tũngĩenda </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩria nĩ kaba gũikara tũtarĩ thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ,
nĩguo tũtũũranie </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Mwathani ta arĩ kuo gwitũ.  Na tondũ ũcio ningĩ tũgeragia na kĩyo </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũtũma akenage nĩ ũndũ witũ, o na twaakorũo tũrĩ o gũkũ mĩĩrĩ-inĩ iitũ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana tũkoretwo tũthamĩte kuo. Tondũ-rĩ, no </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũhaka ithuothe tũkoneka ũrĩa tũtariĩ tũrĩ mbere ya gĩtĩ gĩa Kristũ kĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gĩa ituĩro, nĩ getha o mũndũ akaheo kĩrĩa aagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũheo nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa maũndũ marĩa aaneka arĩ na mwĩrĩ, makorũo marĩ mega kana marĩ moru.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani 
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Atũmwo 16:14</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. Wee Mwathani hingũra ngoro ciitũ, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ tũrĩ hunguraga ciugo cia Mwana waku. Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 4:26-34</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akiuga atĩrĩ: Ũthamaki wa Ngai ũtariĩ ta rĩ, ta mũndũ angĩikia </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbeũ tĩri-inĩ; na akomage agĩũkagĩra ũtukũ na mũthenya, nacio </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbeũ imere na ikũrage, atoĩ we ũrĩa ciĩkũragia. Thĩ ĩiciaragia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yo nyene; ĩkaamba kũmeria nguha, na thutha gũgoka igira, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na thutha ũcio igira thĩinĩ hakagĩa na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njiganu. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ irio cioma, o rĩmwe agĩciikia rũhiũ, tondũ hingo nĩ nginyu ya </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũgetha. Agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩ: Tũhaananie ũthamaki wa Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kĩ?, kana tũheane ũhoro waguo na ngerekano ĩrĩkũ? </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ta kahĩndĩ ga karatarĩ, ko kaahandwo tĩri-inĩ, o na gaakorũo ge </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kanini gũkĩra mbeũ ciothe irĩ thĩ, kaahandwo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gagakũra gagakĩria irio ciothe cia mũgũnda kũneneha, na gakaruta honge </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nene; nacio nyoni cia rĩera-inĩ ikahotaga kũraara kĩgunyĩ-inĩ gĩako.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ aamaheaga ũhoro na ngerekano nyingĩ ta icio, o ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mangĩhota kũũigua: na ndaamaaragĩria hatarĩ ngerekano:</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na arutwo ake mwene, acio nĩ aamataũragĩra maũndũ mothe 
rĩrĩa hatarĩ andũ angĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani 
(NI TWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU) </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA IMWE MWAKA B"},{Guid:"bElsar4A2kaSqx+anL3VCQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA SITA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Yeremia 23:1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Yeremia</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ole wao wachungaji, wanaowaacha kondoo wa malisho </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yangu kutawanyika na kupotea - asema Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiyo maana Bwana, Mungu wa 
Israeli, amesema hivi juu ya </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wachungaji wanaowalisha watu wa taifa langu: mmewatawanya </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuwasambaza kondoo wa kundi langu. Hamkuwaangalia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini sasa mimi nawaangalia ninyi  sababu ya matendo yenu maovu, asema </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana. Nami nitawakusanya kondoo wangu waliobaki, kutoka </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nchi zote nilikowasambaza.
Nitawarudisha katika malisho </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yao, hapo watazaa tena na kuongezeka. Nitaweka juu yao </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wachungaji wenye kuwalisha, nao hawataona tena woga </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hofu, wala hatapotea hata mmoja wao, asema Bwana. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, siku zitakuja -  asema Bwana- nitakapomwoteshea Daudi chipukizi </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>takatifu, mfalme atakayetawala na kutenda kwa hekima, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kufanya hukumu na haki katika nchi. Siku zake, Yuda ataokolewa, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Israeli atakaa salama, naye ataitwa jina hili: \"Bwana ndiye haki yetu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 23:1-3a, 3b-4, 5,6(K 1)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, Sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hunipumzisha katika malisho mabichi hunipeleka </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwenye maji matulivu; hunipatia nguvu. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huniongoza katika njia zilizo sawa
kwa ajili ya jina lake. Hata </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nijapopita katika bonde la giza, siogopi mabaya, kwani wewe upo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pamoja nami, gongo lako na fimbo yako vyanituliza. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waandaa meza mbele yangu,
machoni pa adui zangu;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umenipaka mafuta kichwani;
kikombe changu kinafurika. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kweli, wema na fadhili zitanifuata siku zote za maisha yangu;</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nitakaa nyumbani mwa Bwana kwa miaka mingi ijayo. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Bwana ndiye mchungaji wangu, sitapungukiwa na kitu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Waefeso 2:13-18</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Sasa kwa damu ya Kristo ninyi mliokuwa mbali tangu zamani </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mmeletwa karibu katika Kristo Yesu. Kwa maana yeye ni amani  yetu.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ameziunganisha jamii hizo mbili Wayahudi na Watu wa Mataifa  kuwa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>moja. Kwa kutoa mwili wake msalabani ameubomoa ukuta  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uliowatenganisha na kuwafanya adui.
Ameitangua sheria pamoja na amri </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zake na madai yake. Amefanya jamii hizo mbili kuwa  \"mtu mmoja mpya\" </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika nafsi yake. Hivyo ameleta amani.  Alizipatanisha jamii </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zote mbili na Mungu kuwa mwili mmoja kwa nguvu ya msalaba.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika nafsi yake ameumaliza uadui. Amekuja kuwahubiria amani </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi wa mbali na sisi wa karibu pia. Kwake,  sisi sote tumepata </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>njia ya kumkaribia Baba katika Roho mmoja.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Yohane 10:27</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.Aleluya. Kondoo wangu huisikia sauti yangu, asema </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana; nami nawajua, nao wanifuata. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Marko 6:30-34</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Mitume walikusanyika kwa Yesu na wakamweleza</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yote waliyofanya na waliyofundisha.
Akawaambia,  \"Njoni twende </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sehemu ya upweke mpate kupumzika kidogo.” Kwa maana watu </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliokuja na kutoka walikuwa wengi mno hata wasipate nafasi ya </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kula. Wakaondoka kwa chombo waende mahali pa ukiwa, wao peke yao.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu waliwaona wakiondoka, na wengi walitambua lengo lao. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakaenda hima kwa miguu toka miji yote, wakawatangulia </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kufika. Aliposhuka pwani, aliona umati mkubwa wa watu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawahurumia, kwa maana walikuwa kama kondoo wasio na </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mchungaji; akaanza kuwafundisha mambo mengi.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA SITA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"VgkQGyPr5k+DEQGcqmdCvQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA  
Mwanzo 9:8-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu alisema hivi na Nuhu na wanawe:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Mimi ninafunga agano langu nanyi, pia na vizazi vyenu baada yenu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tena na viumbe vyote vyenye uzima vilivyo pamoja nanyi: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndege, na wanyama wa kufugwa, wanyama wote wa mwitu walio pamoja nanyi, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>basi wote waliotoka katika safina, wanyama wote wa nchi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitaweka agano langu nanyi: hakuna kiumbe chenye mwili</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kitakachoangamizwa tena na gharika, wala </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hakutakuwa tena gharika ya kuiharibu nchi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu akasema: Hii ndiyo alama ya agano ninaloweka kati yangu </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mimi nanyi, na viumbe vyote vyenye uzima vilivyoko </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>pamoja nanyi, kwa vizazi vijavyo: nauweka upinde wangu wa mvua mawinguni, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao utakuwa alama ya agano kati yangu mimi na dunia. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitakapoleta mawingu juu ya nchi, na huo upinde 
utakapoonekana </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mawinguni, nitalikumbuka agano lililo kati yangu mimi nanyi, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na viumbe vyote vyenye uzima, yaani kila kilicho na mwili; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wala maji hayatakuwa tena gharika ya kuharibu kila kiumbe chenye mwili.\"</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana. (TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 				
Zaburi 25:4bc-5ab, 6-7bc, 8-9 (K. 4a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio; Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako; unijulishe mapito yako.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uniongoze katika uaminifu wako, unifundishe,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maana wewe ndiwe Mungu mwokozi wangu. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, ukumbuke huruma yako; na rehema zako,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maana ni za tangu milele. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Unikumbuke kwa kadiri ya upendo wako. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio; Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ni mwema, tena mwenye haki, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa hiyo huwajulisha wakosefu njia zake.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huwaongoza wanyenyekevu katika haki,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kuwafundisha njia yake. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
 1 Petro 3:18-22</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Petro</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wapendwa: Kristo alikufa mara moja kwa ajili ya dhambi. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwadilifu alikufa kwa ajili ya wakosefu, ili awapeleke kwa Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aliuawa katika mwili, akahuishwa katika roho. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hivyo alikwenda kuhubiri kwà roho zilizokaa kifungoni.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Zamani Nuhu alipounda safina, na Mungu alipongoja kwa subira, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>roho hizo zilikataa kusikiliza. Wachache tu, yaani wanane, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waliingia wakaokolewa katika maji. Maji hayo ni mfano wa ubatizo </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>unaowaokoa ninyi sasa. Ubatizo si kuondoa uchafu wa mwili, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>bali ni kumwomba Mungu tupate dhamiri njema </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa nguvu ya ufufuko wa Yesu Kristo. Naye amewaweka </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>malaika na wenye enzi na wenye nguvu chini ya mamlaka yake. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akaingia mbinguni. Yuko kuume kwa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KWANZA YA KWARESMA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"SVNPq2mWOkSVwRD9f49zjw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	    Jeremia 23:1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI JEREMIA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩ!, kaĩ arĩithi arĩa maninaga mbũri cia rũũru rũakwa o na magacihurunja marĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na haaro-ĩ! Ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.  Tondũ ũcio, Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai wa Israeli ekuuga ũũ ha ũhoro wa arĩithi acio marĩithagia andũ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akwa-rĩ: Nĩ kũhurunja mũhurunjĩte mbũri cia rũũru rũakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mũgacihahũra, na mũkaaga gũthiĩ gũcirora; atĩrĩ, nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngamũherithĩria ũũru o ro ũcio wa ciĩko cianyu; ũguo nĩguo Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ekuuga. Niĩ na niĩ nĩ ngacokereria mbũri iria itigarĩte cia rũũru rũakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciume mabũrũri mothe marĩa ndacitwarithirie, ndĩcicokie ciugũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciacio; nacio nĩ igaciara ciongerereke mũno.  Na niĩ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngaciigĩra arĩithi a gũcirĩithia; na itigacoka gwĩtigĩra o na rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana imakio, na hatirĩ o na ĩmwe yacio ĩkaagwo; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũguo nĩ guo Mwathani ekuuga.
Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matukũ nĩ magoka marĩa ngaarahũrĩra Davide mũndũ mũthingu </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgerekanĩtio na Thuuna ya mũtĩ,
na nĩwe ũgathamaka, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na thĩinĩ wa ũthamaki wake agaacĩre o 
kũgaacĩra; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ agatuanagĩra cira wega, na ekage maũndũ ma kĩhooto bũrũri ũcio.  </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukũ-inĩ make-rĩ, Juda nĩ akahonokio, nake Israeli atũũre egangarĩte; </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>narĩo rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa agetagwo nĩrĩo rĩrĩ, Mwathani ũthingu witũ.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                        Thaburi 23: 1-3a,3b-4;5;6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Mwathani, wee nĩwe ũkũndũara ũnene wa ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩwe mũrĩithi wakwa;  ndirĩ kĩndũ ingĩkĩaga. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Atũmaga njarahe cieni-inĩ iria ii nyeki nduru; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andĩithagia ngurumo ya maaĩ o marĩa me na 
ũhurũko. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ kũriũkia ariũkagia ngoro yakwa.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Mwathani, wee nĩwe ũkũndũara ũnene wa ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akandongoria na njĩra cia ũthingu nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩake.  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O na ingĩtuĩka ndĩrahungurĩra mũkuru wĩ nduma ta ya gĩkuũ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndirĩ ũgwati ingĩĩtigĩra, nĩ gũkorũo twĩ hamwe nawe;  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thiarĩ  waku na mũthĩgi, nĩcio igũtũma makũke.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Mwathani, wee nĩwe ũkũndũara ũnene wa ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũnjarĩire metha harĩa ndĩ, o ũthiũ-inĩ wa thũ ciakwa; </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũnjitĩrĩirie maguta mũtwe; gĩkombe gĩakwa nakĩo nĩ kĩembembaine.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:	Mwathani, wee nĩwe ũkũndũara ũnene wa ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukũ mothe ma muoyo wakwa, wega na ũtugi itirĩ hingo itarĩrũmanagĩrĩra </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na niĩ, na ngũtũũra nyũmba ya Mwathani matukũ matarĩ mũthia.   </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:	Mwathani, wee nĩwe ũkũndũara ũnene wa ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Aefeso 2:13-18</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, rĩu, thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu-rĩ, inyuĩ arĩa mwaraihĩrĩirie </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mũreharehetwo hakuhĩ nĩ ũndũ wa thakame ya Kristũ.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu nĩwe thayũ witũ, o we watũmire ithuĩ twarĩ erĩ tũtuĩke </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ro ũmwe, agĩgĩtharia rũhĩrĩgo rũrĩa rũatũhakanĩtie;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo ũthũ-rĩ, akĩũnina na ũndũ wa mwĩrĩ wake, naguo  ũguo nĩta </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuuga atĩ nĩ aaninire watho ũrĩa wa maathani marĩa maatuĩtwo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩgĩĩka ũguo nĩ getha ombe thĩinĩ wake mwene mũndũ ũmwe </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwerũ uumĩte harĩ acio erĩ, na amaciarithanie ũguo;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na ningĩ nĩ getha atũme matuĩke mwĩrĩ ũmwe, amaiguithanie na Ngai na ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa mũtharaba, tondũ wa ũrĩa aaninĩte ũthũ naguo.  Agĩgĩũka akĩhunjanĩria ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa thayũ, thayũ kũrĩ inyuĩ arĩa mwaraihĩrĩirie, 
o na thayũ kũrĩ arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maakuhĩrĩirie o nao, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ tondũ wake we ithuĩ a irũka icio cierĩ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twĩtĩkagĩrio tũkinye harĩ Ithe witũ, tũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Muoyo o ũmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI	
John 10,27</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya. Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Ng’ondu ciakwa-rĩ, nĩ ciiguaga </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgambo wakwa, na niĩ nĩ ndĩciũĩ, nacio ikanũmĩrĩra. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 6:30-34</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo arekio magĩcoka kũũngana kwĩ Yesu; na </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩmwĩra maũndũ mothe, o marĩa mekĩte, na marĩa maarutĩte andũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ũkai inyuĩ inyuiki kũrĩa gũtarĩ andũ, mũkahurũke hanini.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondũ andũ nĩ aingĩ mokaga magĩthiaga, nao makaaga hingo o </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ya kũrĩa irio. Magĩthiĩ na marikabu kũndũ gũtaarĩ andũ, o oiki. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao andũ makĩona magĩthiĩ, na aingĩ makĩmamenya, magĩtwarana </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuo na magũrũ mahanyũkĩte moimĩte  matũũra mothe makĩmahĩta. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akiuma marikabu akĩona kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ, agĩkĩiguĩra tha, tondũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maatariĩ ta mbũri ciagĩte mũrĩithi: agĩitĩka kũmaruta mohoro maingĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>    </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA ITHATHATU MWAKA B"},{Guid:"i93WAsYQIEyEJkVxyXIQdA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA	
I Samueli 3:310-10, 19</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha kwanza cha Samueli </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku Lile: Samueli alikuwa amelala 
katika hekalu la Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pale lilipokuwapo sanduku la Bwana. Bwana akaita: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Samueli, samueli,\" naye akaitikia, \"Mimi hapa!\" </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye akamwendea Eli kwa haraka akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mimi hapa, kwa kuwa uliniitao\" Eli akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Sikukuita, nenda ukalale.\" Akaenda kulala. Bwana akaita tena.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Samueli, Samueli!\" Naye akamwendea tena Eli, na kusema, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mimi hapa, kwa maana uliniita\" Naye akajibu, akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Sikukuita mwanangu, nenda ukalale.\" </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule Samueli alikuwa bado hajamfahamu Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na neno la Bwana lilikuwa bado halijafunuliwa kwake. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akamwita tena Samueli mara ya tatu. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo aliamka na kumwendea Eli akasema, \"Mimi hapa, kwa maana uliniita.\" </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndipo Eli akatambua ya kuwa Bwana ndiye aliyemwita kijana. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwambia Samueli, \"Nenda ukalale na utakapoitwa, utasema, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>'Nena Bwana kwa kuwa mtumishi wako anasikia.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>''Basi akaenda tena kulala mahali pake.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akaja, akasimama, na kuita kama awali: </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Samueli, Samueli\" Ndipo Samueli akaitikia, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nena Bwana kwa kuwa mtumishi wako anasikia.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\" Samueli akakua, na Bwana pamoja naye, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hakuacha neno lolote lianguke chini</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 40: 2	na 4ab,7-8a, 8b-9, 10 </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Tazama, nimekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nalimngojea Bwana kwa subira; akanielekea na kukisikia kilio changu, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akaweka wimbo mpya kinywani mwangu, sifa za Mungu wetu. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Tazama, nimekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako,ee Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hukupenda sadaka wala matoleo; ila masikio wazi kwa kutii; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hukutaka dhabihu za kuteketeza wala sadaka za dhambi; </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hapo nilisema, 
\"Mimi hapa, nimekuja.\" </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Tazama, nimekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Katika gombo la chuo nimeandikiwa amri zako. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Napenda kutimiza mapenzi yako, ee Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wangu, sheria yako imo moyoni mwangu!\" </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Tazama, nimekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ninatangaza habari za haki yako katika mkutano mkubwa; </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wala sikuzuia midomo yangu, ee Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Tazama, nimekuja kuyatimiza mapenzi yako, ee Bwana,
wewe wajua. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI 
I Wakorintho 6:13c—15a, 17-20 </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Mwili si kwa ajili ya anasa, bali ni kwa ajili ya Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Bwana ni kwa ajili ya mwili. Na Mungu aliyemfufua Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye atatufufua sisi pia kwa uwezo wake. Je, hamjui ya kuwa miili yenu</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni viungo vya Kristo? Lakini yeye anayeambatana na Bwana ni roho moja naye. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikimbieni zinaa. Makosa yote ayatendayo mwanadamu </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yapo nje ya mwili, ila mwenye kuzini huukosea mwili wake wenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Au hamjui ya kuwa miili yenu 
ni hekalu la Roho Mtakatifu </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliye ndani yenu? Mwili mmepewa na Mungu! Kwa hiyo si mali yenu. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana mmenunuliwa kwa bei kubwa. Basi, mtukuzeni Mungu katika miili yenu.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Yohane 1:41. 17b</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.Aleluya. Tumemwona Masiya, ndiye Kristu; </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>neema na kweli zimepatikana kupitia yeye. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI	
Yohane 1:35-42 </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yohane alisimama 
tena huko pamoja na wawili wa wafuasi wake, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamwona Yesu akipita njiani, akasema, \"Tazameni, Mwana kondoo wa Mungu.\" </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wale wafuasi wake wawili 
waliposikia hayo walimfuata Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akageuka, akawaona wanamfuata, akawauliza, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mnatafuta nini?\" Nao wakajibu, \"Rabbi,\" inayotafsiriwa mwalimu, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Unakaa wapi?\" Akawaambia, \"Njoni, mtaona.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\" Wakafuatana naye, wakaona, 
wakashinda kwake siku ile. Ilikuwa saa kumi. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andrea, nduguye Simoni Petro, alikuwa mmoja wa wale wawili </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliomsikia Yohane na kumfuata Yesu. Huyo alikutana kwanza na Simoni, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nduguye, akamwambia, \"Tumemwona Masiya,\" (inayotafsiriwa, Kristu). </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akampeleka kwa Yesu. 
Yesu akamtazama, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Wewe ni Simoni, mwana wa Yohane; </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utaitwa Kefa,\" 
inayotafsiriwa, Petro. </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA PILI MWAKA B"},{Guid:"E0VXzQe/W0+oHAITT54/RQ",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA KENDA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
1 Athamaki 19:4-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATHAMAKI</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Elia agĩthiĩ rũgendo rũa mũthenya mũgima arorete </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>werũ-inĩ, agĩikara thĩ gĩtina-inĩ kĩa mwethia; nake akĩĩhoera atĩ akue, </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Rĩu nĩ njiganĩtie; wee Mwathani, nduta  muoyo,</s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ  ũndũ ti niĩ mwega gũkĩra aa baba.  Agĩgĩkoma thĩ toro hau </s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Brush:{Type:0,Color:"FF0000D8"}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwethia-inĩ. Gũgĩtuĩka atĩrĩ, atĩ akĩhutio nĩ mũraika, akĩĩrũo ũũ: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Arahũka ũrĩe irio. Nake agĩgĩcũthĩrĩria, na atĩrĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũtwe wake hagĩkorũo he mũgate ũhĩhĩirio makara igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na mbũthũ ya maaĩ. Nake agĩkĩrĩa o na akĩnyua; agĩcoka agĩkoma </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o rĩngĩ. Ningĩ mũraika wa Mwathani agĩthiĩ harĩ we rĩngĩ, hĩndĩ</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kerĩ; akĩmũhutia, akiuga atĩrĩ: Arahũka ũrĩe irio; nĩ gũkorũo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rũgendo rũrĩa ũgũthiĩ nĩ rũgũkũnenehera mũno.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩkĩarahũka, akĩrĩa, o na akĩnyua: nake agĩgĩthiĩ na hinya </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa irio icio aarĩire matukũ mĩrongo ĩna, mũthenya  na ũtukũ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩgĩkinya kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Ngai kĩrĩa gĩĩtagwo Horeb.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 34:1-2,3-4;5-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: 
Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ndĩrĩgathaga Mwathani o hingo ciothe; kanua gakwa kũmĩkumia </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gatirĩ hĩndĩ gatarĩmũkumagia.  
Mwathani nowe ngoro yakwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩrĩĩrahagĩra: arĩa ahoreri marĩiguaga ũguo magakena.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ kĩgoocei Mwathani mũmũnenehie mwĩ hamwe na niĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũtũũgĩrie rĩĩtwa rĩake tũrĩ o ũndũ ũmwe. Ndarongoririe </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, nake akĩnyamũkĩria, agĩkĩndeithũra harĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maũndũ mothe marĩa maanjiguithĩtie guoya.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andũ aya-rĩ, nĩ maamũrorereirie, makĩarĩrũo nĩ ũtheri, nao</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mothiũ mao matirĩ hingo makahumbwo nĩ thoni. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũthĩnĩki ũyũ aakaire, nake Mwathani akĩmũigua, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmũhonokia mĩnyamaro-inĩ yake yothe.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩ camai muone atĩ Mwathani nĩ mwega</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Aefeso 4:30 – 5:2</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũtikanaiguithie Muoyo Mutheru wa Ngai ũũru, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we ũrĩa mwekĩrirwo rũũri nĩwe o nginya mũthenya ũrĩa wa</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũkũũrwo ũgakinya. Eheriai kũrĩ inyuĩ ũhoro wothe wa gũtũũranĩria </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũũru ngoro,  o na mang’ũrĩka na marakara na kũrumana, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningĩ mweherie muku wothe. Tuganagai o mũndũ na </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ, na mũkĩohanagĩra mehia o mũndũ na mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ũrĩa Ngai nake amuoheire mehia manyu, arĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, rũmanagĩrĩrai kwĩgerekania na Ngai,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta ciana ciendetwo mũno; na mũtũũre mwendaine, o ta ũrĩa Kristũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake aamwedire inyuĩ, agĩkĩruta nĩ ũndũ witũ, nĩ getha atuĩke ihaki </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na igongona rĩa kũrutĩrwo Ngai, rĩĩ na mũtararĩko ũnungĩte wega.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 6,51</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu ekuuga atĩ; Nĩniĩ mũgate ũrĩa waikũrũkire uumĩte</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>igũrũ, wĩ muoyo: mũndũ aarĩa mũgate ũyũ, agatũũra tene na tene. </s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
John 6:41-51</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Ayahudi magĩteta nĩ ũndũ wake, nĩ tondũ oigire: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ niĩ mũgate ũrĩa woimire Igũrũ.  Makiuga atĩrĩ: ũyũ anga towe Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũrũ wa Joseph, na Ithe na nyina nĩ tũmoĩ? Nĩ atĩa tondũ rĩu ekuuga: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ nyumĩte Igũrũ? Nake Yesu agĩcokia ũhoro, akĩmera:</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tigai gũtetania.  Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota gũũka kũrĩ niĩ atagucĩrĩirio </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ Ithe witũ ũrĩa wandekirie; na niĩ nĩ ngamũriũkia mũthenya </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa kũrigĩrĩria. Nĩ haandĩke atĩrĩrĩ maandĩko-inĩ marĩa ma irori:</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao othe makarutwo ũhoro nĩ Ngai.  Mũndũ o wothe  ũiguĩrĩire uhoro gwĩ Ithe witũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agakĩĩruta-rĩ, ũcio nĩ okaga kurĩ niĩ.na tiatĩ kwi mundu wanona ithe witu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tiga uria umite kwi Ngai: ucio nĩoete ithe witu.
Ndamwĩra atĩrĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ma, ma: Mũndũ ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩtie e na muoyo wa tene na tene. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ niĩ mũgate wa muoyo.  Maithe manyu ma tene maarĩaga irio icio </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cietagwo maana, me werũ-inĩ, 
nao nĩ maakuire. Ũyũ-rĩ, nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgate ũrĩa wa gũikũrũka uumĩte Igũrũ, nĩguo mũndũ aũrĩe, aage </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũkanakua. Nĩ niĩ mũgate ũrĩa waikũrũkire uumĩte Igũrũ, wĩ muoyo; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũndũ aarĩa mũgate ũyũ, agatũũra tene na tene; na </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgate ũrĩa ngakĩruta nĩ mwĩrĩ wakwa, ndĩũrute nĩ ũndũ wa muoyo wa kĩrĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA KENDA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"NPET4ZCjqE+HlU1iEZuFJA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA TISA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
1 Wafalme 19:4-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha kwanza cha Wafalme</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Eliya alienda siku nzima jangwani, hadi alipofika </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>chini ya mti wa mzeituni, akaketi chini yake. Akasali akiomba kifo, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Sasa  yatosha, ee Bwana! Uondoe uhai wangu, kwa maana mimi </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si mwema kuliko baba zangu.\"
Akajilaza chini ya mretemu, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akalala usingizi, lakini mara malaika akamgusa, akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simama, ule!\" Akatazama, kumbe, akaona mkate umeokwa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>juu ya makaa, na gudulia la maji kichwani pake. Akala, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akanywa na akajinyosha tena, malaika wa Bwana akaja </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mara ya pili, akamgusa, akasema, \"Simama, ule maana safari </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hii ni kubwa mno kwako!\"
Akasimama, akala, akanywa; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kutokana na nguvu ya chakula hicho, akasafiri kwa muda </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa siku arobaini mchana na usiku hata akafika Horebu mlima wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 34:2-3, 4-5, 6-7, 8-9 (K. 9a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitamtukuza Bwana kila wakati sifa zake zi kinywani mwangu daima.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nafsi yangu itajisifu katika Bwana Wanyonge wasikie na kufurahi. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtukuzeni Bwana pamoja nami, tuliadhimishe jina lake pamoja.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nilimkimbilia Bwana, akanisikiliza, akaniopoa katika hofu zangu zote.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtazameni Mungu mkafurahiwe na nyuso zenu zisihuzunike.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mnyonge huyu alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza, akamwokoa katika shida zake zote. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitilio: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Malaika wa Bwana ameweka kambi kwao,kuwazungukia wale wamchao </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu na kuwaokoa. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alivyo mwema heri mtu yule anayemkimbilia. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Waefeso 4:30-5:2</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Msimhuzunishe Roho Mtakatifu wa Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliyewatia muhuri wake, mpate kuwa tayarı siku ya ukombozi.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila uchungu, hasira, chuki, kelele, matukano na kila aina </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya ubaya viondoshwe kati yenu. Muwe wema ninyı kwa ninyi, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mhurumiane na kusameheana kama Mungu alivyowasamehe </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi katika Kristo. Hivyo fanyeni bidii kumwiga Mungu kama watoto </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wapenzi. Mpendane daima kama Kristo alivyotupenda na kujitoa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sadaka kwa Mungu kwa ajili yetu, ndiyo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>harufu nzuri ya kumpendeza Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Yohane 6:31</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi ndimi mkate wa uzima ulioshuka toka mbinguni, asema </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana; aulaye mkate huu ataishi milele.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 6:41-51</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Wayahudi walimnung' unikia Yesu kwa sababu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alisema, \"Mimi ni mkate ulioshuka toka mbinguni.\" Wakasema, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Je, huyu si Yesu,  mwana wa Yosefu? Twamjua baba yake na mama </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yake. Awezaje kusema 'Nimeshuka 
toka mbinguni’?\" </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akajibu, akawaambia, \"Msinung'unike ninyi kwa ninyi. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna awezaye kuja kwangu, asipovutwa na Baba aliyenituma, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nami nitamfufua siku ya mwisho.
Imeandikwa katika vitabu </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vya manabii: ‘Wote watafundishwa na Mungu.’ Kila amsikiaye Baba na </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kujifunza kwake anakuja kwangu. 
Si kwamba mtu amemwona Baba, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ila yeye atokaye kwa Mungu; huyu ndiye aliyemwona Baba.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amin, amin, nawaambieni, anisadikiye anao uzima wa milele. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi ndimi mkate wa uzima. Baba zenu walikula mana jangwani, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini wakafa; huu ndio mkate utokao mbinguni, ili mtu aulaye asife. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi ndimi mkate wa uzima ulioshuka toka mbinguni;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aulaye mkate huu ataishi milele, na mkate nitakaotoa mimi ni mwili </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wangu kwa ajili ya uzima wa ulimwengu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
