Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Elia agĩgĩũkĩra agĩthiĩ Zarepta.  
Na aakinya  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũrango-inĩ wa kĩhingo gĩa itũũra, akĩona mũtumia wa ndigwa akĩũngania </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũkũ, akĩmwĩta, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ndagũthaitha ndehere </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũĩ na kaihuri nyue , na rĩrĩa athiaga gũtũgira akĩmuĩta </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmuĩra atiri  Ndagũthaitha  ũndehanĩrie na kenyũ ka mũgate.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: O ta ũrĩa Mwathani Ngai waku atũũraga </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>muoyo-rĩ, ndirĩ na kamũgate tiga o kamũtu ka rũhĩ rũmwe </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ke ndigithũ-inĩ, o na tũguta tũnini twĩ cuba-inĩ; na atĩrĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩu ndĩrongania tũkũ nĩguo ‘thiĩ ngathondeke ndĩkaruge nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũndũ wakwa niĩ mwene, o na mũrũ wakwa, nĩguo tũkarĩe </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũcoke tũkue. Nake Elia agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tiga gwĩtigĩra, thiĩ wĩke o ta 
ũguo woiga; no rĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amba ũthondekere kamũgate kanini kaguo, ũndehere, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na thutha wa ũguo wĩthondekere wee mwene mwĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mũrũguo. Nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani, Ngai wa Israeli, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>oigĩte ũũ: Ndigithũ ĩo ya mũtu ndĩninũka, o na kana cuba </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũcio wa maguta ũninũke, tiga o mũthenya ũrĩa Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akoiria mbura gũkũ thĩ. Nake agĩgĩthiĩ, agĩĩka o ta ũguo  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Elia oigĩte gwĩkwo; nake mũtumia ũcio, o na Elia, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na andũ othe a nyũmba yake, makĩria  kandũ kau matukũ maingĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo ndigithũ ĩo ndĩigana gũthira mũtu, o na kana cuba ũgĩthira </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maguta, o ta ũrĩa uuge wa Mwathani watariĩ  ũrĩa aaririe na kanua ka Elia.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani 
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
