Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ũtuagĩra andũ arĩa agũmĩre matuĩro ma kĩhooto; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa ningĩ ũheaga arĩa ahũtu irio. Mwathani-rĩ, arĩa ohe nĩ amohoraga.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ ahingũraga arĩa atumumu maitho, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ ainamũraga arĩa mekonotete,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ enda arĩa athingu; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ amenyagĩrĩra ageni.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  
Mwana wa ngoriai na mũtumia wa ndigwa, nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũmanyitagĩrĩra; nayo njĩra ya andũ aaganu nĩ kũmĩhotomia </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amĩhotomagia. Mwathani 
egũtũũra athamakaga </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tene na tene, Ngai waku, wee Sion-rĩ, egũtũũra athamakaga nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{
