Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristũ ndaatonyire handũ hatheru hathondeketwo nĩ 
moko, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>harĩa hahaananĩtio na harĩa ha ma; nĩ gũtonya </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aatonyire o igũrũ kuo kwene, nĩ getha rĩu onekage </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbere-inĩ ya Ngai nĩ ũndũ witũ. Ningĩ ti getha erutage kaingĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ta ũrĩa mũthacerdoti 
mũnene atonyaga Handũ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Harĩa Hatheru o mwaka o mwaka akuuĩte thakame </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩtarĩ yake mwene; amu kũngĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, no mũhaka </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>angĩtũire anyariragwo kaingĩ kuuma o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa thĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yaambĩrĩirie kũũmbwo. Ĩndĩ rĩu, o mahinda maya ma </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũrigĩrĩria-rĩ, nĩ aguũranĩirio ihinda o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩguo athengie wĩhia o gũthengia nĩ kwĩruta atuĩke </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa igongona we mwene.  
Na ta ũrĩa gũtuĩtwo atĩ andũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makue gĩkuũ o kĩmwe, na 
thutha ũcio matuĩrũo cira-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũguo no taguo Kristũ nake, tondũ nĩ arĩkĩtie kũrutwo arĩ wa igongona </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ihinda rĩmwe, nĩ getha akuue mehia ma andũ aingĩ, nĩ agacoka kuoneka</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ihinda rĩa kerĩ, gũtarĩ na mehia, nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akahonokie andũ arĩa mamwetagĩrĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani 
(MWATHANI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Mathayo 25:34</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: Ũkani, inyuĩ mũrathimĩtwo nĩ Awa, gwatai igai rĩa ũthamaki ũrĩa mwathondekeirũo gwata rĩrĩa thĩ yombirũo.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			             Marko 12:38-44</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akĩra kĩrĩndĩ gĩake, akĩrutana: Wĩmenyagĩrĩrei aandĩki marũa arĩa mendaga gũceera mehumbĩte nguo ndaya, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na makenda kũgeithagio ing’ang’a-inĩ, na gũikaragĩra itĩ cia  mbere me thinagoga, na kũgĩaga harĩa ha gũtĩo maruga-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na no-o manyamaragia nyũmba cia atumia a ndigwa, o makĩhoyaga mahoya maraya nĩ ũndũ wa ũhinga; acio nĩo magatuĩrũo ituĩro rĩũru makĩria. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ningĩ agĩikara thĩ ang’etheire harĩa hekagĩrũo kĩgĩĩna, akĩĩrorera ũrĩa kĩrĩndĩ gĩekagĩra mbia kĩgĩĩna-inĩ kĩu: na andũ aingĩ arĩa maarĩ itonga magĩĩkĩra mbia nyingĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Na gũgĩũka mũtumia wa ndigwa mũthĩni, nake agĩĩkĩra tũthendi twĩrĩ, tũrĩa tũiganaga mbeca ĩmwe.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake agĩĩta arutwo ake, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ na ma, mũtumia ũyũ wa ndigwa mũthĩni nĩ ekĩra nyingĩ kũrĩa andũ othe arĩa marekĩra mbia kĩgĩĩna-inĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondũ acio othe nĩ mekĩra mbia nĩ ũrĩa maingĩhĩtie; nake nĩ ekĩra indo ciake iria oima nacio ciothe, nĩ ũrĩa akĩarĩte, na nĩcio mũthithũ wake wothe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
