Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mũnene ũrĩa wĩ bata ma, na ũhungurĩte agakinya o Igũrũ, na nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Mũrũ wa Ngai, nĩ tũrũmieni ũhoro ũrĩa tũtũire tuumbũraga. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu tũtirĩ na mũruti  igongona mũnene ũtangĩhota gũtũiguĩra tha
 
maũndũ-inĩ maitũ ma kwaga hinya; ũrĩa twĩ nake aanagerio maũndũ-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mothe o ta ithuĩ, tiga atĩ ndaigana kwĩhia o na atĩa.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondũ ũcio nĩ tũthengerei gĩtĩ-inĩ gĩa ũthamaki kĩrĩa kĩa Wega wa Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmĩrĩirie, nĩ getha tũkaiguĩrũo tha, 
na tuone Wega wake wa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũtũteithagia hĩndĩ ĩrĩa tũbataire.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
