Isaiah 53:10-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndungata ya Mwathani yatũire ĩkũraga ĩrĩ mbere </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake o ta mũtĩ mwĩthĩ, o na ta mũri ũmerete rũng’ũrĩ-inĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩa yamenirũo o na ĩkĩregwo nĩ andũ; nĩ mũndũ wĩ kĩeha, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩĩte thĩna. No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩ onire arĩ mwega amũhehenje,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩkĩmũiguithia ũũru ngoro; na  rĩrĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa akeruta </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>muoyo wake utuĩke igongona ria mehia nĩakona ruciaro rwake ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ akaingĩhia matukũ make, o namo maũndũ marĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani endaga mekwo nĩ makagaacĩra nĩ ũndũ wake.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ akona kĩguni kĩa ũrĩa ngoro yake yanaigua ruo mũno, na </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondũ ũcio nĩ akaigua wega. O na ningĩ tondũ wa ũmenyi wayo, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndungata ĩo yakwa thingu ĩgatũma andũ aingĩ matuwo </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>athingu; namo maũũru mao nĩ ĩkamakuua ĩmeherie.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{
