Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, uuge wa Mwathani nĩ mwerekereru; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩra wake wothe nĩ wa kwĩhokwo.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũndũ ũrĩa enda nĩ ũthingu, o na kĩhooto: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thĩ ĩiyũire ũtugi wa Mwathani o kũiyũra.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atĩrĩrĩ; riitho rĩa Mwathani rĩerekeire harĩ arĩa amwĩtigĩri, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩgakĩerekera harĩ andũ arĩa merĩgagĩrĩra o ũtugi wake; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩguo ateithũrage ũtũũro wao gĩkuũ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwata hingo ya ng’aragu amaikaragie na muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA
Tũtegera ũtugi waku, Mwathani: tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mĩoyo itũ-rĩ, ĩkirĩrĩrie yetereire o Mwathani: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>we nowe ũteithio witũ o na ngo iitũ.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũtugi waku, Mwathani, tũma ũikarage na ithuĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũringana o na ũrĩa tũtũire tũkwĩrĩgĩrĩire.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA
