Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, kuona atĩ twĩ na mũruti igongona </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mũnene ũrĩa wĩ bata ma, na ũhungurĩte agakinya o Igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩwe Yesu Mũrũ wa Ngai, nĩ tũrũmieni </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhoro ũrĩa tũtũire tuumbũraga. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amu tũtirĩ na mũruti  igongona mũnene ũtangĩhota gũtũiguĩra tha</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maũndũ-inĩ maitũ ma kwaga hinya; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa twĩ nake aanagerio maũndũ-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mothe o ta ithuĩ, tiga atĩ ndaigana kwĩhia o na atĩa.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ ũcio nĩ tũthengerei gĩtĩ-inĩ gĩa ũthamaki kĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩa Wega wa Ngai tũmĩrĩirie, nĩ getha tũkaiguĩrũo tha, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na tuone Wega wake wa gũtũteithagia hĩndĩ ĩrĩa tũbataire.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Marko 10,45</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu Kristũ ndokire atungatanĩre, na arute muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake ũtuĩke wa gũkũũra andũ aingĩ. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 10:35-45</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Jacob na Johana, ariũ arĩa a Zebedo, makĩmũkuhĩrĩria </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwonania, tũkwenda ũtwĩke o ũrĩa tũgũkũhoya. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akĩmoria: Mũkwenda ndĩmwĩke atĩa? Nao makĩmwĩra </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩrĩ: Ũtwĩtĩkĩrie tũgaikara ũmwe guoko-inĩ gwaku kwa ũrĩo na ũmwe guoko-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwaku kwa ũmotho, wagĩa na riri waku. Nake Yesu akĩmera: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũtiũĩ ũrĩa mũkũhoya. Mwahota kũnyuĩra gĩkombe kĩrĩa niĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngũnyuĩra, kana mũbatithio kũbatithio kũrĩa niĩ ngũbatithio nakuo? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Makĩmwĩra: Twahota. Yesu agĩkĩmera:
Gĩkombe kĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngũnyuĩra no mũkanyuĩra, o na kũbatithio kũrĩa ngũbatithio no </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũkabatithio nakuo: ĩndĩ gũikara guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũrĩo, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana guoko-inĩ gwakwa kwa ũmotho, ti ũndũ ũngĩheanwo nĩ niĩ;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũkaheo o arĩa mathondekeirũo.  Arĩa angĩ ikũmi nao maaigua, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magĩitĩka kũrakara nĩ ũndũ wa Jakubu na Johana. 
Nake Yesu akĩmeta, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmera atĩrĩrĩ: Nĩ mũũĩ atĩ arĩa meragwo nĩ athamaki kwa andũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>a Ndũrĩrĩ nĩ metũũgagĩria igũrũ rĩao, na anene ao nĩ mamathaga.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No ti ũguo gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu; no rĩrĩ, ũrĩa ũngĩenda gũtuĩka </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũnene thĩinĩ wanyu, nĩ atuĩke o ngombo yanyu inyuothe.  </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ ti-itheru Mũrũ wa mũndũ ndokire gũtungatĩrũo, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no atungatanĩre, na arute muoyo wake ũtuĩke wa gũkũũra andũ aingĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani
(NI TWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTO) </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA KENDA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"KF2czpXW9E6FRPyht/B8Xw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO ITATU NA IMWE MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Gũcokerithia Maathani 6:2-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa agĩgĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ na akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ũgetigagĩra Mwathani Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waku, ũmenyagĩrĩre irĩra ciothe cia watho wake wa kũrũmĩrĩrũo, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na maathani make marĩa ngũgwatha  wĩkage, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>we mwene, na mũrũguo, o na mwana wa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũrũguo, matukũ mothe ma muoyo waku; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩguo matukũ maku makĩingĩhio. Tondũ ũcio, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee Israeli, igua, o na ũmenyagĩrĩre ũhoro wa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwĩkaga maũndũ macio; 
nĩ getha ũtũũre wonaga </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wega, na ningĩ nĩ getha mũthaathare mũingĩhe mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũrĩ bũrũri wĩ bũthi wa iria o na ũũki, o ta ũrĩa Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wa mathoguo, aakwĩrire.  Atĩrĩrĩ! Wee Israeli, thikĩrĩria; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Ngai witũ, we wiki nowe Mwathani, nawe enda </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku yothe, na muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waku wothe, o na hinya waku wothe. Namo mohoro maya </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndĩrakũhe ũmũthĩ ngĩgũtaara-rĩ, reka matũre ngoro-inĩ yaku.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 18:2;3-4;46.50a</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani-rĩ, nĩwe rũaro rũakwa rũa ihiga, nĩ kĩhingo gĩakwa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩa hinya, o na nowe mũhatũri; nĩwe Mũrungu wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ndũmba yakwa ya ihiga, ĩrĩa ndahagĩra, ningĩ ngo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yakwa, o naruo rũhĩa rũrĩa rũ’honokagia, o na nowe </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩangĩro rĩakwa rĩakĩtwo handũ haraya na igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngayagĩra Mwathani, o ũcio wagĩrĩirũo nĩ kũgoocagwo, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngakĩhonokio harĩ thũ ciakwa. Ndarigicĩirio nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mĩgeto ya gĩkuũ, nayo mĩiyũro ya wanangi ĩkandua nda.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani e muoyo; we ndũmba yakwa ya ihiga arogathwo! </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>We Ngai mwene ũhonokio wakwa arotũũra atũũgĩrĩte! </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũhonokio nĩ mũnene, ũcio aheaga mũthamaki wake; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũcio wake mũitĩrĩrie maguta-rĩ, nĩ gũtuga amũtugaga.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngwenda mũno, wee Mwathani, o wee hinya wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Aheberea 7:23-28</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨĨRŨO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, (andũ a Israeli) a mbere nĩ aingĩ ao maatuagwo  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aruti igongona, tondũ nĩ maagiragio gũtũũra wĩra-inĩ ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũndũ wa gũkua: Ĩndĩ we rĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa atũũraga muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nginya tene, aikaraga arĩ mũruti igongona atarĩ hingo agatigĩra </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ ũngĩ wĩra ũcio. Ningĩ nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo, nĩ ahotaga </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũhonokia kũna kũna andũ arĩa makũhagĩrĩria Ngai mathiĩrĩire </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>harĩ we, kũona atĩ atũũraga muoyo hĩndĩ ciothe nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amahoyagĩre. Tondũ rĩrĩ, nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũgĩe na mũruti </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>igongona  mũnene ta ũcio,
mũtheru na ũtarĩ na ũũru, kana </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũũgũ, na mwamũre kũrĩ ehia , o na agatũũgĩrio o igũrũ rĩa matu-inĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndarĩ na bata wa kũrutaga magongona o mũthenya </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o mũthenya ta aruti igongona anene acio angĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩa mbere nĩ ũndũ wa mehia make mwene, na thutha ũcio nĩ ũndũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mehia ma kĩrĩndĩ, tondũ  nĩ ekire ũguo  ihinda o rĩmwe rĩa kũigana, rĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>erutiire we mwene. Tondũ watho-rĩ, 
nĩ ũtuaga andũ matarĩ hinya  aruti </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>igongona anene: ĩndĩ kiugo kĩrĩa kĩa mwĩhĩtwa,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũcio wokire thutha wa watho-rĩ, nĩ gĩtuĩte Mũriũ mũruti igongona mũnene, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o we ũtuĩtwo mwagĩrĩru kũna o nginya tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 14:23</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya. Mwathani ekuuga atĩrĩ: mũndũ aakorũo nĩ anyenda, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩmenyagĩrĩra uuge wakwa; nake Awa nĩ arĩmwendaga, na nĩ tũrĩũka kũrĩ we.
Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 12:28-34</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo mwandĩki marũa ũmwe nĩokire kũrĩ Yesu, akĩigua magĩcira, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na aamenya atĩ nĩ amacokeire ũhoro wega, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ rĩathani rĩrĩkũ rĩĩ mbere ya marĩa mangĩ mothe? Nake Yesu agĩcokia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩrĩrĩ: Rĩrĩa rĩa mbere nĩ rĩrĩ: Igua Israeli; Mwathani Ngai witũ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ ũmwe: nawe enda Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yothe, na muoyo waku wothe, na gwĩcirĩra gwaku guothe, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na hinya waku wothe. Narĩo rĩa kerĩ nĩ rĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Enda mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩendete wee mwene.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũtirĩ rĩathani rĩngĩ inene kwĩ macio.  Nake mwandĩki marũa ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ti- itherũ Mwonania,
nĩ woiga wega </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩ Ngai nĩ ũmwe, na gũtirĩ ũngĩ tiga we: ningĩ kũmwenda </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ngoro yothe, o na ũũgĩ wothe, o na hinya wothe, o na mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ende mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩendete we mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũguo nĩ ũkĩrĩte mũno mahaki mothe ma gũcinwo me magima, o na </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magongona mothe. Nake Yesu o na atĩ nĩ aacokia ũhoro ta mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũũgĩ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, ndũrĩ haraya na ũthamaki wa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na thutha ũcio gũtirĩ mũndũ wacokire kwenda kũmũũria ũndũ.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani
(NITWAGUKUMIA WE KRISTU) </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO ITATU NA IMWE MWAKA B"},{Guid:"Zz6BcoTMS0iJBRUSa5ixmg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA ITHANO MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Amosi 7:12-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA KĨRORI AMOSI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Amasia agĩcoka akĩĩra Amosi atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee muoni ũyũ wa maũndũ, wĩthiĩre ũũrĩre bũrũri wa Juda, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũkarĩage irio kuo, na ũrathagĩre ũhoro kuo: no gũkũ Bethel-rĩ, ndũkanarathe ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩngĩ: amu nĩ handũ haamũre haikairio nĩ mũthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ nyũmba nyamũre ya rũrĩrĩ rũrũ. Hĩndĩ ĩo Amosi agĩcokeria </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amasia ũhoro, akiuga atĩrĩ: Niĩ-rĩ, ndirĩ mũnabii, o na ndirĩ wa thiritũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩo ya anabii;niĩ ndĩ mũndũ wa ũhiũ-inĩ na mwĩthondekeri mĩkũyũ: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Mwathani agĩkĩnduta rũũru-inĩ rũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndarũmagĩrĩra. We Mwathani agĩkĩnjĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thiĩ, ũkarathĩre kĩrĩndĩ gĩakwa gĩa Israeli ũhoro.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 85:8-9;10-11;12-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, 
ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngũthikĩrĩria njigue ũrĩa Mũrungu, o we Mwathani, ekuuga, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amu kĩrĩndĩ gĩake, o acio marĩ ũiguano nake, no ũhoro wa thayũ angĩkĩhe, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nakĩo nĩ kĩmenye gĩgacokerera 
ũrimũ wa mwĩĩro. Gũtirĩ nganja </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũhonokania wake ũikaraga hakuhĩ na arĩa amwĩtigĩri, nĩ getha riri ũtũũre bũrũri witũ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũtugi na ũhoro-wa-ma ituĩke nĩ icemainie, ũthingu na thayũ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>igakĩmumunyana; ũhoro-wa-ma ũtuĩke nĩ ũramera ũgĩkunũkaga thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo ũthingu ũgũcũthagĩrĩrie ũrĩ igũrũ matu-inĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩĩ-ni Mwathani no aheanage kĩndũ 
o gĩothe  kĩega, naguo bũrũri ũyũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>witũ ũrutage uumithio waguo. Ũthingu-rĩ, nĩguo ũrĩmũthiaga mbere, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũtũmage makinya make matuĩke njĩra ya gũthiagĩrũo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Tuonie ũtugi waku, Mwathani, ũgĩtwĩtĩkĩrie ũhonokio waku</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Aefeso 1:3-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai arogoocwo, o we Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nowe Ithe, ũrĩa ũtũrathimĩte thĩinĩ  wa Kristũ  na irathimo ciothe </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cia muoyo, iria ciumaga igũrũ, 
kũringana na ũrĩa aatũthurire </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩinĩ  wake thĩ ĩtanombwo, nĩ getha tũtuĩke atheru  na twage  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kaũgũ agĩtuona. Na tondu wagũtwenda-rĩ getha tũtuĩke atheru  na twage  kaũgũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩtuona. Ni atũorereire o mbere niguo tutuike ciana ciake na ũndũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Kristũ, agĩgĩĩka ũguo no ũndũ wa ũrĩa endete gũtũguna, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ getha Wega ũcio aatũitũrũrĩire na ũtana thĩinĩ wake we ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>endete mũno. Na nĩ thĩinĩ wake twakũũrirũo, 
nĩ ũndũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thakame yake, o na  tũkoherũo mehia maitũ kũringana na ũrĩa Wega wake </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũingĩhĩte, o Wega ũcio aatũingĩhĩirie na  ũndũ wa ũũgĩ wake, o na ũtaũku </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake, aarĩkia gũtũmenyithia ũndũ ũrĩa wa hitho aatanyĩte gwĩka </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩinĩ wa Kristũ; naguo nĩguo atĩ, rĩrĩa hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njagĩrĩru ĩgakorũo </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩkinyĩte-rĩ, nĩ agacokanĩrĩria maũndũ mothe thĩinĩ wa Kristũ,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o marĩa marĩ igũrũ na marĩa marĩ gũkũ thĩ; ĩĩ-ni, o thĩinĩ wake we.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ nĩ thĩinĩ wake ithuĩ twatuirũo ũgai wa kũgayũo nĩwe, tondũ wa ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tworereirũo o mbere tũtuĩke ũguo, 
kũringana na kwenda gwake, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we wĩkaga maũndũ mothe o ta ũrĩa aciragĩra gwĩka.  Ningĩ ekire ũguo nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>getha ithuĩ tũtuĩke a gũtũma riri wake ũkumagio,
o ithuĩ arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twambire kwĩrĩgĩrĩra Kristũ.  Na rĩrĩ, nĩ thĩinĩ wake o na inyuĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwarĩkia kũigua ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma, 
nĩguo ũhoro-ũrĩa-mwega</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watũmire mũhonokio-rĩ, o na 
ningĩ mwarĩkia kũmwĩhoka-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgĩĩkĩrũo rũũri nĩ kũheo Muoyo Mũtheru ũũrĩa weranĩirũo:</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kũheo Muoyo Mũtheru ũguo nĩ mũtũrio wa mbere na kũonania na ma </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ nĩ tũkagaĩrũo igai riitũ rĩothe,
rĩarĩkia gũkũũrũo nĩ Ngai rĩtuĩke</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩake kĩũmbe; ũguo noguo twekirũo nĩ getha riri wake ũkumagio.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Athesalonike 2,13</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya.Mũthikĩrĩrie Mũgambo wa Ngai ti ta rĩ </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgambo wa andũ, no ta arĩ mũgambo wa Ngai, na nĩ ma. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 6:7-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩcoka agĩĩta arĩa ikũmi na erĩ, akĩrika kũmatũma o erĩ erĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmahe wathani wa gwatha ngoma thũku; 
na akĩmera, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matigakuue kĩndũ kĩa njĩra, no mũtirima wiki; matigathiĩ na irio, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana mburungo, kana makuue mbia ndoho-inĩ ciao; na mathiĩ mekĩrĩte  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iratũ: akĩmera ningĩ; Na mũtikehumbe  nguo igĩrĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩcoka akĩmera atĩrĩ: O kũndũ mwatonya mũciĩ raaragai kũu nginya </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũkoima kuo. Na kũrĩa andũ matakamũgwata ũgeni, na marege </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũmũigua-rĩ, mũkiuma kuo, thukiai magũrũ manyu rũkũngũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rũitĩke, rũtuĩke ũira kũrĩ o. Nao magĩthiĩ, makĩhunjia ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ andũ merire. Na magĩtũma ndaimono nyingĩ ciume andũ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na magĩitĩrĩria andũ aingĩ maguta, arĩa maarĩ arũaru, makĩmahonia.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA ITHANO MWAKA B"},{Guid:"xtEHF922ZEWe2//cUfzGuQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA INYANYA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Thama  16:2-4,12-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, nakĩo kĩrĩndĩ kĩu gĩothe gĩa ciana cia Israeli gĩgĩteteria  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa na Haron kũu werũ-inĩ; nacio ciana cia Israeli ikĩmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na arĩ korũo nĩ kũũragwo tworagĩirũo na guoko kwa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani oro kũu bũrũri wa Misri, 
hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twaikaraga </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũkuhĩhĩirio nĩ nyũngũ cia nyama, o na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twarĩaga mũgate </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nginya tũkahũna! Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, mwatũrutire kũu,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgĩtũrehe werũ-inĩ ũyũ, mũũrage kĩrĩndĩ gĩkĩ gĩothe na ng’aragu.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Mwathani agĩkĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ:
Nĩ ngũmuurĩria irio ciume igũrũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta mbura; nao andũ nĩ makoimagara mũthenya o </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũthenya makonganie cia kũmaigania,
nĩguo ndĩmagerie </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana nĩ marĩthiaga marũmĩrĩire watho wakwa, kana aca.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ njiguĩte ũrĩa ciana cia Israeli itetete. 
Aria nacio </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũciĩre atĩrĩ: Hwaĩ-inĩ mũrĩrĩaga nyama, na rũcinĩ mũrĩhũnagio </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mũgate; na nĩ mũkũmenya atĩ niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani Ngai wanyu. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ hwaĩ-inĩ wakinya, hagoka tũmakia-arũme; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>natuo tũkaiyũra handũ hau maambĩte hema ciao;</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na rũcinĩ-rĩ, ime rĩkaroka kũgĩa handũ hau mambĩte hema ciao, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩkaharigicĩria. Na rĩrĩ, ime rĩu rĩaitĩka, kũndũ jũu werũ-inĩ guothe gũkaiyũra </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũnyamũ tũthiũrũrĩ, tũnyihĩte o ta ũrĩa ime rĩikaraga rĩĩ thĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa rĩamatio </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mbaa. Na rĩrĩa ciana cia Israeli cionire tũnyamũ tũu, ikĩũrania </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mũndũ na mũndũ atĩrĩ: Ĩ nĩ kĩ gĩkĩ? 
Nĩ ũndũ itiamenyaga </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩa kĩo. Nake Musa agĩciĩra atĩrĩ:Nĩ irio iria </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani amũheete cia kũrĩa.  </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi  78:3-4;23-24;25.54</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
We Mwathani akĩmaitũrũrĩra ngano ya ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Marĩa twanaigua na tũkamamenya, o marĩa maithe maitũ maanatwĩra.  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tũtingĩmahitha ciana ciao, tiga twĩrage rũciaro rũria rũi </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thutha ũkumio wa Mwathani, kinya ũhoro wa hinya wake, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa maũndũ ma magegania maria aaneka.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
We Mwathani akĩmaitũrũrĩra ngano ya ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No we agĩatha kũrĩa matu-inĩ, agĩkĩhingũra mĩrango </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya igũrũ; akĩmaitũrũrĩra mana ta mbura </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩe, ngano ya kũu igũrũ-rĩ, nĩyo aakĩmaheire.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Wee Mwathani akĩmaitũrũrĩra ngano ya ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andũ magĩkĩrĩa irio o iria cia ihoti; nĩ rĩĩgu mũingĩ aamerehithĩirie, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa kũmahũnia. Akiya gũkamakinyia rũtere-inĩ rũa kũndũ gwake kwamũre, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩma-inĩ gĩkĩ guoko  gwake kwa ũrĩo kwegũrĩire.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
We Mwathani akĩmaitũrũrĩra ngano ya ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Aefeso 4:17. 20-24</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A EFESO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, niĩ ni nguuga atiri, na ngamuumburĩra ndĩ thĩinĩ wa Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ mũtigacoke gũthiaga na mĩthiĩre ĩrĩa andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ mathiaga </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nayo, marũmanĩrĩire na uungumania wa meciria mao. No inyuĩ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũguo tiguo mwĩrutĩte ũhoro wa Kristũ; mũngĩkorũo ti-itherũ nĩ mũiguĩte </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgambo wake, na mũkarutwo ũhoro mwĩ thĩinĩ wake, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũhoro-wa-ma ũrĩa wĩ na Yesu.  Ha ũhoro wa mĩthiĩre yanyu yambere-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩaũrei mũndũ ũrĩa wa tene, ũrĩa ũthũkĩte nĩ ũndũ wa kũrũmĩrĩra merirĩria </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ma kũhenania; na merũhio ma muoyo o na meciria manyu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwĩhumbe mũndũ ũrĩa mwerũ, o ũrĩa wombirũo ahanaaine na Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>e na ũthingu, na ũtheru ũrĩa uumanĩte na ũhoro-wa-ma.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Mathayo 4,4</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya.Ti mũgate wiki ũtũũragia mũndũ muoyo, no kiugo </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o gĩothe kĩrĩa kiumaga kanua ka Ngai.
Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
John 6:24-35</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo, tondũ ũcio kĩrĩndĩ gĩakĩona atĩ Yesu ndarĩ kuo, o na arutwo ake, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gĩgĩtonya macua icio arĩ kĩo, gĩgĩthiĩ Kafarnao  gũcaria Yesu.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na maamũkora mũrĩmo ũrĩa, makĩmũũria: Mwonania, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũũkire rĩ gũkũ? Nake Yesu akĩmacokeria akiuga: ndamwĩra </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩrĩ o ma, ma: Mũtikũnjaragia nĩ ũndũ mũronire ciama; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũkũnjaragia nĩ ũndũ mũrarĩire mĩgate, mũrahũna.
Tigaga gũtungatĩra </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>irio iria ithiraga; tungatagĩrai irio iria ciikaraga nginya muoyo wa tene </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tene, iria Mũrũ wa mũndũ akũmũhe;
amu nĩwe mwĩkĩre </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũhũri nĩ Ithe, Ngai.  Nao magĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Twĩkage atĩa, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩguo tũtuĩke nĩ mawĩra ma Ngai tũraruta?
Nake Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩcokia akĩmera: Wĩra wa Ngai nĩ rĩrĩ, nĩ mwĩhoke ũrĩa areketie.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, kĩmenyithia gĩkĩrĩ kĩrĩkũ ũrutaga, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩguo tuone tũgwĩtĩkie? Nĩ ũndũ ũrĩkũ wĩkaga? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maithe maitũ ma tene marĩaga irio iria cietagwo maana, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>me werũ-inĩ, o ta ũrĩa haandĩkirwo, atĩ:
Aamaheire mũgate </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uumĩte Igũrũ marĩe.  Nake Yesu agĩkĩmera: Ndamwĩra </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩrĩ o ma, ma: Ti Musa wamũheire mũgate uumĩte Igũrũ; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no nĩ Awa mũmũhei mũgate uumĩte Igũrũ ũrĩa wa ma. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu-rĩ, mũgate wa Ngai no ũrĩa ũikũrũkaga uumĩte igũrũ, ũgekagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ muoyo. Nao magĩkĩmwĩra: Mũthuri ũyũ, tũheage mũgate </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũcio o hingo ciothe. Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ niĩ mũgate wa muoyo; mũndũ ũũkĩte kũrĩ niĩ ndakahũta, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mũndũ wĩĩ’hokete, niĩ, ndarĩ hingo akanyota.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA INYANYA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"SoMJtxN4wkC/OoTqnKbpAg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"Blue Sky over Field.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA INYANYA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Ũũgĩ 7:7-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨŨGĨ: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ndahoire na ngĩheo ũmenyi; nĩ ndaririe na hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ngĩheo muoyo wa Ũũgĩ.  Ndamũtuire wa goro kũrĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthĩgi na itĩ cia ũthamaki; 
ũtonga ũgerekanĩtio nake </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ wa tũhũ.  Gũtirĩ ihiga o na rĩrĩkũ rĩa goro ndamũgerekanirie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>narĩo nĩ amu thahabu yothe ĩgerekanĩtio nake no ta </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩhumbu kĩa mũthanga, na ningĩ mbere yake mbeca </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ihuana ta ndoro. Ndamwendete kũrũga ũgima wa mwĩrĩ kama </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũthaka, ngĩmũhuanania na ũtheri, tondũ mũrũri wake </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndũkomaga. Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndatwaranire nake nĩ ndonire </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>indo ciothe njega, na ũtonga ũrĩa woimaga njara-inĩ ciake ndũngĩtarĩka.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 90:2;2-4;12-13;14-16</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O mbere irĩma itaanaciarũo, 
o ũtaanomba thĩ na mabũrũri, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuuma o tene na nginya tene, wee ũrĩ o Mũrungu.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũhũndũraga andũ magacoka gũtuĩka mũthegethege; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũkoiga, Cokai, ciana ici cia kĩrĩndĩ.
Amu harĩ wee, mĩaka ngiri </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no ta mũthenya wa ira, 
o ũguo ũrathirire ũrehera, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ningĩ no ta ituanĩra rĩmwe rĩa camu wa ũtukũ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gĩtũmenyithie gũtara matukũ 
maitũ nĩ getha tũgĩe na ngoro </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cia kũũhĩga.  Garũrũka, Jehova; 
nĩ nginya rĩ? </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gĩcoke kũiguĩra ndungata ciaku tha.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rũcinĩ ũroke gũtũhũnia ũtugi waku; 
nĩguo tũtũũre </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũkũngũyagia o tũgĩkenaga 
matukũ maitũ mothe. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wĩko waku ũroonwo kũrĩ ndungata </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciaku, na ũkaru waku woneke kũrĩ ciana ciacio.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani ũrathime wĩra wa moko maitũ</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Aheberea 4:12-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MARĨA MAANDĨKĨIRŨO 
KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũgambo wa Ngai ũrĩ muoyo, 
na ũrĩ hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩ mũgĩ kũrũga rũhiũ o ruothe rũnoretwo mĩena yerĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũgatheca ũgakĩgayũkania muoyo na ũtũũro, o na </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũgaatĩa mĩthimo na ũkagayũkania mahĩndĩ ma maguta,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ningĩ nĩ ũhiũhaga gũkũũrana meciria ma ngoro o na </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa icirĩire gwĩka.  Na gũtirĩ kĩndũ o gĩothe kĩũmbe </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gĩtonekete mbere yake; no rĩrĩ, indo ciothe ciikaraga itarĩ humbĩre, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no iguũrĩtio maitho-inĩ make, we mwene ũhoro witũ.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Aefeso 1:17-18</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ atũhe o mũndũ muoyo wa ũũgĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha tũmenye ũtarii atia wetereri wa rĩĩtana riitũ. Alleluia</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 10:17-30</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu oimagaraga erekeire njĩra, mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmũteng’erera, akĩmũturĩria ndu, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Mwonania mwega,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ atĩa ingĩĩka nĩ getha ngagae muoyo wa tene na tene? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: Ũkũnjĩta mwega nĩkĩ?</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũtirĩ mwega tiga o ũmwe, nĩwe Ngai.  Ndũũĩ maathani atĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndũkanoragane, ndũkanatharanie, 
ndũkanaiye, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndũkanaigĩrĩre mũndũ kĩgenyo, ndũkanahenanie, 
tĩa thoguo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nyũkwa? Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, 
mũrutani, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maũndũ macio ndũire ndĩmarũmĩtie nginya ndĩ o </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũnyinyi. Nake Yesu,  aamũrora, akĩmwenda, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ kũrĩ ũndũ ũmwe ũtigairie: nĩ rĩrĩ, thiĩ, ũkendie indo ciothe iria wĩ nacio, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhe arĩa athĩni, na nĩ ũkagĩa na ũtonga Igũrũ: na ũũke, ũnũmĩrĩre.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nowe agĩtuka gĩthithi aaigua ũhoro ũcio, agĩthiĩ e na kĩeha:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũndũ warĩ na indo nyingĩ. Nake Yesu akĩroranga, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩĩra arutwo ake atĩrĩ: Andũ arĩa me na indo-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kaĩ nĩ makona hinya magĩgatonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai-ĩ! </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao arutwo makĩgega nĩ ciugo icio ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu agĩcokia ũhoro rĩngĩ, akĩmera: Ciana ici, andũ arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mehokete indo-rĩ, kaĩ nĩ hinya 
magĩgatonya </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai! Nĩ ũhũthũ ngamĩra ĩhungure kahoro ga cindano, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũrĩ mũndũ mũtongu atonye ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makĩgega mũno mũno, makĩmũũria: Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nũ ũngĩkĩhota kũhonoka? Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ, amacũthĩrĩirie:</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũtingĩhoteka nĩ andũ, no ti ũguo Ngai: amu-rĩ, maũndũ mothe </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mahotekaga nĩ Ngai. Nake Petro akĩrika kũmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩu-rĩ, ithuĩ tũtitigĩte indo ciothe na tũgakũrũmĩrĩra? Nake Yesu akiuga: </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ na ma: Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũtigĩte nyũmba, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana agatiga ariũ a nyina, kana aarĩ a nyina, kana nyina, kana ithe, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana ciana, kana ithaka, nĩ ũndũ wakwa na tondũ wa Injiri, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtakaheo rĩu matukũ maya  tũrĩ, na akĩrĩrĩrio maita igana, nyũmba, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ariũ a nyina, na aarĩ a nyina, na manyina, na ciana, na ithaka, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hamwe na mĩnyamaro; na hingo ĩrĩa ĩgoka thutha, aheo muoyo ũtathiraga.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA INYANYA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"FcZTUCoDCUmHmvvcwgazrg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA MUGWANJA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
2 Athamaki 4:42-44</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATHAMAKI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, na rĩrĩ, hagĩgĩũka mũndũ oimĩte Baali-Shalisha, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩrehere mũndũ ũcio wa Ngai irio cia mũro wa mbere, nacio nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mĩgate mĩrongo ĩĩrĩ ya cairĩ, o na igira njigũ cia ngano aciĩkĩrĩte </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kĩondo-inĩ. Nake akiuga atĩrĩ; Cinengere andũ marĩe. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nayo ndungata yake ĩkĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Hĩ! Atĩ atĩa? </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njigĩre andũ igana mĩgate o ro ĩno?
No Elisha akiuga atĩrĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩhe andũ marĩe; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani oigĩte ũũ: Nĩmekũrĩa,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ mekũmĩtigaria. Tondũ ũcio ndungata yake </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩgĩkĩmĩiga mbere ya andũ acio, nao makĩrĩa na </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩmĩtigaria, o ta ũrĩa uuge wa Mwathani watariĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                               Thaburi 145: 8-9;10-11;12-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ muuma andũ, ningĩ nĩ wa matha maingĩ; ndahiũhaga </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũrakara, na e na ũtugi mũnene.  Mwathani-rĩ, 
nĩ ekaga andũ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe wega; indo ciothe iria aathondekire gũtirĩ atarĩ tha nakĩo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mawĩra macio maku mothe, Mwathani, megũtũũra </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o magũcokagĩria ngatho; nao andũ arĩa maiguaine nawe,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũgatha no matũre makũgathaga.  Megũtũũra moigaga ũrĩa ũthamaki </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waku wĩ riri, o magĩteretaga ũhoro wa ũrĩa wee wĩ na ũhoti.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maũndũ macio maku ma ũhoti mamamenyithie ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o gwata ũthamaki waku, mamere ũrĩa ũkaru waguo  wĩ riri, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũthamaki waku nĩ ũrĩa wa tene na tene, wathani waku-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũtũũraga nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Nĩ ngagoocaga rĩĩtwa rĩaku, Mwathani
 
GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
John 6:1-15</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩthiĩ mũrĩmo ũrĩa ũngĩ wa iria rĩa Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na norĩo iria rĩa Tiberiade.  Akĩrũmĩrĩrũo nĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ ma,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndũ nĩ kĩonaga ciama  iria ekaga andũ arĩa arũaru akĩmahonia.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩhaica kĩrĩma-inĩ, agĩikara thĩ ho na arutwo ake. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩrĩ, Paska yarĩ hakuhĩ gũkinya, nĩyo gĩathĩ kĩrĩa kĩa Ayahudi.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu aagĩtiira maitho, ona atĩ gwĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ gĩgũũka kũrĩ we, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩũria Filipo atĩrĩ: Tũkũgũra mĩgate kũ, andũ aya makĩrĩe? </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akĩmũria ũguo atĩ amũgerie amu we mwene nĩ oĩ ũrĩa egwĩka. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Filipo akĩmucokeria atĩrĩ: mĩgate ya ciringi magana merĩ ndĩngĩmaigana </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ nĩguo o mũndũ one kanini.  Na mũrutwo wake ũmwe, wetagwo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andrea, mũrũ wa nyina na Simone Petro, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Haha he kahĩĩ kena mĩgate itano  ya ngano ya cairĩ, na ciũngũyũ  igĩrĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩndĩ tũirio tũu-rĩ, tũkĩrĩ kĩ, andũ maigana ũũ? Nake Yesu akiuga: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩrai andũ maikare thĩ. Na rĩrĩ, handũ hau haarĩ na nyeki nyingĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Arũme magĩgĩikara thĩ, mangĩhinga ta ngiri ithano, nake Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩkĩiyũkia mĩgate ĩo, na aarĩkia gũcokeria Ngai ngatho, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩgaĩra andũ acio maaikaire thĩ; o na ciũngũyũ nacio o ũndũ ũmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmahe ciigana o ũrĩa mekwenda. 
Na maahũna, akĩĩra arutwo ake: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Oyai cienyu iria itigarĩte, gũtikore kĩndũ. Magĩkĩoya,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩiyũria  ciondo ikũmi na igĩrĩ cienyũ  cia mĩgate ĩo ĩtano ya cairĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iria ciatigirio nĩ  andũ acio maarĩire. 
Nao andũ maakĩona </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩama kĩu aaringire, makiuga atĩrĩ: Ti-itherũ, ũyũ nĩwe mũrathi ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa gũũka gũkũ thĩ. Nake Yesu aakĩona atĩ nĩ makiriĩ gũũka kũmũtwara</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na hinya makamũtue  mũthamaki wao, agĩcoka  kĩrĩma-inĩ wiki.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA MUGWANJA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"H0SQqQ1ROEe8Kl8YNQ7/KA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA ITHATU 
MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Ũũgi 1:13-15.2:23-24</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨŨGĨ:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gĩkuũ gĩtiarĩ wĩko wa Ngai, ndakenagio nĩ ũndũ wa kũharaganio</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa arĩa marĩ muoyo. Nĩ ũndũ nĩ ombire indo ciothe itũũre muoyo; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>indo ciothe iria ciombirũo nĩ ikoragwo na ũgima thĩinĩ wacio </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũtingĩkorũo kũrĩ ũrogi, na gĩkuũ gĩtikoragwo na hinya thĩinĩ wa thĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ mũtugo mwega ndũkuaga.  Na ningĩ Ngai ombire mũndũ atarĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa kũharagana; amũmbire thĩinĩ wa mũhiano wa mũgĩre wake Wee mwene;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũiru wa Shaitani nĩguo warehire gĩkuũ thĩinĩ wa thĩ, o ta ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩa maikaranagia na Ngai makamenya.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                        Thaburi 30:4-5;10.11a.12b</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani; tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ, ũgakĩaga kũreka thũ ciakwa ingenerere.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>  Ĩ Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ ũmĩrutĩte thĩ o kwa ngoma; na ũnjikairie na muoyo, ndige gũtonyerera irima.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inĩrai Mwathani mũmũgooce, inyuĩ mũrĩ ũiguano nake, rĩĩtwa rĩu rĩake rĩamũre mũkĩrĩcokerie ngatho.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>  Amu marakara make no ma kahinda kanini, ĩndĩ mĩtuganĩre yake nĩ ya gũtũũria mũndũ muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.	Mwathani, igua ũkĩnginyĩrie wega waku: Ĩ Mwathani, ĩtĩkĩra gũtuĩka mũndeithia. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Rĩu nĩ ũngarũranĩirie mũcayo ũcio ndĩrarĩ naguo ũgatuĩka ndũrũhĩ, Ĩ Mwathani, Ngai wakwa-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ngũgĩtũũra ngũcokagĩria ngatho nginya mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, wee Mwathani, tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>  </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
2 Akorintho 8:7. 9. 13-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, na rĩrĩ, o ta ũrĩa mũingĩhĩtie maũndũ mothe-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wĩtĩkio, na kũhota kwaria, na ũmenyo, o na kĩyo gĩtangĩnyihia, ningĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wendani ũrĩa mũtwendete naguo-rĩ, kĩingĩhiei wega ũndũ ũyũ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa gũtugana o naguo. Amu nĩ mũũĩ Wega ũrĩa Mwathani witũ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Kristũ aarĩ naguo, mũgakĩmenya atĩ o na aarĩ gĩtonga, nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aatuĩkire ngĩa nĩ ũndũ wanyu, nĩ getha inyuĩ mũtuĩke itonga nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ũrĩa we aakĩarĩte.Ndikuuga ũguo nĩguo andũ angĩ mehererio </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩna, na inyuĩ mũthĩne, no rĩrĩ, nĩ getha kũigananio maũndũ, ihinda </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩrĩ ũrĩa  inyuĩ mũingĩhĩtie indo ũtuĩke wa gũteithia wagi wao, nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩrĩa acio makaingĩhia indo, o nao 
magateithia wagi </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wanyu; nĩguo maũndũ maigananio. O ta ũrĩa haandĩkĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũrĩa wacokereirie nyingĩ ndaarĩ kĩndũ o na kĩ aatigarĩirio, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake ũrĩa wacokereirie tũnini 
ndaanyihirie.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 6: 63. 68</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya			   
Ciugo ciaku, wee Mwathani, nĩcio muoyo na ũtũũro: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee nĩwe wĩna ciugo cia ũtũũro wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ. Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 5:21-24, 35-43</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu aarĩkia kũringa rĩngĩ na marikabu, aakinya mũrĩmo </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũrĩa ũngĩ, kĩrĩndĩ kĩingĩ gũkĩũngana 
harĩ we: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake aarĩ hau hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia iria.  Na gũgĩũka mũnene ũmwe wa thinagogi, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wetagwo Jairũ; na aamuona, akĩmũgũĩra thĩ magũrũ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmũthaitha mũno akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Kairĩtu gakwa nĩ gakiriĩ gũkua:</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndagũthaitha ũũke ũgakaigĩrĩre moko maku, nĩguo  kahonio gatũũre muoyo.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magĩgĩthiĩ nake; na kĩrĩndĩ  kĩingĩ gĩkĩmuuma thutha, na gĩkamũhatĩkaga.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mũtumia watũire oiraga thakame mĩaka ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akanyamario na maũndũ maingĩ nĩ athondekani aingĩ, na akanina </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>indo ciake ciothe, na ndahone, no kwĩhĩrũo akehĩrũo makĩria, ũcio-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ nĩ aaiguĩte ũhoro wa Yesu, agĩũka na thutha wake thĩ-inĩ wa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩndĩ, akĩmũhutia nguo. Tondũ nĩ oigire atĩrĩ: ingĩhutia o nguo </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciake ciiki ndahona. Na kahinda o kau rĩurĩro rĩa thakame yake  rĩgĩtuma, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩigua mwĩrĩ ta aahonio mũrimũ wake. 
Nake Yesu, tondũ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ aamenyire na ngoro yake atĩ hinya ũrĩa woimaga kũrĩ we ũrĩ kuuma, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩĩhũgũra o rĩmwe e thĩinĩ wa kĩrĩndĩ, akĩũria: Nũ wa’hutia nguo? </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao arutwo ake makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: 
Woria, Nũ wa’hutia, ũkĩonaga </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩndĩ gĩgĩkũhatĩka? Nake akĩroranga one ũrĩa wĩkĩte ũguo.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake mũtumia agĩũka o agĩĩtigagĩra na akĩinainaga, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ kũmenya ũrĩa ekĩtwo, akĩmũgũĩra thĩ, akĩmũhe ũhoro wothe na ma.  </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Mwarĩ ũyũ, gwĩtĩkia gwaku nĩkuo  gwatũma ũhone;</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thiĩ na ũhoro, ũikare wĩ mũhonu mũrimũ waku. Andũ magĩũka moimĩte </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa mũnene ũrĩa wa thunagogi, makiuga: Mwarĩguo nĩ aakua: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgũcoka gũtanga Mũrutani nĩkĩ? Nake Yesu, atekũũria ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kweranwo, akĩĩra mũnene wa thunagogi atĩrĩ: Ndũkamake, no </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gwĩtĩkia wĩtĩkie.  Na ndarĩ mũndũ etĩkĩririe matwarane nake, tiga Petro </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Jakubu, na John ũrĩa mũrũ wa nyina na Jakubu.  Magĩkinya nyũmba </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya mũnene ũcio wa thunagoga; 
nakuo akĩona ironjo, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na andũ aingĩ mekũrĩra na magakaya mũno.  Na aarĩkia gũtonya </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Mũraronja nĩkĩ, na mũkarĩra? Mwana ti mũkuũ, no toro </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩ. Nao makĩmũthekerera.
Nake aarĩkia kũmoimia nja othe, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩtwara Ithe wa mwana na nyina na arĩa mokĩte nake, agĩtonya kũu </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwana aarĩ. Akĩnyita mwana gwoko, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: “Talitha kumi”! </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo wataũrũo, nĩ ta kuuga: Kairĩtu gaka, ndakwĩra atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũkĩra! Nako kairĩtu gagĩũkĩra  o rĩmwe, gagĩĩtwara; nĩ gũkorũo nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kaahingĩtie miaka ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ.
Magĩkĩgega kĩgeganio </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩnene mũno. Nake akĩmakaania mũno </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matikamenyithie mũndũ ũhoro ũcio: agĩcoka </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmaatha atĩ kairĩtu kaheo gĩa kũrĩa.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani. 
(NITWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU) </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA ITHATU MWAKA B"},{Guid:"ZXzBKy0l50eDc/8woNZtTA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA IGIRI MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Job 38:1,8-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA JOB:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ  ĩo Mwathani agĩcokeria Job ũhoro e kĩhuhũkanio-inĩ , </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiuga atĩrĩrĩ : Nũ wahingĩire iria rĩrĩa inene na mĩrango rĩrĩa rĩatothokire rĩkiuma ihu-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndatuire matu nguo yarĩo,
ngĩgĩtũma nduma ndumanu ĩtuĩke tama warĩo, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta ũrĩa ũrigicagĩrio mwana? Na ngĩrĩĩkĩrĩra mũhaka  mũtue nĩ niĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngĩkĩrĩhingĩra na mĩgĩĩko o na mĩrango.  Ngiuga: Ũrĩkinyaga o hau, na ndũkanaagarare;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hau nĩ ho makũmbĩ maku megugumi marĩtĩmagĩrĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Ciugo cia Mwathani 
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                               Thaburi 107:23-24;25-26;28-29;30-31</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Nĩ macokerie Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andũ arĩa maikũrũkaga 
magathiĩ na iria me thĩinĩ wa marikabu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩa mathiaga wonjoria kũu maaĩ-inĩ maingĩ, acio nĩ monaga mawĩko ma Mwathani; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maũndũ make me magegania magakĩmeonera me maaĩ-inĩ macio mariku.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu rĩrĩa oiga, rũhuho nĩ rũarahũkaga, 
rũrĩa rũa kĩhuhũkanio, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naruo rũkaiyũkĩrĩria makũmbĩ ma maaĩ, 
macio ma iria, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ makoyũo na igũrũ o nginya matu-inĩ, ningĩ magacoka na thĩ o mũriko-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngoro ciao ĩgakĩregera nĩ ũũru ũrĩa marona.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magagĩkaĩra Mwathani tondũ wa ũrĩa mathĩnĩkĩte, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake akamaruta mĩnyamaro-inĩ ĩo marĩ nayo. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atũmaga kĩhuhũkanio gĩcoke kũhorera, makumbĩ macio moima kuo magagĩkira ngiria.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao magakena nĩ ũndũ rĩu mo nĩ mahorerete, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agakĩmakinyia rĩingĩrĩro-inĩ o rĩrĩa merirĩirie makinye;</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o, ta nĩ macokerie Mwathani ngatho 
nĩ ũndũ wa ũtugi wake, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maũndũ ma magegania marĩa ekaga ciana cia kĩrĩndĩ!</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ macokerie  Mwathani ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ ma magegania make</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
2 Akorintho 5:14-17</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, wendani ũrĩa Kristũ atwendete naguo nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũtũhatagĩrĩria, nĩ ũndũ tũonaga atĩrĩ, atĩ mũndũ ũmwe nĩ aakuire ithenya </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩa andũ othe, na tondũ ũcio gũkua nĩ maagĩkuire othe. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ atĩrĩ, aakuire ithenya rĩa andũ othe, nĩ getha arĩa matũũraga muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matigacoke gũtũũra nĩ ũndũ wa bata wao ene, no matũre nĩ ũndũ wa bata </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ũcio wakuire ithenya rĩao, agĩcoka akĩriũka. Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuuma rĩu tũticoka gũtarania ũhoro wa mũndũ na njĩra ya ũmwĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gwagĩtuĩka kwĩ hingo twataranagia ũhoro wa Kristũ na njĩra ya ũmwĩrĩ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩu tũtigĩte gũtarania ũhoro wake na njĩra ĩo.  Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ angĩkorũo arĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ agarũrũkĩte agatuĩka mũndũ ũngĩ mwerũ: maũndũ marĩa ma tene </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mathirĩte; nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ matuĩkĩte mangĩ merũ.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.
(NGAI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Thaburi 148:12,15</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya.
Wee Jerusalem, kumia Ngai waku </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũrĩa ũtũmaga Mũgambo wake guo Mwene gũkũ thĩ. Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 4:35-41</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mũthenya o ũcio, hwaĩ-inĩ wakinya, Yesu akĩĩra Arekio ake: </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ tũringe mũrĩmo ũrĩa. Magĩtigana na kĩrĩndĩ kĩu,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> makĩmũtwara hamwe nao marikabu-inĩ, o ũguo aatariĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kwarĩ marikabu ingĩ ciatwaranire hamwe nake. Na gũkĩgĩa kĩhuhũkanio kĩnene kĩa rũhuho, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo makũmbĩ ma maaĩ magĩĩtonyia o marikabu thĩinĩ, marikabu igĩkĩenda kũiyũra maaĩ</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We nake aarĩ mũthia-inĩ wa thutha wa marikabu akomeire muuto e toro: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩmũũkĩria, makĩmwĩra: Mũrutani, githĩ ndũkũũria tũkĩũra? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake agĩũkĩra, agĩkaania rũhuho, 
na akĩĩra iria atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kira, ũhorere. Naruo rũhuho rũgĩtuĩka, gũkĩhorera o kũhorera.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩcoka akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Mũmakĩtee nĩkĩ?
Mũtirĩ mũretĩkia </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na rĩu? Nao magĩĩtigĩra o mũno, makĩũrania atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kaĩ mũndũ ũyũ akĩrĩ ũ, kuona atĩ o na rũhuho na iria nĩ imũiguaga?</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani 
(NITWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,Style:{Background:{Image:"sunsea4.jpg"}},
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA IGIRI MWAKA B"},{Guid:"zi34KCsAX0iO4peRkTpU9Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA ITHANO MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Ũgĩ 2:12. 17-20</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ŨGĨ: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andũ arĩa matoĩ Ngai moigaga atĩrĩ: Rekei tweterere mũndũ ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũthingu, tondũ nĩ atũrakaragia, na akamenereria ũtũũro witũ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatũruma tondũ nĩ tũthũkagia rĩathana na  agatũcuka nĩ ũndũ wa mĩtugo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iitũ mĩũru. Ta kĩrekei twone kana ũrĩa oigaga nĩ ũhoro wa ma.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ta rekei twone ũrĩa ithirĩro rĩake rĩgakorũo rĩtariĩ. Angĩkorũo mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũyũ mũthingu nĩ Mwana wa Ngai-rĩ, Ngai nĩ akamũgitĩra na amũkũre kuuma </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>moko-inĩ ma thũ ciake. Rekei tũmũgerie nĩ getha aigue ruo, nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmenye ũhoreri ũyũ wake, na twone ũrĩa ũkirĩrĩria wake ũigana.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rekei tũmũrage gĩkuũ gĩa thoni tondũ Ngai nĩ ekũmũmenyerera, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũringana na ũrĩa oigire.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 54:1-2;3;4-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ Ngai, honokia na rĩĩtwa rĩaku, tondũ wa ũguo wĩ na ũhoti-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nduĩra ũhoro wakwa.  Ngai, igua  ihoya rĩakwa; ciugo ici cia kanua gakwa, citegere matũ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gũkorũo nĩ njũkĩrĩirũo nĩ andũ ageni, muoyo  wakwa nĩ ũracario </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ andũ marĩ itua-nda: Ngai -rĩ, magakĩrega aikare maitho-inĩ mao.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rĩrĩ, Ngai nĩwe mũndeithia; muoyo wakwa nĩ Mwathani  ũrĩ wa kũũtiirĩrĩra. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ nĩ igongona  ndĩĩkũrutĩra, ndute o ndĩĩendeire; wee Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ngatho ndĩĩgĩcokeria rĩĩtwa rĩaku, tondũ nĩ rĩega.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
No rĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe mũndeithia </s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Jakobu 3:16 - 4:3</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, nĩ ũndũ harĩa harĩ ũiru na mĩamũkano, nĩĩho harĩ ngũĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ciĩko ciothe cia waganu. Ĩndĩ ũũgĩ  uumaga Igũrũ o mbere nĩ mũtheru, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningĩ wenda ũiguano, na nĩ ũcayanagĩra, na ndũrĩ ngarari, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningĩ ũkaiyũrũo nĩ tha  o na maciaro  mega, na ndũrĩ ngariũko o na kana </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũhinga. Namo maciaro ma ũthingu nĩmo moimanaga na mahanda ma </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũiguano marĩa mahandagwo nĩ arĩa ateithũrani. Rĩu-rĩ, mbaara na </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũhũrana -rĩ, ciumaga kũ thĩinĩ  wanyu? Githĩ itiumaga o thuti-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cianyu iria irũaga ciĩga-inĩ  cianyu thĩinĩ? Mwĩriragĩria na mũkaaga </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuona: ningĩ mũũraganaga, mũkagĩa na rũitho, na mũtione kĩndũ: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningĩ mũhũranaga na mũkarũa mbaara,
mũgakĩaga kuona </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩndũ tondũ wa kwaga kũhoya.  Mũhoyaga, na mũtiheo, nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũhoyaga na mũhoere ũrĩa ũtaagĩrĩire, no getha mũitangage </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩa mũngĩheo na maũndũ marĩa mwendaga gwĩkenia namo.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Mathayo 11,25</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa, Mwathani wa igũrũ o na wa thĩ, ndakũgatha  nĩ ũndũ nĩ ũhithĩte </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ arĩa ogĩ na imenyi maũndũ macio, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũkamaguũrĩria tũkenge. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 9:30-37</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu na arũmĩrĩri ake makiuma kũu, 
makĩhungura bũrũri </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Galilea; na ndendaga mũndũ amenye. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondũ nĩ kũruta aarutaga arutwo ake ũhoro, akamera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũrũ wa mũndũ nĩ wa kũneanwo  moko-inĩ ma andũ,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao nĩ kũmũũraga makamũũraga; nake aarĩkia kũũragwo, thuutha </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa mĩthenya ĩtatũ nĩ agacoka kũriũka. Nao matiigana gũtaũkĩrũo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ kiugo kĩu, na nĩ metigĩrire kũmũũria. Magĩkinya Kafarnao:</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na aakorũo e nyũmba thĩinĩ akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Nĩ ũhoro ũrĩkũ  mũgũciraga twĩ njĩra? </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao  magĩkira: tondũ nĩ maakararanagia me njĩra atĩ nĩ ũrĩkũ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũnene kũrĩ arĩa angĩ. Nake agĩikara thĩ, agĩĩta arĩa ikũmi na erĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũndũ angĩenda gũtuĩka mbere, nĩ atuĩke wa thutha  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa arĩa angĩ othe, na atuĩke ndungata yao othe.  Akĩrehe kaana, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩkarũgamia gatagatĩ-inĩ kao: na aarĩkia gũkarigicĩria </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>moko make, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũndũ o wothe wa gwĩtĩkĩra  kaana </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kamwe ta gaka nĩ ũndũ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, nĩ niĩ etĩkĩra:</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mũndũ o wothe wanjĩtĩkĩra niĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>to niĩ etĩkĩra, nĩ etĩkĩra  ũrĩa wandekirie.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA ITHANO MWAKA B"},{Guid:"JWfI5fKSBE++Pd+JQbQoPQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA MUGWANJA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Kĩambĩrĩria 2:18-24</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨAMBĨRĨRIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Ngai akiuga atĩrĩ: Ti wega mũndũ ũyũ aikare </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wiki; nĩ ngũmũũmbĩra mũmũteithia o ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maaganĩrĩirũo nake. Na rĩrĩ, Mwathani Ngai ombire </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nyamũ o yothe ya gĩthaka na tĩri, o na nyamũ o yothe ĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩrĩ njoya ya rĩera-inĩ, agĩcoka agĩcitwara ciothe kwĩ mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũcio, nĩguo emenyerere ũrĩa egũciĩta; na rĩrĩ, kĩũmbe o </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gĩothe gĩa icio irĩ muoyo-rĩ,
o rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa mũndũ ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aagĩtuire, rĩu rĩgĩtuĩka rĩtwa rĩakĩo.  Nake mũndũ ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩtua mahiũ mothe marĩĩtwa, 
o na nyamũ iria ii njoya cia </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩera-inĩ, o na nyamũ ciothe cia gĩthaka; no rĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ-rĩ, gũtiakorirũo kwĩ na mũmũteithia maaganĩrĩirũo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake. Nake Mwathani Ngai agĩtũma mũndũ ũcio agwatwo nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>toro mũnene mũno, agĩgĩkoma; ningĩ akĩmũruta rũbaru </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũmwe, agĩcoka agĩcokania nyama hau ruuma, naruo rũbaru rũu </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Ngai aarutire mũndũ ũcio, akĩrũkũmbania  </s></f>"},{ID:18,
