njiguĩra tha.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na andũ aingĩ makĩmũkaania, makĩmwĩra atĩ akire; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake no kwanĩrĩra aacokire kwanagĩrĩra o mũno.  Mũrũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
