Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Mwathani agĩgĩikũrũka arĩ thĩinĩ wa itu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩaria nake, akĩgaya hinya ũmwe wa muoyo ũrĩa aarĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo akĩũhe athuri acio mĩrongo mũgwanja;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ hinya ũcio wa muoyo wake wagĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hamwe nao, makĩratha mohoro, no matiacokire gwĩka </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũguo hĩndĩ ĩngĩ. No rĩrĩ, nĩ haatigarire andũ erĩ maaikarĩte </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩraaro-inĩ, nao ũmwe etagwo Eldad, na ũrĩa ũngĩ Medad, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo hinya ũcio wa muoyo wa Musa ũkĩgĩa nao; nao maarĩ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>a gĩkundi-inĩ gĩa acio maandĩkĩtwo, no rĩrĩ, matiathiĩte </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hema-inĩ ĩo; nao andũ acio makĩratha mohoro maikarĩte </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ro kũu kĩraaro-inĩ. Hagĩgĩteng’era mwanake ũmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ: Eldad na Medad nĩ mararatha mohoro </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>marĩ o kũu kĩraaro-inĩ. Nake Joshua wa Nun, ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>watungatagĩra Musa gwata o rĩrĩa aarĩ mũnyinyi, agĩcokia </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhoro akiuga atĩrĩ: Mwathani wakwa Musa, makaanie.  </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Musa agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Kaĩ ũkũmaiguĩra ũiru nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakwa? Niĩ-rĩ, ndenda makĩria korũo andũ othe a Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ arathi na amahe hinya wa muoyo wake!</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Jakobu 5:1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rĩu-rĩ, ta thikĩrĩriai, itonga ici, rĩrai mũkĩanũkaga  nĩ ũndũ wa mĩthĩnĩko  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩrĩa ĩkamũkora. Ũtonga wanyu nĩ ũbuthĩte, nacio nguo cianyu </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ndĩĩku nĩ memenyi. Nayo thahabu yanyu 
o na betha yanyu </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ĩrotete, nakuo kũrota gwacio nĩkuo gũkamuumbũra ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũtariĩ, na nĩ gũkamumuthũra nyama cia mĩĩrĩ yaanyu  o ta mwaki. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ mwĩĩigĩire mũthithũ o matukũ-inĩ marĩa ma ithirĩro.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atĩrĩrĩ, mũcara wa aruti wĩra arĩa maamũgetheire irio mĩgũnda yanyu,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa mwamaimire na wogogani-rĩ, mũcara ũcio nĩ wanagĩrĩra: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo mũkayo wa agethi acio 
nĩ ũkinyĩte matũ-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ma Mwathani mũnene wa ita.  Inyuĩ-rĩ, mũtũire gũkũ thĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwĩgangarĩte na mũgĩkenagia na indo iria ciothe muonaga,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nacio ngoro cianyu-rĩ, mũtũire mũcituagĩra ta irĩ gĩcegũ, o nginya </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthenya wa gũthĩnjwo. 
Nake mũndũ ũrĩa mũthingu-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ mũmũtuĩrĩire cira hatarĩ kĩhooto, na </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũkamũũragithia; nowe ndamũgiaga.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũgambo waku, Mwathani, nĩ ũma: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtũũmĩrĩrie thĩinĩ wa rwendo rwaku.
Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 9:38-43. 45,47-48</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo, John akĩmwĩra: Mwonania, tũronire mũndũ akĩruta </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ ndaimono na rĩĩtwa rĩaku:
na tũramũkaania, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo ndatwaranaga na ithuĩ.  
Nake Yesu akiuga </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩrĩ: Mũtikamũkaanie:
tondũ gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩĩka </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩko wa hinya na rĩĩtwa rĩakwa, na ahote gũcoka kũmenereria narua. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amu-rĩ, ũrĩa ũtarĩ ũthũ na ithuĩ no witũ.  Amu mũndũ o wothe </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũkamũhe gĩkombe kĩa maaĩ mũnyue, 
nĩ ũndũ mũrĩ a Kristũ, ngũmwĩra </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩrĩrĩ na ma, ũcio ndarĩ ũndũ ũgatũma aage ũtungati </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake. Na mũndũ o wothe ũgatũma twana tũtũ twĩĩhokete kamwe </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gatuo kahĩtie, wega wake no aharũkio ihiga inene rĩa gĩthĩi ngingo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na aikio iria thĩinĩ. Na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ guoko gwaku nĩ gwa gũkũhĩngithia,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũtinie; kaba gũtonya muoyo –inĩ wĩ kĩonje gwĩ gũtonya jeena wĩna </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>moko merĩ, ũtonye mwaki-inĩ ũrĩa ũtangĩhoreka. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ kũgũrũ gwaku nĩ gũkũhĩngithia, gũtinie; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ kaba gũtonya muoyo-inĩ wĩ gĩthua gwĩ gũikio Jeena wĩ na magũrũ merĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na kũngĩtuĩka atĩ riitho rĩaku nĩ rĩa gũkũhĩngithia, rĩkũũre ũrĩte: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ kaba gũtonya ũthamaki-inĩ wa Ngai wĩna riitho rĩmwe gwĩ gũikio </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Jeena wĩna maitho merĩ; kũrĩa kĩgunyũ kĩao gĩtakuaga, naguo mwaki ũtahoraga.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA ITHATHATU MWAKA B"},{Guid:"silx+geNk0ah+WmXmeBIpQ",Verses:[{
