Ezekiel 2:2-5</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI EZEKIELI:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Muoyo wa Ngai agĩtonya thĩ-inĩ wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩndũgamia na magũrũ makwa, 
na niĩ ngĩkĩigua ũcio ũraaria </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na niĩ. Nake agĩkĩnjĩra atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa Mũndũ, nĩkũrekia </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngũkũrekia harĩ ciana cia Israeli, 
ũthiĩ kũrĩ ndũrĩrĩ icio nemu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nacio nĩcio ciagararĩte watho wakwa na ikanema, cio nyene o na </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maithe ma cio, o nginya mũthenya ũyũ tũrĩ; nacio ciana icio nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciĩndĩĩire na ikoma ngoro; nacio nĩcio ndakũrekia harĩ cio, nawe ũciĩre </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai oigĩte ũna na ũna.  Nacio nĩ ikamenya atĩ hoima mũrathi </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩ-inĩ wacio, o na ingĩkũigua kana irege gũkũigua, nĩ ũndũ kĩruka kĩu nĩ kĩremu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                                    Thaburi 123:1-2a;2b;3-4</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee nĩwe ndirĩire maitho, o wee ũikaire thĩ kũu igũrũ. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, O ta ũrĩa maitho ma ndungata maroragĩrĩria guoko  kwa mũthuri ũrĩa ũciathaga.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ta ũrĩa maitho ma mũirĩtu ndungata maroragĩrĩria guoko kwa mũtumia mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no taguo maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ, o nginya agatũkinyĩria wega wake.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tũkinyĩrie wega waku, Mwathani, gĩtũkinyĩrie wega waku, amu tũrĩ ahũnie kĩrario </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kũhũnio. Ngoro ciitũ kũhũna ihũnĩte o mũno ndendwa  cia aria maikaraga </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mearaganĩtie, andũ acio a ngũrũ-rĩ, tũgakĩhũna kĩrario 
kĩao o kũhũna.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Maitho maitũ maroragĩrĩria Mwathani Ngai witũ</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
2 Akorintho 12:7-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, na rĩrĩ, tondũ wa ũrĩa maũndũ macio ndanaguũrĩrio </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maarĩ manene ũũ, nĩguo ndikae gwĩtũũgĩria nĩ ũndũ wamo gũkĩra </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwaagĩra, ndarehithirio ũndũ ũhaaana 
ta mũigua mũnene </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũthecete mwĩrĩ wakwa, ũikarage 
ũrĩ ũrekio wa Chaitani </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>a’tũũkũrage, nĩ getha ndikae gwĩtũũgĩria gũkĩra kwagĩra.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naho ha ũhoro wa ũndũ ũcio, 
nĩ ndathaithire Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mahinda matatũ atĩ aũnjehererie.
Nake ũrĩa aanjĩrire nĩ atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wega wakwa nĩguo ũkũiganĩte, nĩ gũkorũo ũhoti wakwa ũiganagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>harĩa harĩ ũhinyaru. Tondũ ũcio-ri, ndirĩ hingo itarĩĩrahaga nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩa njagĩte hinya nĩ ũndũ wamo, 
ngenete mũno, nĩ getha ũhoti </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Kristũ ũikarage na niĩ.  Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, rĩrĩa ngwaga hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na rĩrĩa ngũrurũkwo, na rĩrĩa nyamarĩkĩte, 
na rĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngũnyarirũo, o na rĩrĩa ngũtuurio 
nĩ ũndũ wa Kristũ,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩrĩo njiguaga o wega, tondũ-rĩ, hĩndĩ </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩrĩa hinyarĩte, nĩyo ngoragwo ndĩ na ũhoti.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 1:14.12</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya. Uuge  ũgĩgĩtuĩka mũndũ na agĩtũũra thĩinĩ witũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No arĩa othe maamwĩtĩkĩrire acio akĩmahotithia gũtuĩka ciana cia Ngai. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 6:1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩthiĩ bũrũri wao; nao arutwo ake makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mũthenya wa thabatũ wakinya akĩgwata kũruta andũ ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thinagoga-inĩ: na andũ aingĩ maamũigua makĩgega, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩũria atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũyũ akĩrutĩte maũndũ maya kũ?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ningĩ makĩũria: Nĩ atĩa ũũgĩ ũyũ mũndũ ũyũ aheetwo; o na ciĩko icio cia </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hinya mũnene ũũ ciĩkĩtwo na moko make?
Ũyũ anga towe </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũtharamara, o we mũrũ wa Maria, na mũrũ wa nyina na Jakobu na Joseph na Juda na Simone?</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao airĩtu a nyina anga matitũire o gũkũ gwitũ? Magĩkĩhingwo nĩ ũndũ wake.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũnabii kũndũ aagaga gũkumio no bũrũri wake, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa andũ ao, na  gwake nyũmba. Agĩkĩremwo nĩ gwĩka wĩko wa hinya kũu,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> tiga nĩ andũ amwe arũaru matarĩ aingĩ aaigĩrĩire moko make, akĩmahonia. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Na nĩ aagegire nĩ ũrĩa maaregete gwĩtĩkia.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu agĩcoka gũceeranga mĩciĩ-inĩ akĩrutaga andũ ũhoro. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IKUMI NA INYA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"bXgqrTIKgUyPZlB2vh7r7w",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TISA (MISSION SUNDAY) MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Isaya 53:10-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ametaka kumponda mtumishi wake kwa mateso:  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amemhuzunisha; amefanya maisha yake kuwa sadaka ya </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>malipo ya dhambi. Naye ataona uzao wake, atazindisha siku</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>zake, nayo mapenzi ya Bwana yatatimia kwa mikono yake; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa ajili ya mateso aliyoyavumilia; yeye ataona </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwangaza, atajaliwa mema; Kwa maarifa yake, mtumishi </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wangu mwema atatakasa wengi, yeye atajitwika maovu yao.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana. 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 33:4-5;18-19;20, 22
 </s></f> 			"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(K)Fadhili zako zikae nasi, ee Bwana; kama vile tunavyokutumainia wewe.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la BWANA ni la kweli;
matendo yake yote ni maaminifu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BWANA apenda unyofu na haki
dunia imejaa wema wake. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(K)Fadhili zako zikae nasi, ee Bwana; kama vile tunavyokutumainia wewe.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Macho ya BWANA yawaelekea wale wamchao,wale wanaotumainia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wema wake, ili aziopoe roho zao katika kifo, na wakati wa njaa awalishe. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(K)Fadhili zako zikae nasi, ee Bwana; kama vile tunavyokutumainia wewe.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nafsi zetu zinamngoja BWANA, yeye ndiye msaada wetu na ngao yetu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Fadhili zako zikae nasi, ee BWANA;kama vile tunavyokutumainia wewe. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(K)Fadhili zako zikae nasi, ee Bwana; kama vile tunavyokutumainia wewe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
Waebrania 4:14-16</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua kwa Waebrania</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa kuwa tuna kuhani mkuu aliyekwisha penya mbingu,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndiye Yesu, Mwana wa Mungu, tuyashikilie maungamo yetu. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana hatuna kuhani mkuu asiyeweza kuonea huruma </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>udhaifu wetu, kwani yeye alijaribiwa kama sisi katika </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mambo yote, ila hakutenda dhambi.  Basi, tukaribie  kiti </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cha neema kwa matumaini, ili tujaliwe  huruma na neema na msaada wakati wa shida.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Marko 10:45</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwana wa Mtu hakuja kutumikiwa, bali kutumikia, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kutoa maisha yake kuwafidia wengi. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Marko 10:35-45</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule: Yakobo na Yohane, wana wawili wa Zebedayo, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walimwendea( Yesu) wakamwambia, “Mwalimu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>twataka utufanyie tutakachokuomba. \"Akawajibu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Mwataka niwafanyie nini?\" Nao wakamjibu,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Utujalie sisi tuketi, mmoja mkono wako wa kuume </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mmoja mkono wako wa kushoto, katika utukufu wako.\"</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akawaambia, \"Hamjui mnachoomba. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwaweza kunywea kikombe nitakachonywea mimi, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>au kubatizwa ubatizo nitakaobatizwa mimi?\" </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakamwambia, \"Twaweza.\"
Yesu akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Kikombe nitakachonywea mimi mtakinywea, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ubatizo nitakaobatizwa mimi mtabatizwa. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini kuketisha watu kuume na kushoto kwangu </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>si katika mamlaka yangu, bali watapewa waliojaliwa.”</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wale kumi wengine waliposikia hayo, walianza kuona </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>chuki juu ya Yakobo na Yohane. Yesu akawaita, akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Mwajua ya kuwa waonekanao kuwa watawala </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa mataifa hutawala kwa nguvu raia wao, na masultani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wao huwatumikisha. Lakini kwenu isiwe hivyo. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bali apendaye kuwa mkubwa wenu, awe mtumishi wenu; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na apendaye kuwa wa kwanza wenu, awe mtumishi wa wote. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa maana Mwana wa mtu hakuja kutumikiwa, bali kutumikia, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kutoa maisha yake kuwafidia wengi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana. 
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)
 </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TISA (MISSION SUNDAY) MWAKA B
"},{Guid:"UjB3JrmhdE+OubwMC3wzjA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Isaia 50:5-9</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Ngai angunũrĩte gũtũ, na niĩ ndirĩ ndamũrema, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana ngacoka na thutha.  Andũ arĩa ahũrani-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ kũhutata ndamahutatĩire ma’hũre, o namo makai </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makwa ngĩmahũgũkĩria andũ arĩa maa’munyaga nderu.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiigana kũhitha ũthiũ wakwa atĩ nĩguo ndigaconorithio </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana ndige gũtuĩrũo mata. Nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani Ngai nĩwe ũkandeithia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tondũ ũcio ndiconorithĩtio; ningĩ nĩ tondũ ũcio ndũmĩte ũthiũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakwa ũikarage uumĩte o ta ihiga rĩa nyaigĩ, ngakĩmenya atĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndigaconorithio. Ningĩ We ũrĩa ũnduaga mũthingu  e hakuhĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nũ ũgagĩtetania na niĩ? Nĩ tũrũgamei ithuerĩ hamwe.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ ũrĩa ũkũnjirithia nĩwe ũrĩkũ? Ta nĩ agĩokoke </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anguhĩrĩrie.  Atĩrĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai nĩwe ũkandeithia; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nũ ũgakĩndua mwĩhia cira-inĩ? Othe nĩ gũkũra magakũra ta nguo; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mathire biũ ta nguo irĩĩkĩte nĩ memenyi.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 116:1-2;3-4;5-6;8-9</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ nyenda Mwathani, tondũ nĩ aiguĩte mũgambo wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agakĩigua ngĩmũthaitha. Kuona nĩ aanyinamĩrĩirie </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũtũ-rĩ, tondũ ũcio, matukũ makwa mothe nĩwe ndĩrĩthathayagia.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nderigicĩirio nĩ mĩgeto ya gĩkuũ, nganyitwo nĩ mĩtandiũko </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kwa-ngoma: nĩ ndonire mĩnyamaro o na kĩeha. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngĩkaĩra rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani, ngiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ Mwathani, ndagũthaitha, hatũra muoyo wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ muuma-andũ, na nĩ mũthingu; ĩĩ-ni, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai witũ nĩ wa matha maingĩ. Mwathani nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amenyagĩrĩra arĩa matarĩ ogĩ: nĩ kũhinyio </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndahinyĩtio, nake agĩkĩ’honokia.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu wee, Mwathani, nĩ ũtharĩte muoyo wakwa gwĩ gĩkuũ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgakĩria maitho makwa maithori, na nĩ ũgirĩtie magũrũ makwa mahigũrũo.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ndiĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mabũrũri-inĩ ma arĩa me muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩĩgendaga ndĩ ũthiũ-inĩ wa Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Jakobu 2:14-18</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, gũkĩrĩ  na uumithio ũrĩkũ, mũndũ angiuga </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ arĩ na wĩtĩkio, no ndarĩ na ciĩko njega ekaga? Ĩ, wĩtĩkio ũcio wakĩhota </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũmũhonokia? Mũrũ wa Ithe witũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ angĩkorũo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩ njaga, na aagĩte irio cia kũrĩa o mũthenya-rĩ, na ũmwe wanyu </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amere atĩrĩ: Thiĩi na ũhoro, mũgote mwaki na mũkarĩe, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũhũne; na ndamahe indo iria mabatairio nĩcio cia mwĩrĩ, gwĩka ũguo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwĩ na uumithio ũrĩkũ? Ũguo na taguo wĩtĩkio, ũtarĩ na ciĩko njega, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mũkuũ guo mwene.  Ĩndĩ hihi mũndũ no kuuga atĩrĩ: wee-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wĩ na wĩtĩkio, na niĩ-rĩ, ndĩ na ciĩko njega; rĩu-rĩ, 
ta kĩnyonie wĩtĩkio waku </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hatarĩ ciĩko njega, na niĩ-rĩ, nĩ ngũkuonia </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wĩtĩkio wakwa nĩ ũrĩa njĩkaga ciĩko njega.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Agalatia 6,14
	</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩroaga kwĩgooca  na ũndũ o wothe, tiga o ndĩĩgocire nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa mũtharaba wa Kristũ, nĩ ũndũ waguo-rĩ,
maũndũ ma </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũkũ thĩ nĩ maambĩtwo mũtharaba nĩguo ma’thengere, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na niĩ ngaambwo mũtharaba nĩguo ndĩmathengere.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 8:27-35</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu akiuma kũu, o na arutwo ake magĩthiĩ mĩciĩ ya Cesarea </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya Filipo: na me njĩra, akĩũria arutwo ake atĩrĩ: 
Andũ manduaga-ũ?  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Kũrĩ moigaga nĩwe John Mũbatithania, na kũrĩ moigaga </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩwe Elia, na ningĩ kũrĩ moigaga nĩwe ũmwe wa arathi.  Agĩcoka akĩmoria: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ inyuĩ mũnduaga-ũ? Nake Petro agĩcokia ũhoro akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee nĩwe Kristũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akĩmakaania matikere mũndũ ũhoro ũcio wake.
Agĩitĩka  kũmaruta atĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũrũ wa mũndũ ndarĩ hingo atakona mathĩna maingĩ, na aregwo nĩ athuri, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na asacerdoti arĩa anene, na aandĩki-marũa, na ningĩ oragwo, na thutha wa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mĩthenya ĩtatũ acoke ariũke. Naguo ũhoro ũcio akĩwaria atekũhitha.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Petro akĩmũtwara ndundu agĩitĩka kũmũkaania.  
Nake akĩĩhũgũra, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ona arutwo ake, agĩkaania Petro, akiuga atĩrĩ: Coka na thutha wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>shaitani: tondũ ndwĩciragia maũndũ ma Ngai, tiga o marĩa ma andũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩcoka agĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ kĩrĩa kĩarĩ ho, o na arutwo ake, akĩmera atĩrĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũndũ ũkwenda kũnũmĩrĩra, nĩ erege, na oe mũtĩ wake wa kwambĩrũo, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anyume thutha.  Amu-rĩ, mũndũ o wothe wendaga gũtũũria muoyo wake, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũcio nĩ kũũrũo akorũo nĩguo; na mũndũ o wothe ũkorũo nĩ muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake nĩ ũndũ wakwa na wa Injiri, ũcio nĩ kũũtũria akaũtũũria.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA INYA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"GaWEUCtugE6Kp9MRx4SCKg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Hekima ya Sulemani 2:12, 17-20</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Hekima ya Sulemani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu wasio na imani walisemezana:] \"Natumvizie </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwenye haki, kwani anatuletea usumbufu; 
maana anapinga </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matendo yetu, pia anayashutumu makosa yetu dhidi ya sheria,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kutulaumu kwa kukosa dhidi ya malezi tuliyopewa. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na tuone kama maneno yake ni kweli;
na tuyachunguze </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yatakayompata katika mwisho wake. Maana mwenye haki </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikiwa ni mwana wa Mungu, Mungu atamsaidia na kumwokoa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika mikono ya wapinzani wake. Tumchunguze kwa jeuri na mateso,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tupate kujua upole wake, na kujaribu ustahimilivu wake. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na tumhukumu kifo cha aibu; maana kadiri ya maneno yake, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hatakosa kujiliwa na ulinzi wa Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 54:3-4, 5, 6 na 8 (K. 6b)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: 
Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Mungu, kwa jina lako unisalimishe.Kwa nguvu yako </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>unifanyie haki. Ee Mungu, usikie sala yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uyasikilize maneno ya kinywa changu. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio:
Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana wageni wamenishambulia;watu wakatili wanaitafuta nafsi yangu;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hawakumweka Mungu mbele ya macho yao. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio:
Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, Mungu ananisaidia, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa moyo mkunjufu nitakutolea sadaka, nitalisifu jina lako, ee Bwana, maana ni jema. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio:
Tazama, Bwana ananitegemeza mimi.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Yakobo 3:16-4:3</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Yakobo</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wapendwa: Kwenye wivu na ubinafsi, ndipo palipo machafuko </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matendo mabaya ya kila namna. Lakini hekima itokayo juu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwanza ni safi, pia ni ya amani, ya hisani, ni tiifu, imejaa huruma </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matendo mema, haina ubaguzi wala unafiki. Kwa wale </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wenye kutunza amani, tunda la uadilifu hupandwa katika amani.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Vita na mapigano kati yenu hutoka wapi? Hutoka wapi isipokuwa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika mapigano ya tamaa zenu mbaya ndani yenu? </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwatamani, na hampati kitu. Mwaua na kuonea wivu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini hamwezi kutimiziwa hamu zenu. Mwapigana na kufanya vita, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini hampati kitu kwa sababu hamwombi. Mnaomba, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini hampewi kitu kwa sababu mnaomba vibaya, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani kwa nia ya kushibisha tamaa zenu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
2 Wathesalonike 2:14</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu ametuita kupitia Injili, kuushiriki utukufu wa Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Marko 9:30-37</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu na wafuasi wake walipita katikati ya Galilaya. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye hakutaka watu wapate habari. Alikuwa akiwafundisha </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wafuasi wake akiwaambia, \"Mwana wa Mtu atatiwa mikononi mwa watu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao watamwua, baada ya siku ya tatu atafufuka.\" </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hawakulifahamu neno hilo, lakini waliogopa kumwuliza.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walifika Kapernaumu na alipokuwa nyumbani, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alianza kuwauliza, \"Njiani mlijadiliana nini?\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini wakanyamaza, kwa maana njiani walikuwa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wamebishana ni nani aliye mkubwa kati yao.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akakaa chini, akawaita wale Kumi na Wawili akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mtu akitaka kuwa wa kwanza, Sharti awe wa mwisho wa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wote na mtumishi wa wote.\" Akatwaa mtoto, akamweka katikati yao, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamkumbatia, akawaambia, “Anayempokea mtoto kama </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huyu kwa jina langu, ananipokea mimi; na anayenipokea </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mimi hanipokei mimi bali anampokea yeye aliyenituma.”</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TANO MWAKA B"},{Guid:"MYwZNUGd9E6xBINfXjDjjg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA INYA KIA lRIUKIRO MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
2 Samuel 7; 1-5, 8-12;14,16</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA SAMUELI WA KEERI</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nagugikinya atiri, ati hindi iria muthamaki Daudi </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aaturire nyumba yake, o nake mwathani agikoruo atumite ahuruke </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatiga guukiriruo ni thu ciake iria ciamurigiciirie na miena yothe-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agikira Nathan, uria munabii, atiri, tarora wone ati riu nii nduraga nyumba </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yakiitwo na mitarakwa, no riri ithanduku ria ngai rutuuraga </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mitamai-ni ma kurihumbira. Nake Nathan agikira muthamaki atiri,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"thii ugeke undu o wothe uria wi ngoro-ini yaku; nigukoruo Mwathani ari hamwe nawe\"</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nagigikinya atiri, ati utuku oro ucio, ndumiriri ya mwathani igikinyirira Nathan,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiruo atiri,\" Thii ukere ndungata yakwa Daudi atiri, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani oiga uu; Atiriri, anga ni wega ujakire nyumba ndimituure? </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atiriri ndakurutire ciuguini cia mburi utige gucirumira, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni getha utuike munene wa gwathaga andu akwa israel; </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ni njikarite hamwe nawe kundu guothe wanathii, na ni ninite thu ciaku ciothe, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikehera mbere yaku, na ngatuma ugie na igweta muno o ta andu a guku </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thi aria mari igweta muno. Nao andu akwa Israel ningumathurira handu </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndimahande ho nigetha matuurage handu hao kiumbe, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matigacoke guthamio ringi o na ri; </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana ciana iria njaganu icoke kumanyarira o na atia, o ta uria ciekaga tene, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ta uria gwatarii kuuma muthenya uria ndathanire ngiuga </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ati atiiririri bururi matuike agutongoria andu akwa Israeli</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ni ngukuhurukia,utige kunyarirwo ni thu ciaku ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ona nigi Mwathani egukwira atiri, ati mwathani ni akahanda nyumba yaku. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riri, hindi iria matuku maku makahingio nawe ukome hamwe na mathoguo, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningahanda mbeu yaku iria igoka thutha waku, yumite muthirimo waku; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o naguo uthamaki wake ningatuma urume muno.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ningatuika ithe, nake atuike muru wakwa. Na ruo ruciarwo rwaku, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na uthamaki waku, ni ukona ihanditwo igatuura irumite muno, nginya tene;  </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o naguo uhoro waku wa guikarira git gia uthamaki </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni ukahandwo utuure urmite wega tene na tene</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiugo kia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERWO 
Thaburi 89;1-2, 3-4, 26; 28</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Motugi ma Mwathani ni ngutura ndimainagira o nginya tene</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kanua gakwa menyithanagie kwihokeka gwaku nako nginya njiarwa na njiarwa</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni amu njugite atiri, utugi-ri ni gwakwo uriakagwo o nginya mindi na mindi: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee wihokeku waku ugutuura urumitie o kuu iguru</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Motugi ma Mwathani ni ngutura ndimainagira o nginya tene</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nii-ri, ni ndikaniire na muthurwo wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndungata yakwa Daudi ni kwihita ndihitiite ngamirikiria atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mbeu yaku ningumituria ii nomu o nginya tene ma tene, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngiake giti giaku kia unene gikinyagirie njiarua na njiarua.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Motugi ma Mwathani ni ngutura ndimainagira o nginya tene</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We ariitanaga na kuri nii ta uu: Wee niwe awa, nowe Ngai wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ndomba ya ihiga ira nyene uhonokio wakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utugi wakwa ngutura ndiururumiirie kinya o tene, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nakio kirikaniro giakwa gituure kiri o gia kwihokeka niwe</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Motugi ma Mwathani ni ngutura ndimainagira o nginya tene</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI 
Aroma 18: 25-27</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A ROMA</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariu a Ithe witu, na riri, Ngai niwe uhotaga kumwikira </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hinya na njira iria nyonanie ni uhoro uria mwega hunjagia,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o uria wa kwaniririra uhoro wa Yesu Kristu, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na niguo uringaine na kuguoranirio kwa uhoro wa hitho uria watuire </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uhithitwo ugaikara uguo mahinda maria ma mindi na mindi naguo riu ni </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kumirio umiritio, na kuringana na uria Ngai, we uturaga tene na tene athanire-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni umenyithagio andu a nduriri ciothe na maandiko maria ma anabii, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni getha matuike aathiku uhoro-ini wa witikia. nake we Ngai,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we wiki muugi-ri, arotuura agocagwo na njira ya Yesu Kristu </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nginya tene na tene. Ni gutuike guo</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RWA INJIRI
Luka 1: 38</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluia. Aleluia
One ndungata ya Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni njikwo o ta uria woiga. 
Aleluia</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJIRI
Luka 1:26-38</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHERU LUKA </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io Muraika Gabrieli agitumwo ni Ngai itüûıra-ini ria Nazareth, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bürüri wa Galilea, kwi muiritu wetagwo Maria woritio ni mundu wa nyumba ya </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Daudi wetagwo Joseph, na Muraika atonya kwa muiritu akimwirwa: </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningukugeithia, we muiyure ni wega; 
Mwathani ari nawe, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we urimurathime thi-ini wa aka othe Maria aigua ndeto icio no kimako, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na agiikara agithugunda ngeithi icio uria ithiite; nake Muraika agicokia: </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugetigire, Maria amu ni wonire wega wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na niundu hau ni ukagia nda na uciare mwana ukamutua Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ucio ni agatwika Muenene, na ni agetwo mwana wa munene-ma. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai ni akamunengera unene wa Daudi ithe wake na ni agathana mucii-ini wa Jakubu </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hindi ciothe, na unene wake ndugathira. Maria agicokeria Muraika: </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uhoro ugathii atia na nii itoe mundurume. Muraika agicokia: </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo Mutheru ni ugaikuruka iguru riaku, na hinya wa Ngai ni ugakuhumbira; </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niundu uria ugaciarwo ni we ni Muthure, na agatuo Mwana wa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>One mugendiguo Elisabeth nake ni agiire nda, o na ari mukuru uguo, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mweri uyu turi niguo wa itandatu ari na nda, undu areragwo ni thata; </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni gukorwo gutiri undu ungirema Ngai. Maria nake akiuga:</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>one ndungata ya Mwathani ni njikuo o ta uria woiga. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Muraika akimweherera agithii. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri Theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA INYA KIA lRIUKIRO MWAKA B"},{Guid:"aaibd7ppPUCjb+d4U5izrg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA ITHATU KIA MWAKA B GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE				                            Jonah 3:1-5.10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA KĨRORI JONAH:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Nayo ndũmĩrĩri ya Mwathani ĩgĩcoka ĩgĩkinyĩra Jonah rĩa kerĩ, akĩĩrũo atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũkĩra ũthiĩ Nineve, itũũra rĩrĩa inene, ũrĩgũtũkĩre ũrĩhunjĩrie ũhoro o ũrĩa ngũkwĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Nake Jonah agĩgĩũkĩra agĩthiĩ Nineve, kũringana na ũhoro ũcio wa Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Na rĩrĩ, itũũra rĩu rĩa Nineve rĩarĩ inene mũno, rĩa kũnina matukũ matatũ rĩgĩgatuĩkanĩka.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Jonah akĩambĩrĩria gũtonya itũũra rĩu, agĩthiĩ itĩĩna rĩa mũthenya ũmwe,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> agĩkĩanĩrĩra akiuga atĩrĩ: No matukũ mĩrongo ĩna matigaire gũkũ Nineve kũhang’ũranio! Nao andũ acio a Nineve magĩgĩĩtĩkia Ngai; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩanĩrĩrithia atĩ kũgĩe hĩndĩ ya kwĩima irio, na makĩĩhumba nguo cia makũnia,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kuuma o ũrĩa mũnene wao othe o kinya ũrĩa mũnyinyi wao othe.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Ngai akĩona ciĩko icio ciao atĩ nĩ maathengeire mĩthiĩre yao mĩũru;</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ningĩ Ngai agĩkĩĩricũkwo agĩtiga ũũru ũrĩa oigĩte ekũmeka; na ndaigana kũwĩka.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani  THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                              Thaburi 25:4-5ab;6-7b;8-9</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Menyithia njĩra ciaku , Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>1.Menyithia njĩra ciaku, Mwathani; ndutaga ikĩro ciaku, ndĩimenye. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ndwaragĩra o ũhoro-
inĩ waku wa ma, o ũkĩndutaga; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo wee nĩwe Ngai mwene ũhonokio wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Menyithia njĩra ciaku , Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>2.Ririkana matha maku, o nayo mĩtuganĩre yaku, Mwathani; nĩ amu ndĩrĩ yaaga o kuuma
 tene.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ndirikana kũringana o na ũguo ũtugi waku ũtariĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa wega waku, wee Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Menyithia njĩra ciaku , Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>3.Mwathani nĩ mwega, o na nĩ mũrũngĩrĩru: tondũ ũcio, arĩa mahĩtĩtie, nĩ arĩmonagĩrĩria </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> njĩra.  Arĩa ahoreri arĩmatwaraga na mĩthiĩre o ĩrĩa ya kĩhooto: acio ahoreri-rĩ, nĩ kũruta arĩmarutaga mũgerere wa njĩra yake.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA Menyithia njĩra ciaku, Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:13,
