Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũrĩa nguuga, ariũ a Ithe witũ, nĩ atĩrĩ, nĩ atĩ hingo nĩ ĩnyihĩte; kuuma rĩu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ arĩa me na atumia nĩ maikarage ta matarĩ nao, na andũ arĩa marĩraga maikarage ta matekũrĩra, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na arĩa makenaga maikarage ta mategũkena; nao arĩa megũragĩra indo maikarage ta matagĩĩte nacio,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na arĩa mahũthagĩra maũndũ ma gũkũ thĩ maikarage ta matekũmahũthĩra mũno;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nĩ gũkorũo mũtabarĩre wa thĩ ĩno nĩ gũthira ũrathira.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI							    Aefeso 1:17-18		
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wa Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ, o we Ithe witũ mwene riri, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amũhe o mũndũ muoyo wa kũmũũhĩgia, nĩ getha mũmenye wega kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro kĩrĩa mwĩtĩirũo nĩwe mũgĩe nakĩo.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluia</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			         Mark 1:14-20</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thutha wa John aarĩkia kũnyitwo, Yesu agĩkinya bũrũri wa Galilea </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiumbũraga Injiri ya Ngai, akiugaga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hingo nĩ ĩhingĩte, naguo ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩ ũkuhĩrĩirie:  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩrirei, na mwĩtĩkie Injiri. Na rĩrĩa aathiaga rũtere </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rũa iria rĩa Galilea nĩ onire Simone na Andrea, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩwe mũrũ wa nyina na Simone, akĩmona makĩrekia rũgara </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rũnene rũa ndigi iria-inĩ; amu maarĩ atahi a ciũngũyũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ: Ũkai mũnyume thutha, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩ ngatũma mũtuĩke atahi a andũ.  Nao magĩtiga </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngara ciao cia ndigi o ihinda o rĩu, makĩmuuma thutha.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ningĩ aathianga hanini, akĩona Jakobu wa Zebedeo na mũrũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nyina wetagwo John,
marĩ marikabu thĩinĩ o nao, magĩthondeka </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngara ciao harĩa ciatuĩkĩte. 
O rĩmwe akĩmeta: nao magĩtiga Ithe wao Zebedeo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũu marikabu thĩinĩ hamwe na ndungata iria cia wĩra, makĩmuuma thutha.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
