Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE	 Thama 20:1-17</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Ngai akĩaria mohoro maya mothe, akiuga atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani Ngai waku ũrĩa wakũrutire bũrũri wa Misiri, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o nyũmba-inĩ ya ũkombo. Ndũkanagĩe na ngai ĩngĩ tiga niĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndũkanethondekere 
mũhianano mwacũhie, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana mũhianĩre wa  
kĩndũ o gĩothe  gĩĩ kũrĩa Igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana wa kĩndũ gĩĩ gũkũ thĩ, maaĩ-inĩ marĩa mee mũhuro wa thĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndũkanaciinamĩrĩre ka ũcitũngatĩre; nĩ gũkorũo niĩ Mwathani Ngai waku </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndĩ Ngai wĩ ũiru, ngagĩkinyĩria ciana waganu wa maithe, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nginya rũciaro rwa gatatũ na rũa kana rũa andũ arĩa mathũire;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
