wa thabatũ ũwamũrage.  </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Rutaga wĩra mĩthenya ĩtandatũ, ũgeka maũndũ maku mothe;</s></f>"},{ID:13,
