Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthenya ũcio ndũkanarute wĩra o na ũrĩkũ, wee mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana mũrũguo,Kana mwarĩguo, kana ndungata yaku ya mũndũ mũrũme,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana ya mũndũ-wa-nja, 
kana ũhiũ  waku, kana 
mũgeni ũrĩa ũrĩ gwaku mũciĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani 
ombire igũrũ na thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na iria rĩrĩa rĩnene, 
o na indo ciothe iria irĩ kuo </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mĩthenya ĩtandatũ; 
akĩhurũka mũthenya wa mũgwanja;</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũndũ ũcio Mwathani 
akĩrathima mũthenya </s></f>"},{ID:20,
