Yesu</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai , tondũ wa ũrĩa endete kĩrĩndĩ gĩa gũkũ thĩ, nĩ aarutire Mũrũ wake wa mũmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩhokete ndakore, 
no agĩe muoyo wa tene na tene.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                    
John 2:13-25</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na rĩrĩ, Paska ya Ayahudi nĩ yatuĩte gũkinya, nake Yesu akĩambata Jerusalem. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na kũu hekarũ-inĩ agĩkora andũ arĩa mendagia ng’ombe na ng’ondu  na ndutura,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ona arĩa maakũũranagĩria  andũ mbia maikaire thĩ kuo: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩthondeka mũcarica  na mĩkanda, 
akĩmarutũrũra kũu hekarũ othe,  o </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ng’ondu na ng’ombe;
o nacio mbeca cia arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maahunjithagia mbia agĩciita thĩ, na akĩgũithia metha ciao; akĩĩra arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mendagia ndutura atĩrĩ;: Umiai ici gũkũ; tigai gũtua nyũmba ya Awa nyũmba ya thogora.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao arutwo ake makĩririkana atĩ nĩ haandĩke atĩrĩ: Nĩ kĩyo kĩrĩa ndĩ nakĩo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩa nyũmba yaku gĩkandĩa. Nao Ayahundi magĩgĩcokia makĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rĩu-rĩ tondũ ũreka maũndũ maya-rĩ,
kĩmenyithia nĩ kĩrĩkũ ũgũtuonia? </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu agĩcokia ũhoro akĩmera: 
Thariai hekarũ ĩno, na mĩthenya ĩtatũ</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ngamĩcokia igũrũ. Nao Ayahundi magĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Nyũmba ĩno-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩninĩte mĩaka mĩrongo ĩna na ĩtandatũ ĩgĩakwo nawe gĩthiĩ ũkamĩcokia igũrũ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mĩthenya  ĩtatũ ĩrĩĩke? No we nĩ hekarũ ya mwĩrĩ wake aagwetaga. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na tondũ ũcio aarĩkia kũriũkio akoima kwĩ arĩa akuũ, arutwo  ake </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magĩkĩririkana atĩ nĩ oigire ũguo; 
magĩgĩĩtĩkia ũhoro ũrĩa mwandĩke, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kiugo kĩu Yesu oigire. 
Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩo aarĩ kũu Jerusalem </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Paska-inĩ hĩndĩ ya gĩathĩ, 
andũ aingĩ makĩaga kwĩhoka </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩĩtwa rĩake mona ciama ciake iria ekaga. No Yesu we ndaigana kwĩhoka ũhoro wao, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo nĩ oĩ andũ othe, na tondũ ndaabataragio nĩ kuumbũrĩrũo ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa mũndũ; amu we mwene 
nĩ oĩ ngoro ciao.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.
(NI TWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU) </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
