2 Timotheo 1:10</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.  				Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwokozi wetu Kristo Yesu ameishinda mauti na ametangaza uzima wa milele kwa Injili.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI 									Marko 10:46-52</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu alipokuwa anatoka tena Yeriko pamoja na wafuasi wake na umati wa watu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bartimayo, yaani mwana wa Timayo, mtu kipofu, alikaa kando ya njia akiomba.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naye aliposikia ya kwamba ni Yesu Mnazareti, alianza kuita kwa sauti kubwa, akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Yesu, Mwana wa Daudi, unirehemu.” Wengi wakamkemea  ili anyamaze. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Lakini alizidi kupaza sauti na kuita, “Mwana wa Daudi, unirehemu.”</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akasimama, akasema, “Mwiteni.” Wakamwita kipofu wakimwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Jipe moyo; simama anakuita.” Akatupa vazi lake, akaruka, akasimama, akamwendea Yesu.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akamwuliza, “Wataka nikufanyie nini?” Kipofu akajibu, “Mwalimu, nipate kuona tena.”</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Yesu akamwambia, “Nenda, imani yako imekuponya.” Mara akaona, akamfuata njiani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili takatifu ya Bwana
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
