Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Ezekieli</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Roho ikaniingia, kama nilivyoambiwa, ikanisimamisha, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nikamsikia mwenye kusema nami. Akaniambia: \"Mwana wa mtu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nakutuma kwa wana wa lsraeli, kwa taifa la waasi walioniasi mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpaka siku ya leo, wao na baba zao wamenikataa mimi, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wana hawa wana nyuso kaidi na mioyo migumu, ninakutuma </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwao, nawe utawaambia: Bwana Mungu amesema hivi.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao wakisikiliza, au wakikataa kusikiliza - maana wao </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni taifa lenye kuasi- watatambua kuna nabii katikati yao.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
