Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Macho yetu yamwelekea Bwana, Mungu wetu, mpaka atuonee huruma.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninainua macho yangu kwako,
wewe uketiye mbinguni.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama vile macho ya watumishi
kwa mkono wa bwana wao. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Macho yetu yamwelekea Bwana, Mungu wetu, mpaka atuonee huruma.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama vile macho ya mjakazi, kwa mkono wa bibi yake, ndivyo macho </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yetu yamwelekeavyo Bwana Mungu wetu mpaka atuonee huruma. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Macho yetu yamwelekea Bwana, Mungu wetu, mpaka atuonee huruma.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utuhurumie, ee Bwana, utuhurumie sisi, kwani tumeshiba sana dharau.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nafsi zetu zimeshibishwa sana mzaha wa wenye majivuno, na dharau ya wenye kiburi. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Macho yetu yamwelekea Bwana, Mungu wetu, mpaka atuonee huruma.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
2 Wakorintho 12:7-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Kusudi ukubwa wa ufunuo usinitie majivuno, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nimepatwa na mwiba mwilini, yaani mjumbe wa Shetani,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anipige makofi, nisije nikajivuna. Kwa hiyo nilimwomba Bwana mara tatu unitoke.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye akaniambia: \"Neema yangu yakutosha, maana nguvu hukomaa katika udhaifu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, napenda kujisifia udhaifu wangu, ili nguvu ya Kristo ikae </s></f>"},{ID:7,
