Yohana 3; 16</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Jinsi hii Mungu aliupenda ulimwengu, hata akamtoa Mwanawe </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa pekee, ili kila mtu amsadikiye asipotee, bali awe na uzima wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
