Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Pasaka ya Wayahudi ilikuwa imekaribia. Yesu akapanda kwenda Yerusalemu. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akaona pale hekaluni watu wakiuza ng'ombe, kondoo, na njiwa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>pia wabadilisha fedha wamekaa mezani pao. Akafanya mjeledi kwa kamba,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akawafukuza wote katika hekalu pamoja na kondoo na ng'ombe. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akamwaga fedha za wabadilisha fedha,
akapindua meza zao, akawaambia wauza njiwa,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Ondoeni vitu hivi, msiifanye nyumba ya Baba yangu kuwa nyumba ya biashara.\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wafuasi wake wakakumbuka ya kuwa imeandikwa,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Wivu wa nyumba yako utanila.\"  Hapo Wayahudi wakamrudia na kumwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Je, utaweza kutuonyesha ishara gani inayokuruhusu kufanya hayo?\" </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akajibu, akawaambia, \"Livunjeni hekalu hili,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nami nitalijenga tena kwa siku tatu”  Wayahudi wakamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Miaka arobaini na sita ilitakiwa kujenga hekalu hili, na wewe utalijenga kwa siku tatu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini yeye alikuwa anazungumzia hekalu la mwili wake. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Baada ya ufufuko wake katika wafu, wafuasi wake wakakumbuka ya kuwa alisema hayo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na wakayasadiki
maandiko na maneno aliyokuwa ameyasema Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>alipokuwa Yerusalemu kwa sikukuu ya Pasaka, watu wengi walisadiki jina lake </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walipoziona ishara alizozifanya. Lakini Yesu mwenyewe hakuwa na imani nao, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa maana aliwafahamu wote, wala hakuhitaji ushuhuda wa mtu yeyote, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa maana aliyajua yaliyomo ndani ya mtu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
