Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kufedheheshwa.                         
Hakika, aliyachukua mateso yetu, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na alijitwika huzuni zetu. Sisi lakini, tulidhani ameadhibiwa na Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kupigwa naye, na kuteswa. lla aliumizwa kwa sababu ya makosa yetu,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alipondwa kwa ajili ya maovu yetu. Alibeba adhabu iletayo uzima juu yetu, tumeponywa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa vidonda vyake. Wote kama kondoo, tulitangatanga, kila mmoja akienda njia</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yake basi, Bwana ameweka juu yake yeye maovu yetu sisi sote.  Alionewa vikali sana,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> akanyenyekea wala hakufunua kinywa chake; kama mwanakondoo anayepelekwa machinjoni,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na kama vile kondoo anyamazavyo mbele yao wakatao manyoya yake vivyo hivyo hakufumbua kinywa chake.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alishikwa kwa nguvu na kuhukumiwa; Ni nani atasimulia maisha yake?</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kweli, walimwondoa kutoka nchi ya walio hai, aliuawa kwa ajili ya makosa ya watu wake. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walimpa kaburi pamoja na waovu, na pamoja na matajiri katika kifo chake, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ingawa hakutenda ukatili wowote, wala haukupatikana udanganyifu wowote Kinywani mwake.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ametaka kumwumiza mtumishi wake kwa mateso amemhuzunisha; </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amefanya maisha yake kuwa sadaka ya malıpo ya dhambi,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> naye ataona uzao wake, ataishi siku nyingi, nayo mapenzi ya Bwana yatatimia kwa mikono yake.  </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa ajili ya mateso aliyoyavumilia; yeye ataona mwangaza, atajaliwa mema; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maarifa yake, mtumishi wangu mwema atatakasa watu wengi, yeye atajitwika maovu yao.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiyo maana, nitamgawia sehemu kati ya wakuu wa watu, atagawanya nyara pamoja nao walio hodari,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
