mauti, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani mauti ya msalabani. Kwa sababu hiyo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu alimtukuza, akampa jina lipitalo kila jina.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sifa na utukufu kwako, ee Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 18:1-19:42</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwenye simulizi hili la mateso: 
M - Msomaji;  </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* = maneno ya Yesu; 
W. = maneno ya watu mbali mbali.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>MATESO YA BWANA WETU YESU KRISTU</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yalivyoandikwa na Mtakatifu Yohane. (Ijumaa Kuu)</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Wakati ule: Yesu aliondoka pamoja na wafuasi wake, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwenda ng'ambo ya kijito Kidroni, pale palikuwa na bustani,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaingia yeye na wafuasi wake. Kadhalika Yuda, yule aliyemsaliti, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alijua mahali pale, kwa maana mara nyingi Yesu alikusanyika </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huko pamoja na wafuasi wake. Basi, Yuda alipokea kikosi cha </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>askari na walinzi waliotumwa na makuhani wakuu na Mafarisayo, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaenda huko, walishika mienge, na taa, na silaha mikononi. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akijua yote yatakayompata, 
akatoka, akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Mnamtafuta nani?\"
M. Wao wakamjibu,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Yesu Mnazareti.\"
M. Yesu akawaambia,
* \"MIMI NDIYE.\"</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Yuda aliyemsaliti alisimama pamoja nao. Alipowaambia, \"MIMI NDIYE,\" </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>walirudi nyuma, wakaanguka chini. Akawauliza tena,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Mnamtafuta nani?\"
M. Wakasema,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Yesu Mnazareti.\"
M. Yesu akajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Nimekwisha kuwaambia ya kwamba MIMI NDIYE. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, ikiwa mnanitafuta mimi, waacheni hawa waende zao.\"</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Hayo alisema, ili neno lake litimie, yaani:</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> \"Sikumpoteza hata mmoja wa hao ulionipa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi Simoni Petro alikuwa na upanga, akauchomoa, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akampiga mtumishi wa kuhani mkuu, akamkata sikio la kulia. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na yule mtumishi jina lake ni Malko. Yesu akamwambia Petro,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Rudisha upanga alani mwake.
Je, nisinywe kikombe alichonipa Baba?\"</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Hapo kikosi cha askari na jemadari wake na walinzi wa </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wayahudi walimkamata Yesu, wakamfunga, na wakampeleka </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwanza kwa Anasi. Maana huyo alikuwa mkwewe Kayafa, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye alikuwa kuhani mkuu wa mwaka ule. Kayafa huyo ndiye </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliyewapa Wayahudi shauri kwamba yafaa mtu mmoja afe kwa ajili ya taifa.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Petro na mfuasi mwingine wakamfuata Yesu. Huyo mfuasi </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwingine alijulikana na kuhani mkuu, akaingia pamoja na Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika ukumbi wa kuhani mkuu. Lakini Petro alisimama nje karibu na mlango.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Basi, yule mfuasi mwingine, aliyejulikana na kuhani mkuu, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akatoka akasema na mngoja mlango, akamleta Petro ndani. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kijakazi huyo aliyekuwa mngoja mlango, akamwambia Petro,</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Je, wewe si mmojawapo wa wafuasi wa mtu huyu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Naye akasema,
W. \"Si mimi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Watumishi na walinzi walisimama huko na walikuwa wamewasha moto </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa makaa, maana kulikuwa baridi nao wakaota moto. Na Petro pia </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alisimama nao akiota moto. Kuhani mkuu akamhoji Yesu juu ya wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake na mafundisho yake. Yesu akamjibu,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Mimi nilisema wazi wazi mbele ya wote. Siku zote nilifundisha katika </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sinagogi na hekaluni  wanapokutana Wayahudi wote, kwa siri sikusema neno. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ya nini kuniuliza mimi? Waulize wale waliosikia niliyowafundisha. Bila shaka wanajua niliyosema.”</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Aliposema hayo, mmoja wa mlinzi aliyesimama karibu alimpiga Yesu kofi akisema,</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Wamjibu hivyo kuhani mkuu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Yesu akamjibu,* \"Kama nimesema vibaya, ushuhudie huo ubaya; </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali kama nimesema vema, mbona unanipiga?\"</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Hapo Anasi alimpeleka hali amefungwa kwa Kayafa, kuhani mkuu.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simoni Petro alisimama huko akiota moto. Basi, wakamwuliza,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Je, wewe si mmoja wa wafuasi wake?\"</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Naye akakana, akasema,
W. \"Si mimi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Mtumishi mmoja wa kuhani mkuu, ndiye jamaa wa yule aliyekatwa sikio na Petro, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Je, mimi sikukuona pamoja naye bustanini?\"</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Petro akakana tena. Mara hapo jogoo akawika. Kutoka kwa Kayafa </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>walimpeleka Yesu praitorio. 
Kulikuwa asubuhi mapema. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wenyewe hawakuingia praitorio, wasije wakajinajisi, maana walitaka </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuila Pasaka. Basi, Pilato akawaendea nje, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Mnaleta mashtaka gani juu ya mtu huyu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Wakajibu, wakamwambia,
W. \"Kama huyu asingekuwa </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtenda maovu tusingemleta kwako.\"
M. Pilato akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Haya! Mchukueni ninyi, mkamhukumu kwa sheria yenu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Wayahudi wakamjibu,
W \"Sisi hatuna ruhusa ya kumwua mtu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Hivyo maneno aliyoyasema Yesu kuonyesha namna ya kifo chake yalipata kutimia. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, Pilato akaingia tena katika praitorio, akamwita Yesu, akamwuliza,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W \"Je, wewe u Mfalme wa Wayahudi?\"
M. Yesu akajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Unasema hivi kwa nafsi yako, au ni watu wengine waliokupa habari yangu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Pilato akajibu,
W. \"Ni Myahudi mimi? Ni taifa lako na </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makuhani wakuu waliokuleta
kwangu. Umefanya nini?\"</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Yesu akajibu,
* \"Ufalme wangu si wa ulimwengu huu. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama ufalme wangu ungekuwa wa ulimwengu huu, watumishi wangu </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wangenipigania, nisije nikatolewa kwa Wayahudi. Lakini ufalme wangu si wa hapa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Basi Pilato akamwambia,
W. \"Wewe u mfalme, basi?\"</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Yesu akajibu,
* \"Wewe unasema ya kuwa, mimi ni mfalme. </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nia ya kuzaliwa mimi na nia ya kuja ulimwenguni mimi ndiyo nishuhudie ukweli.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila aliye wa ukweli husikia sauti yangu.\"
M. Pilato akamwuliza,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Ukweli ni nini?\"
M. Baada ya maneno hayo, alikwenda </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena nje kwa Wayahudi, akawaambia,
W. \"Mimi sioni kosa kwake. </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini kuna desturi kwenu niwafungulie mfungwa mmoja kwa Sikukuu ya Pasaka.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Je, mwataka niwafungulie mfalme wa Wayahudi?\"
M. Wakapiga kelele na kusema,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Si huyu, bali Baraba!\"
M. Na Baraba alikuwa mnyang'anyi. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo Pilato alimtwaa Yesu,
akampiga mijeledi. Nao askari wakasuka </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>taji la miiba, wakamtia k</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ị</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>chwani, wakamvisha joho la zambarau, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamjongea, wakisema,
W. \"Salaam, mfalme wa Wayahudi!\"</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Wakampiga makofi. Kisha Pilato akaenda tena nje, akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Tazameni, ninamleta nje, mpate kutambua ya kuwa sioni kosa kwake.\"</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Hapo Yesu alitoka nje amevaa taji la miiba kichwani na lile joho la zambarau. </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pilalo akawaambia,
W. \"Mtazameni mtu!</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Makuhani wakuu na watumishi walipomwona, walipiga kelele,</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Msulibishe! Msulibishe!\"
M. Pilato akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Mchukueni ninyi wenyewe, 
mkamsulibishe. Kwa maana mimi sioni kosa kwake.”</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Wayahudi wakamjibu,
W. \"Sisi tuna sheria, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa kadiri ya sheria hiyo amestahili kufa, kwa sababu amejidai kuwa Mwana wa Mungu.”</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Pilato aliposikia hayo, akazidi kuogopa, akaingia tena praitorio, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamwambia Yesu,
W. \"Umetoka wapi?\"</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Yesu hakumjibu. Pilato akamwuliza,
W. \"Husemi nami? Hujui ya kuwa nina </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mamlaka ya kukufungua, na nina mamlaka ya kukusulibisha?”</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Yesu akamjibu,
* “Usingekuwa na mamlaka yoyote juu </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yangu mimi, kama usingepewa kutoka juu. 
Kwa hiyo yeye aliyenitia </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mikononi mwako ana kosa kubwa zaidi.\"
M. Toka hapa, Pilato akajaribu kumfungua; </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini Wayahudi wakapiga kelele wakisema,</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Ukimfungua huyu, wewe si rafiki wa Kaisari. Kila mtu ajifanyaye mfalme anamuasi Kaisari.\"</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Pilato aliposikia maneno hayo akamleta Yesu nje na akaketi katika kiti cha hukumu,</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mahali paitwapo Sakafu ya Mawe, au kwa Kiebrania, Gabbatha.</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ilikuwa siku ya maandalio ya Pasaka, mnamo saa sita. Akawaambia Wayahudi,</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Tazameni, mfalme wenu!”
M. Nao wakapaza sauti,</s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Mwondoshe! Mwondoshe! Msulibishe!\"
M. Pilato akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Je, nimsulibishe mfalme wenu?”
M. Makuhani wakuu wakajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Sisi hatuna mfalme ila Kaisari.\"
M. Hapo Pilato alimtoa kwao ili asulibiwe. </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao wakamchukua Yesu, naye mwenyewe alichukua msalaba njiani toka mjini mpaka </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mahali paitwapo Fuvu la Kichwa, 
au kwa Kiebrania Golgotha.</s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huko wakamsulibisha, na pamoja 
naye wengine wawili,mmoja kushoto </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mmoja kulia, na Yesu katikati. Pilato akaandika hati, akaiweka juu ya msalaba.</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ilikuwa imeandikwa,  “Yesu Mnazareti, Mfalme wa Wayahudi.”</s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wayahudi wengi walisoma hati hiyo, maana aliposulibiwa Yesu palikuwa karibu na mji;</s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lugha ya hati ilikuwa Kiebrania, Kilatini, na Kigiriki. Makuhani wakuu wa Wayahudi wakamwambia Pilato,</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Usiandike, \"Mfalme wa Wayahudi,' bali ya kwamba alisema, ‘Mimi ni Mfalme wa</s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wayahudi.”’
M. Pilato akajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. \"Niliyoandika nimeyaandika.\"
M. Baada ya kumsulibisha Yesu,</s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>askari waliyachukua mavazi yake, wakafanya mafungu manne, </s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kila askari fungu moja
Pia walichukua kanzu;</s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nayo kanzu ilikuwa nzima bila mshono, yaani mfumo mmoja toka juu mpaka chini. </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, wakaambiana,
W. \"Tusipasue, afadhali tuipigie kura na </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hivyo kuamua itakuwa ya nani,”
M. Kwa namna hii yalitimia Maandiko yasemayo:</s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Waligawanya nguo zangu, wakalipigia kura vazi langu. \"Hayo ndiyo waliyofanya askari.</s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Karibu na msalaba wa Yesu walisimama mama yake, na ndugu wa mama yake, </s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maria mke wa Klopa, na Maria Magdalena. Basi, Yesu alipomwona mama yake, </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na karibu naye mfuasi aliyempenda, alimwambia mama yake, </s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>* \"Mama, tazama mwanao.”
M. Kisha akamwambia mfuasi,
* “Tazama mama yako.”</s></f>"},{ID:103,
