Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>M. Huko kulikuwako chombo kilichojaa siki.</s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Basi, wakalowesha sifongo katika siki, wakaipachika  kwenye mwanzi, </s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakakigusa kinywa chake. Baada ya kuipokea siki, </s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alisema,
* “Yametimia.”
M. Akainama kichwa, akatoa roho.</s></f>"},{ID:109,
