Lakini walipomjia Yesu na kumwona amekwisha kufa, </s></f>"},{ID:115,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hawakumvunja miguu, ila askari 
mmojawapo alimchoma ubavu kwa mkuki,</s></f>"},{ID:116,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mara ikatoka damu na maji. Aliyeona hayo, ameyashuhudia, na ushuhuda wake ni kweli; </s></f>"},{ID:117,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye anajua ya kuwa anasema kweli, ili ninyi pia mpate kusadiki.</s></f>"},{ID:118,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana hayo yametendeka, ili andiko litimie lisemalo: \"Hatavunjwa mfupa hata mmoja. \" </s></f>"},{ID:119,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tena andiko lingine lasema:  \"Watamtazama yule waliyemchoma.\"</s></f>"},{ID:120,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya hayo, Yosefu wa Arimathea, ndiye mfuasi wa Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:121,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini mfuasi wa siri kwa kuwaogopa Wayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:122,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alimwomba Pilato ruhusa auondoe mwili wa Yesu. Pilato akampa ruhusa.</s></f>"},{ID:123,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, akaenda, akauondoa mwili wake. Akaja Nikodemo, yule aliyemwendea Yesu mara ya </s></f>"},{ID:124,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwanza usiku, akaleta mchanganyiko wa manemane na udi, yapata ratili mia. Kisha </s></f>"},{ID:125,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakautwaa mwili wa Yesu, 
wakaufunga sanda ya kitani pamoja na </s></f>"},{ID:126,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>manukato, kama ilivyo desturi kwa Wayahudi kuzika.</s></f>"},{ID:126,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pale aliposulibiwa palikuwa na bustani, na katika bustani kulikuwa na kaburi jipya, </s></f>"},{ID:127,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ambamo hajazikwa bado mtu.
Basi humo ndani wakamweka Yesu kwa </s></f>"},{ID:128,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sababu ya Maandalio ya Pasaka ya Wayahudi, na kaburi lilikuwa karibu.</s></f>"},{ID:128,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Mungu(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"IJUMAA KUU (MWAKA B)"},{Guid:"NhZbFTBivE2DzssD69MiJA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA MBILI MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Ayubu 38:1,8-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Ayubu</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo Bwana alimjibu Ayubu toka dhoruba, akasema:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nani aliyefunga bahari nyuma ya milango miwili hapo ilipofurika kana kwamba imetoka </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tumboni kwa mama; Nilipotia uwingu juu yake kama vazi lake, na ukungu wa giza </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kama kitambaa cha kumfungia; nilipokata mipaka yake na kuiwekea </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>milango na komeo? Nikasema: Utafika mpaka hapa, wala hutapita: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndipo patakapokoma majivuno ya mawimbi yako.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA                  Zaburi 107:23-24, 25-26, 28-29, 30-31 (K.1b)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mshukuruni Bwana, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wengine walishuka baharini katika merikebu, wakifanya kazi yao penye maji mengi</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hao waliona matendo ya Bwana,
na maajabu ya Mungu vilindini mwa bahari. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mshukuruni Bwana, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana aliamuru, akavumisha upepo wa dhoruba, nao ukarusha juu mawimbi ya bahari.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakapanda juu angani, wakashuka chini vilindini; roho yao ikazimia mashakani. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mshukuruni Bwana, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakamlilia Bwana katika mahangaiko yao, akawatoa katika dhiki yao.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akaituliza dhoruba kukawa shwari;
mawimbi ya bahari yakanyamaza. K.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mshukuruni Bwana, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakafurahi kwa kuwa yametulia,
Bwana akawapeleka kwenye bandari waliyotamani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na wakamshukuru Bwana sababu ya wema wake, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maajabu yake aliyowatendea wanadamu.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mshukuruni Bwana, kwa maana wema wake ni wa milele</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI 					                   2 Wakorintho 5:14-17</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Upendo wa Kristo unatusonga tuking’amua: mmoja alikufa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa ajili ya wote, basi wote wamekufa. Naam, alikufa kwa ajili ya wote, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi kusudi wenye kuishi wasiishi kwa ajili yao wenyewe, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali waishi kwa ajili yake yeye aliyekufa akafufuka.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo, kutoka sasa hatuwajui watu kadiri ya ubinadamu wao tu. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Zamani tulimwona hata Kristo katika utu wake tu.  Lakini sasa maoni yetu ni mbalimbali.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, mtu akiwa katika Kristo ni kiumbe kipya. Ya kale yamepita, mapya yamefika.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Luka 7:16</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya. Aleluya Nabii mkubwa ametokea kwetu, na Mungu amewaangalia watu wake. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI   
Marko 4:35-41</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la injili takatifu 
ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ile ilipokuwa jioni, Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake,\" Tuvuke twende ng'ambo ya ziwa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakauacha ule umati wa watu, wakamchukua Yesu chomboni alimokuwa.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Vyombo vingine vilimfuata. Ikatokea thoruba kubwa na mawimbi,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mawimbi yakapiga chombo, hata kikaanza kujaa maji. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye Yesu alilala shetrini juu ya mto. Wakamwamsha na wakamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mwalimu huhangaiki tukiangamia?\" Akaamuka </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaukemea upepo akaiamuru bahari,\"Nyamaza! Tulia!\" Upepo ukakoma,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kukawa shwari kabisa. Akawauliza,\" Mbona mnaogopa hivi? </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je hamna imani?\" Wakaduwaa kwa hofu. Wakasemezana, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nani huyu, basi, hata upepo na bahari humtii?\" </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana. 
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA MBILI MWAKA B"},{Guid:"KlN9mzGXs0yXhA/Tcs7xhA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"field1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA NANE MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"field1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Kutoka 16:2-4, 12-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Kutoka</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Mkutano wote wa wana wa Israeli waliwanung' unikia </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa na Haruni huko jangwani. 
Wana wa Israeli wakawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Afadhali tungalikufa kwa mkono wa Bwana katika nchi ya Misri, </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tulipoketi kwenye sufuria za nyama, tukala mkate tukashiba!</s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninyi mmetuleta katika jangwa hili mpate kuua kwa njaa mkutano </s></f>"},{ID:7,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huu wote!\" Bwana akamwambia Musa: \"Nitawanyeshea </s></f>"},{ID:8,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi mvua ya mkate kutoka mbinguni. Watu watatoka </s></f>"},{ID:9,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg",BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakusanye siku kwa siku sehemu ya kila siku. Nitawajaribu hivi, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nipate kuona kama watafuata sheria zangu ama sivyo. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nimeyasikia manung’uniko ya wana wa Israeli. Basi waambie: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati wa jioni mtakula nyama, na asubuhi mtashiba mkate.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Ndipo mtajua ya kuwa mimi ndimi Bwana, Mungu wenu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kweli, jioni ile, wakafika kware wakakifunika kituo, na kesho </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yake asubuhi umande ukatanda pande zote za kituo. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umande huo ulipotoweka pakaonekana juu ya jangwa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kitu kama chembe chembe ndogo,
chepesi na cheupe kama unga </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wenye kufunikia nchi. Kukiona, wana wa Israeli wakaambiana, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Nini hii?\" Kwa maana hawakujua ni kitu gani. Musa akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Huo ndio mkate mliopewa na Bwana, uwe chakula chenu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 78:3-4,24-25 na 54 
 		</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Kiitikio) Bwana aliwapa mkate wa mbinguni.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mambo tuliyosikia na kuyajua;mambo ambayo baba zetu walituhadithia,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tutawaambia kizazi kijacho,
sifa za Bwana na nguvu yake. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Kiitikio) Bwana aliwapa mkate wa mbinguni.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aliyaamuru mawingu ya anga; akafungua milango ya mbingu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawanyeshea mana awalishe; akawapa ngano ya mbinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Kiitikio) Bwana aliwapa mkate wa mbinguni.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwanadamu akala mkate wa malaika; akawapa chakula </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tele. Aliwafikisha katika nchi yake takatifu,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mpaka mlima aliotwaa kwa mkono wake wa kulia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(Kiitikio) Bwana aliwapa mkate wa mbinguni.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Waefeso 4:17. 20-24</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Ninasema hili na kushuhudia katika Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwamba hamuenendi tena kama watu wengine wa mataifa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wanavyoenenda katika ubatili wa nia zao. Lakini mambo hayo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hamkujifunza kwa Kristo, ikiwa mlimsikiliza na kuelimishwa ndani </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yake, jinsi neno la kweli lilivyo katika Yesu, imewabidi kuacha mwenendo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wenu wa kwanza na kuvua utu wa zamani wenye kuharibika kwa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kufuata tamaa potovu. Imewapasa kuwa watu wapya katika roho </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maoni yenu. Mkamvae utu mpya ulioumbwa 
kwa mfano </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Mungu katika haki na utakatifu wa kweli.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Mathayo 4:4b</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluia. Alleluia. Mtu haishi kwa mkate tu, ila kwa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kila neno litokalo kinywaní mwa Mungu. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 6:24- 35</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Watu walipoona ya kuwa Yesu hayupo, wala wafuasi wake,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliingia vyomboni, wakaenda Kapernaumu wamtafute Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Walipomwona ng'ambo ya bahari, walimwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Rabbi, lini umefika hapa? Yesu akawajibu, akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Amin, amin, nawaambieni, mnanitafuta, si kwa sababu mliziona </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ishara, ila kwa sababu mlikula mikate, mkashiba. Fanyeni bidii,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si kwa kujipatia chakula kinachoharibika, bali kwa kujipatia </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>chakula kinachodumu hata uzima wa milele. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Chakula hicho atawapa Mwana wa Mtu; kwa maana huyo amekubaliwa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Baba, ndiye Mungu.\" Hapo wakamwambia, “Tufanyeje, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili tutende kazi za Mungu?\" Yesu akajibu, akawaambia, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Hi ndiyo kazi ya Mungu, kumsadiki yule aliyetumwa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na yeye.\" Wakamwambia, \"Basi, utafanya ishara gani,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tupate kuona na kusadiki? Utafanya nini? Baba zetu walikula mana </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>jangwani, kama ilivyoandikwa: Aliwalisha mkate wa mbinguni.\"’ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akawaambia, \"Amin, amin, nawaambieni, si Musa aliyewapa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mkate toka mbinguni, bali ni Baba yangu awapaye mkate </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>halisi toka mbinguni. Kwa maana mkate wa Mungu ni ule </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ushukao toka mbinguni na kuupa ulimwengu uzima.\" </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakamwambia, \"Bwana, utupe mkate huo siku zote.\" </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akawaambia, \"Mimi ni mkate wa uzima;</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ajaye kwangu hataona tena njaa, anisadikiye hataona tena kiu.”</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,Style:{Background:{Image:"pond1.jpg"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA NANE MWAKA B"},{Guid:"Uo7Rg1x+eUekkIBs08DdFA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA SITA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Hesabu 11:25-29</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Hesabu</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku zile: Bwana alishuka katika wingu. Akasema naye Musa,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akatwaa sehemu ya roho iliyokuwa juu ya Musa akaitia juu ya </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wazee wale sabini. Mara roho iliposhuka juu yao, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walitoa unabii, lakini hawakufanya hivyo tena.  Watu wawili walibaki </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kambini; mmoja jina lake Eldadi, na wa pili Medadi. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Roho ikashuka juu yao, ingawa hawakwenda hemani,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao walikuwa kati ya wale walioandikwa. Walitoa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>unabii wao wakiwa kambini. 
Kijana mmoja </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akaenda mbio kumwarifu Musa akisema, Eldadi na Medadi </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wanatoa unabii kambini.\" Yoshua mwana wa Nuni, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aliyekuwa mtumishi wa Musa tangu  ujana wake, akajibu </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akisema, \"Ewe Musa, bwana wangu, uwakataze!\"</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini Musa akamjibu, \"Je, waona wivu juu yangu? </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Laiti watu wote wa Bwana wangekuwa manabii, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Bwana angewajalia roho yake!\"</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
