Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(K) Amri za Bwana ni za haki, zafurahisha moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Basi, mtumishi wako anaziangalia, anapata faida kubwa kuzishika.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini ni nani ajuaye makosa yake? Unitakase na yale nisiyoyatambua. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(K) Amri za Bwana ni za haki, zafurahisha moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mtumishi wako pia umkinge na dhambi nisizozinuia
zisinitawale mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hapo nitakuwa mtimilifu,
