Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Imani mliyo nayo kwa Yesu Kristo, Bwana wetu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa utukufu, msiichanganye 
na ubaguzi. Ikiwa mtu </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anaingia katika mkutano wenu amevaa pete za dhahabu </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nguo maridadi, na pale pale anaingia mtu amevaa nguo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>chafu, nanyi mnamkazia macho mwenye kuvaa kimaridadi </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kumwambia, \"Kaa hapa, tafadhali,\" wakati mnamwambia </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yule maskini\"Simama huko\" au \"Kaa katika kanyagio </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>la miguu yangu,\" je, hapo hamjafanya ubaguzi miongoni </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwenu, mkawa waamuzi wa maoni mabaya?</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Angalieni, enyi ndugu zangu wapendwa je, Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
