Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule: Yohane alimwambia Yesu, \"Mwalimu, tulimwona mtu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akitoa pepo wabaya kwa jina lako, nasi tukamkataza kwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuwa yeye si mmoja wetu.\"
Yesu akajibu, \"Msimkataze, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa maana hakuna mtu afanyaye mwujiza kwa jina langu na papo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hapo akasema mabaya juu yangu. 
Asiyetupinga yu upande wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na kama mtu akiwapa hata kikombe cha maji tu, kwa sababu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ninyi ni wafuasi wa Kristo, amin,
nawaambieni, hatakosa tuzo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake. Yeyote anayemkwaza mmojawapo wa hawa wadogo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wanaoniamini, afadhali afungwe jiwe kubwa la kusagia shingoni </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwake na kutoswa baharini. Pia mkono wako ukikukosesha, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uukate. Afadhali uingie katika uzima u kilema kuliko kuwa na </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mikono miwili na kwenda Jehanamu kwenye  moto </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>usiozimika. Na mguu wako ukikukosesha, uukate. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Afadhali uwe kiwete na kuingia 
katika uzima kuliko kuwa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na miguu miwili na kutupwa Jehanamu. Na jicho lako </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>likikukosesha, uling'oe. 
Afadhali uingie katika ufalme wa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu na jicho moja kuliko kuwa na macho mawili na kutupwa </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Jehanamu. Humo funza hawafi, wala moto hauzimiki.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
