Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Amosi</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Amazia, kuhani huko Betheli, alimwambia </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nabii Amosi: “Haya mwonaji, nenda zako, uikimbilie nchi ya Yuda; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ukale mkate wako huko, ukatabiri huko. Usitabiri hapa Betheli, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana ni patakatifu pa kifalme; na hekalu la ufalme.\"</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amosi akamjibu Amazia: \"Mimi sikuwa nabii, wala mwana wa nabii:</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nilikuwa mchungaji, na mlimaji wa mikuyu. Lakini Bwana amenitwaa,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nilipofuatana na kundi, Bwana akaniambia: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘Nenda, ukatabiri kwa taifa langu Israeli.\"’</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
