Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninasikia anayosema Bwana Mungu; hakika, anasema maneno </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya amani. Wokovu wake ni karibu nao wenye kumcha;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utukufu wake utakaa katika nchi yetu. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Utuonyeshe wema wako, ee Bwana; utuletee wokovu wako.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wema na uaminifu zitakutana;
haki na amani </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zitabusiana. Uaminifu utachipuka katika nchi; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na haki itachungulia kutoka mbinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Utuonyeshe wema wako, ee Bwana; utuletee wokovu wako.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye Bwana atatoa yaliyo mema;
na nchi yetu itatoa mazao.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
