Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake kwa ajili ya Yesu Kristo, kama alivyotaka kwa mapenzi yake, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kusudi tuisifu na kuitukuza neema yake aliyotujalia katika huyo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mpendwa. Katika huyo tunao ukombozi kwa damu yake, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pia msamaha wa dhambi kwa kadiri ya wingi wa neema yake. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neema hiyo ametuzidishia katika hekima na akili yote.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ametujulisha fumbo la mapenzi yake kadiri ya azimio lake rahimu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alilokusudia katika yeye, ili alitimize wakati unapowadia: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani kuunganisha vyote katika Kristo aliye kichwa, vyote vilivyoko </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbinguni na duniani. Kwake yeye sisi tumekuwa warithi wake kwa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>haki. Tumechaguliwa tangu mwanzo kama alivyokusudia </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeye afanyaye yote kama
yanavyompendeza na anavyotaka. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiyo tumechaguliwa toka mwanzo tuweke matumaini </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yetu katika Kristo, na hivyo kuwapo kwa sifa na utukufu wake. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninyi pia mmelisikia neno la kweli katika Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya wokovu wenu, mkawa waamini. Mkatiwa muhuri wa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Roho Mtakatifu aliyeahidiwa. Huyo ni amana ya urithi wetu, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili atukomboe na atufanye mali yake kwa sifa na utukufu wake.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Waefeso 1:17-18</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya. Aleluya.
Baba wa Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo, aangaze macho ya </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mioyo yetu, tupate kujua tumaini la mwito wetu. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
