Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wachafu. Akawaagiza wasichukue kitu njiani - wala mkate, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala mkoba, wala pesa pindoni, ila fimbo ya safari.
Wavae viatu, lakini </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wasivae kanzu mbili. Tena aliwaambia, \"Mnapoingia katika </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyumba fulani, kaeni humo mpaka mtakapohama. Wasipowapokea na </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakikataa kuwasikiliza, ondokeni pale na kung'uteni mavumbi kutoka miguuni </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwenu kuwa ushuhuda kwao.” Basi, walitoka, wakahubiri watu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
