Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana Mungu wetu ni Bwana mmoja tu! Nawe mpende </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana Mungu wako kwa moyo wako wote, na kwa roho </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yako yote, na kwa akili zako zote, na kwa nguvu zako zote.' </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na ya pili ndiyo hii: 'Mpende mwenzako kama unavyojipenda </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwenyewe.' Hakuna amri nyingine iliyo kubwa kuliko hizi.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Yule mwandishi akamwambia, \"Vyema, mwalimu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uliyosema ni kweli. 'Yeye ni mmoja, wala hakuna mwingine </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ila yeye.' Na 'kumpenda yeye kwa moyo wako wote,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na kwa akili yako yote, na kwa nguvu zako zote, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kumpenda jirani kama unavyojipenda mwenyewe' </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni muhimu kuliko sadaka za kuteketeza na dhabihu zote pia.\" </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu alipoona jinsi alivyojibu kwa hekima, alimwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Wewe haupo mbali na ufalme wa Mungu.\" Toka hapo </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hakuthubutu tena mtu kumhoji. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
