Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndwaragĩra o ũhoro-inĩ waku wa ma, o ũkĩndutaga; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo wee nĩwe Ngai mwene ũhonokio wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Menyithia njĩra ciaku , Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ririkana matha maku, o nayo mĩtuganĩre yaku, Mwathani; nĩ amu ndĩrĩ yaaga o kuuma tene.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndirikana kũringana o na ũguo ũtugi waku ũtariĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa wega waku, wee Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
