tondũ ũcio, arĩa mahĩtĩtie, nĩ arĩmonagĩrĩria njĩra.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arĩa ahoreri arĩmatwaraga na mĩthiĩre o ĩrĩa ya kĩhooto: acio ahoreri-rĩ, nĩ kũruta arĩmarutaga mũgerere wa njĩra yake.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
