Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atūtware kw</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769> Ngai: agikiuragwo mwiri, no ha ühoro wa muoyo</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agicoka gwikiruo muoyo. Agithii e na muoyo ucio wa muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
