Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo thabina io, niyo and</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>u</s></f><fArial Black><s2769> anyinyi, nao no andū anana, maahonokeire thii-ini wayo maai-inī, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo ühoro ūcio niguo ngerekano ya üria na inyui mühonokagio riu ni ühoro wa kubatithio, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
