Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agaikaraga guoko-ini kwa urio kwa Ngai, nao araika, na aria ene </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wathani, o na aria marī na hinya matuitwo a gwathagwo niwe. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
