Text:"KIUMIA KIA MBERE KIA WINYEREKIA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"RMySpkJ0zE+dgfuBO4BPQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA MOJA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Ezekieli 17:22-24</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Ezekieli</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>BWANA Mungu asema hivi: Katika kilele kirefu cha mwerezi,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mimi mwenyewe nitatwaa kitawi, na kukiweka katika udongo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitachuma kitawi laini katika tawi la juu, na kukipandikiza </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mimi mwenyewe juu ya mlima mrefu sana. Juu ya mlima unaoinuka </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>zaidi katika Israeli, hapo nitakipandikiza. Kitawi hicho </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kitatoa matawi, na kuzaa matunda, na kugeuka kuwa mwerezi bora.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndege wa kila namna watakaa chini yake, watakaa katika </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kivuli cha matawi yake. Na miti yote ya mashamba itatambua </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kwamba ndimi, BWANA. Ninayeshusha mti mrefu, na kuinua </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mti mdogo, ninayekausha mti mbichi, na kuustawisha mti </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mkavu. Mimi, BWANA, nimesema hayo, nami nitayatimiza!</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA  		
Zaburi 92:2-3, 13-14, 15-16 (K. 2a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni vema kumshukuru Bwana, na kuliimbia jina lako, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ewe Uliye Juu, Ni vema kutangaza wema wako </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>asubuhi, na uaminifu wako nyakati za usiku. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwenye haki atastawi kama mtende,
atakua kama mwerezi </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Lebanoni. Waliopandwa katika nyumba ya Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watastawi katika nyua za Mungu wetu. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hata katika uzee watazaa matunda,
watakuwa na utomvu na ubichi,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili watangaze, \"Bwana ni mwadilifu;
Mwamba wangu, asiye na uovu ndani yake.\" </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
2 Wakorintho 5:6-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Tunachangamka kila wakati hata tukijua ya kuwa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>muda tunaokaa mwilini tunakaa ugenini mbali na Bwana. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo maisha yetu yanategemezwa na imani si kwa kuona.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hata hivyo tunaona radhi na kupendelea zaidi kuuhama </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwili na kukaa kwetu kwa Bwana.
Kwa hiyo tunafanya bidii </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya kumpendeza yeye, tukiwa nyumbani au ugenini.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana sisi sote hatuna budi kuhudhuria katika baraza la Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili kila mmoja ayapate malipo ya mambo aliyoyafanya </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwilini, yakiwa mema au mabaya.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU BWANA)</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya. Aleluya. Mbegu ni neno la Mungu, mpanzi ni Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wale wote wanaokuja kwake,
watakuwa na uzima wa milele. Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Marko 4:26-34</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia umati, akasema, “Ufalme wa Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>unafanana na mtu apandaye mbegu shambani.Usiku na mchana, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akilala, akiwa macho, mbegu inamea na kukua, asijue namna yake. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana udongo wenyewe unasitawisha kwanza jani, halafu </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>suke, kisha punje pevu sukeni. Nafaka inapokomaa, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>analeta mundu, kwa maana mavuno yamefika.\" Alisema, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Tuufananishe ufalme wa Mungu na nini? Au tuupange katika </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mfano gani? Ni kama mbegu ya haradali. Inapopandwa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ardhini, ni ndogo kuliko mbegu zote zipatikanazo duniani.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini baada ya kupandwa inakua na kupita mimea yote ya bustani, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikachipuza matawi makubwa,
hata ndege wa angani waweza </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kukaa kivulini pake.\" Kwa mifano mingi ya namna hii aliwatangazia neno </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lake, kwa kadiri walivyoweza kulifahamu. Pasipo mifano </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakusema nao. Lakini walipokuwa peke </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yao, aliwaeleza wafuasi wake yote.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana. 
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA MOJA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"gBI+eta9e0SR/gfkxVpzPQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f><fArial Black><s1384>   </s></f><fArial Black><s1846>                     MITHALI 9;1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846>somo katika kitabu cha Mithali.</s></f></u></b>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hekima amejenga nyumba yake, amechonga nguzo zake saba; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amechinja nyama yake, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amechanganya divai yake, ametandika meza yake. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ametuma wajakazi wake, waende kulia kutoka miinuko ya mji: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Aliye mjinga apite hapa;\" anamwambia mpumbavu. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Njoni mle ,kate wangu, mnywe divai niliyochanganya! </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Acheni ujinga, na mtaishi; na kuendelea katika njia ya ufahamu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA  			Zaburi 34:2-3, 4-5, 6-7, 8-9 (K. 9a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitamtukuza Bwana kila wakati sifa zake zi kinywani mwangu daima.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nafsi yangu itajisifu katika Bwana Wanyonge wasikie na kufurahi. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtukuzeni Bwana pamoja nami,tuliadhimishe jina lake pamoja.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nilimkimbilia Bwana, akanisikiliza,
akaniopoa katika hofu zangu zote. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtazameni Mungu mkafurahiwe na nyuso zenu zisihuzunike.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mnyonge huyu alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza,
akamwokoa katika shida zake zote. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Malaika wa Bwana ameweka kambi kwao,kuwazungukia wale wamchao Mungu na kuwaokoa.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema heri mtu yule anayemkimbilia. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<b><fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI                 Waefeso 5:15-20</s></f></b>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso.</s></f></u>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu; angalieni sana jinsi mnavyoishi, si kama watu wasio na hekima, bali kama watu wenye hekima. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tena utumieni muda vyema, kwa maana siku hizi ni mbaya. Kwa hio msikose akili, bali mfahamu atakacho Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wala msilewe mvinyo, kwani ulevi humwangamiza mtu, bali mjazwe roho. Imbeni pamoja zaburi na tenzi na nyimbo za dini. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni na kumshangilia Bwana mioyoni mwenu. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Daima mshukuruni Mungu Baba kwa jina la Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo kwa ajili ya yote.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Shangilio la Injili                                       Yohane 6:56</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K; Aleluya.     W. Aleluya</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K; Aulaye mwili wangu na kuinywa damu yangu hukaa ndani yangu nami hukaa ndani yake, asema Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W; Aleluya</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI                                                          Yohane 6: 51-58</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>Somo la injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f></u>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule; Yesu aliuambia umati: \" Mimi ndimi mkate wa uzima ulioshuka toka Mbinguni; </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aulaye mkate huu ataishi milele, na mkate nitakaotoa mimi ni mwili wangu kwa ajili ya uzima wa ulimwengu. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\" Hapo wayahudi wakabishana wao kwa wao wakisema, \" awezaje huyu kutulisha mwili wake?\" </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akawaambia, \" Amin, Amin, nawaambieni, msipoula mwili wa Mwana wa mtu na kuinywa damu yake, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hamna uzima ndani yenu. Aulaye mwili wangu na kuinywa damu yangu anao uzima wa milele, nami nitamfufua siku ya mwisho.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana Mwili wangu ni chakula kweli na Damu yangu ni kinywaji kweli. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aulaye Mwili wangu na kuinywa Damu yangu hukaa ndani yangu , nami ndani yake. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama Baba aliye hai amenituma mimi, nami napata uzima kwake, naye anilaye mimi atapata uzima kwa njia yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huu ndio mMate ushukao toka Mbinguni. Si kama baba zenu walivyokula, wakafa; </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali aulaye mkate huu ataiishi milele.\"</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
