THIMO 9:1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githomo kuuma ibuku ria Thimo.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mutumia ucio ugwitwo uugi-uria-wa-ma ni eyakiire nyumba, na ni aacuhitie itugi ciake mugwanja. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni muthinju ngoima ciake, ndibei yake aringiriirie, na niarikitie gutandika metha yake.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni areketie airitu ake, akaaniririthia ituura-ini o kundu gutuugiriire muno, akoiga mundu o wothe utari muugi, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni akerure atonye na guku! Mundu uria wagite wiciriori, we akamwira: Ukai mukarie irio ciakwa, na munyue ndibei iria ningiriirie! </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyui andu aya mutari ogi-ri, tigai uhoro wanyu, niguo mutuure, mucoke guthiaga na njira o iria ya mbunguiro!</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO                     Thaburi 34:1-2;9-10;11-12;13-14</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Ni ndirigathaga Mwathani o hingo ciothe; kanua gakwa kumukumia gatiri hindi gatarimukumagia. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nowe ngoro yakwa iriirahagira: Aria ahoreri mariiguaga uguo magakena.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Mwitigagirei Mwathani, inyui andu ake atheru, thima aria amwitigiri matiri kindu maagaga. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Miruthi miithi yo ni ithinangaga, igakihuta, no aria marongoragia Mwathani matiri kindu kiega mangiaga.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Ukai ariu akwa, muthikiririe uria nguuga: ni ngumuruta mugie na gwitigira Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni mundu uriku wiriragiria gutuura muoyo, akenda gukiingihia matuku eonagire maundu mega?</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4. Atiri, kirigagiririe rurimi rwaku rutikanoige uuru; giragia miromo yaku ndikanakiarie maheni. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Withemagei uuru-ini, mwikage o wega; caragia thayu, o nginya kuuthingata.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI                                   Aefeso 5:15-20</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>Guthoma marua ma Muthure Paul kuri Aefeso;</s></f></u>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariu a Ithe witu, wimenyagirirei muno mithiire iria muthiaga nayo, mutigathiage na iria ya irimu, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tiga o iria ya andu ogi, na mutigate ihinda riria riagiriru ria gwikaga wega, ni undu matuku maya turi namo ni moru. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni undu ucio-ri, tigagai guikara muritite, no muikare mumenyete uria Mwathani endaga gwikwo. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi mutikanario ni ndibei, ni undu uriu niguo ukiragiriria umaramari, ni kaba muiyuruo ni muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwaranagirie na thaburi na nyimbo cia Ngai, ina nyimbo cia kuguna mioyo ya andu, mukiinagira Mwathani na ngoro cianyu, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mukimuhuragira kinanda. Ningi mucokagirie Ngai, o we Ithe witu, ngatho mahinda mothe ni undu wa maundu mothe, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thiini wa riitwa ria Mwathani witu Yesu Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>Rwimbo rwa Alleluya    </s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>                                    Johana 6:56</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga atiri: uria uriaga mwiri wakwa na akanyua thakame yakwa-ri aikaraga thiini wakwa, na nii ngaikara thiini wake.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJILI                                      Johana 6:51-58</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>Guthoma injiri ya Muthure Johana:</s></f></u>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io Yesu akiira kirindi: Ni nii mugate uria waikurukire uumite iguru, wi muoyo; mundu aaria mugate uyu, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatuura tene na tene; na mugate uria ngakiruta ni mwiri wakwa, ndiurute ni undu wa muoyo wa kirindi. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondu wa uhoro ucia ayahudi makirika gukararania o ene, makorania atiri: mundu uyu ahote ati gutuhe mwiri wake turie?</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akimera: Ndamwira atiri o ma, ma: Mwaaga kuria mwiri wa muru wa mundu na munyue thakame yake, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mutiri na muoyo thiini wanyu. Uria uriaga mwiri wakwa na akanyua thakame yakwa-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ena muoyo wa tene na tene; na ni ngamuriukia muthenya wa kurigiriria. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu mwiri wakwa ni irio kuna, na thakame yakwa ni gia-kunyua kuna. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uria uriaga mwiri wakwa na akanyua thakame yakwa-ri, aikaraga thiini wakwa, na nii ngaikara thiini wake. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ta uria Ithe witu uria wi muoyo aandekirie, na nii ngagia muoyo ni undu wa Ithe witu, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>noguo mundu uria nake undiaga arigiaga muoyo niundu wakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ucio niguo mugate uria waikurukire uumite iguru; ti ta uria maithe manyu maariaga, na magikua; </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uria uriaga mugate ucio-ri, agatuura tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI MWAKA B"},{Guid:"anWuXbWZ80yezls1sdkszw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Isaya 35:4-7a</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wale waliovunjika moyo waambieni “Mjipe moyo, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>msiogope! Tazameni, Mungu wenu yupo hapa atalipiza </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kisasi; adhabu itakuja kutoka kwa Mungu, naye atakuja </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuwaokoa ninyi. 
Ndipo macho ya vipofu yatafumbuliwa, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>masikio ya viziwi yatafunguliwa; ndipo kiwete </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atarukaruka kama swala, na ulimi wa bubu utaimba </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa furaha. Maji yatabubujika katika jangwa, na vijito katika nyika.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nchi kavu itageuka kuwa ziwa la maji, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nchi ya kiu itakuwa chemchemi za maji.\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 146:7, 8-9bc, 10 </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Kiitikio) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ndiye ashikaye uaminifu hata milele. Huwarudishia </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>haki waliodhulumiwa, huwapa wenye njaa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>chakula. BWANA huwafungua wafungwa. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Kiitikio) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BWANA  huyafumbua macho ya vipofu. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BWANA huwainua waliokandamızwa chini;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BWANA huwapenda wenye haki
BWANA huwalinda wageni. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Kiitikio) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana huwategemeza yatima na mjane, bali huipotosha njia </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya waovu BWANA atatawala milele,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu wako, ee Sioni, kizazi hata kizazi! </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(Kiitikio) Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
Yakobo 2:1-5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Yakobo</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Imani mliyo nayo kwa Yesu Kristo, Bwana wetu wa utukufu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>msiichanganye na ubaguzi.
Ikiwa mtu anaingia katika </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mkutano wenu amevaa pete za dhahabu na nguo maridadi,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na pale pale anaingia mtu amevaa nguo chafu, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nanyi mnamkazia macho mwenye kuvaa kimaridadi na kumwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Kaa hapa, tafadhali,\" wakati mnamwambia yule maskini </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Simama huko\" au \"Kaa katika kanyagio la miguu yangu,\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>je, hapo hamjafanya ubaguzi miongoni mwenu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mkawa waamuzi wa maoni mabaya?</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Angalieni, enyi ndugu zangu wapendwa je, Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hakuwachagua fukara wa ulimwenguni hapa wawe matajiri</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika imani na warithi wa ufalme aliowaahidia wenye kumpenda?</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Tazama Mathayo 4:23</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.  Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu alifundisha Injili ya ufalme, na akaponya </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kila ugonjwa na maradhi katika watu.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Marko 7:31-37</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la lnjili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule:Yesu aliporudi kutoka wilaya ya Tiro, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa njia ya Sidoni, akipita katikati ya nchi ya Dekapoli, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akafikia ziwa la Galilaya.
Wakamletea bubu-kiziwi, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakamwomba amwekee mkono. Akamtenga na umati wa watu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamtia vidole masikioni, akatema mate na </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kumgusa ulimi; akatazama juu mbinguni,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akapiga kite, akamwambia, \"Ephphatha!\" 
(maana yake, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Fumbuka!\"). Mara akafumbuka masikio na akafunguliwa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kifungo cha ulimi wake,
akaongea sawa sawa.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akawakataza wasimwambie mtu. Lakini kadiri alivyowakataza, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndivyo walivyozidi kutangaza habari zake. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Walishangaa kupita kiasi, wakasema, Amefanya yote vema, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amewafanya viziwi wasikie, na bubu waongee.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TATU MWAKA B"},{Guid:"LuFWAUqe0E+2TaP/W5EzZg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Isaia 35:4-7</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨRORI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arĩa marĩ na guoya ngoro merei atĩrĩ: Wĩũmĩrĩriei, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũtige gwĩtigĩra; atĩrĩrĩ: Ngai 
wanyu agoka </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ũhoro wa kũrĩhanĩria, we Ngai agerane ngero iringaine </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ũrĩa gwĩkĩtwo. Nĩwe ũgoka amũhonokie.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo maitho ma atumumu nĩ makahingũrũo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o namo matũ ma arĩa mataiguaga  nĩ magakunũrũo. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo  mũndũ ũrĩa ũthuaga agacimbicaga o ta thwariga , </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o naruo rũrĩmĩ rũa ũrĩa ũtahotaga kwaria nĩ kũina rũkaina; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo werũ-inĩ nĩ gũgatathũka maaĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kũu rũng’ũri-inĩ gũthererage tũrũũĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O naguo  mũthanga ũrĩa ũhenahenagia nĩ ũkagarũrũo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtuĩke karia ka maaĩ, nakuo kũndũ kũrĩa gwĩ tĩri </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũnyotu kũgĩe ithima cia maaĩ megũtherũka.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         
Thaburi 146:7:8-9a;9b-10</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ũtuagĩra andũ arĩa agũmĩre matuĩro ma kĩhooto; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa ningĩ ũheaga arĩa ahũtu irio.  Mwathani-rĩ, arĩa ohe nĩ amohoraga.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ ahingũraga arĩa atumumu maitho, Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ainamũraga arĩa mekonotete,
Mwathani nĩ enda arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>athingu; Mwathani-rĩ, nĩ amenyagĩrĩra ageni.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  
Mwana wa ngoriai na mũtumia wa ndigwa, nĩwe ũmanyitagĩrĩra; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nayo njĩra ya andũ aaganu nĩ kũmĩhotomia amĩhotomagia.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani egũtũũra athamakaga tene na tene, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai waku, wee Sion-rĩ, egũtũũra athamakaga nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ arĩa matarĩ na mwĩgatho, nĩ gũkorũo ũthamaki wa igũrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Jakobu 2:1-5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE JAKOBU</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ha ũhoro wa wĩtĩkio ũrĩa wa gwĩtĩkia Mwathani witũ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu Kristũ, o we mwene riri-rĩ, tigai kũwĩtĩkia mũgĩtĩagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ maũthĩ. Tondũ rĩrĩ, kũngĩũka thinagoga yanyu mũndũ wĩ na gĩcũhĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gĩa thahabu na ehumbĩte nguo thaka-rĩ, na ningĩ gũcoke gũũke </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ mũthĩni wĩhumbĩte nguo thũku-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na inyuĩ mũtĩe ũcio wĩhumbĩte nguo ĩrĩa thaka, mũmwĩre atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikara thĩ handũ haha hega; na mwĩre ũcio mũthĩni atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee-rĩ,  rũgama harĩa; kana rĩrĩ:
Ikara thĩ haha magũrũ-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
