Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mũgatuĩka atuĩri andũ, mũkĩrĩ na meciria moru? Ariũ a Ithe witũ,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inyuĩ nyenda mũno, ta thikĩrĩriai: githĩ Ngai ndaagĩthurire andũ arĩa marĩ</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>athĩni gũkũ thĩ, matuĩke itonga ũhoro-inĩ wa wĩtĩkio, na matuĩke </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>a kũgaĩrũo ũthamaki ũrĩa erĩire arĩa mamwendaga?</s></f>"},{ID:9,
