Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu, agĩcoka akiuma kũu bũrũri wa Tiro, agĩtũrĩkĩria Sidone, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩkinya iria rĩa Galilea, atuĩkanĩtie bũrũri wa Dekapoli gatagatĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Makĩmũrehere mũndũ gĩtaigua, na warogoyaga; makĩmũthaitha </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amũigĩrĩre guoko. Nake akĩmwamũrania na kĩrĩndĩ akĩmũtwara </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>keheri-inĩ, agĩtonyia ciara matũ ma mũndũ ũcio, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩtua mata, akĩmũhutia rũrĩmĩ; akĩrora igũrũ, akĩhũmũka, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmwĩra: Effata, ũguo nĩ’rĩ: Hingũka.  Matũ make magĩkĩhingũka, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo, mũkiha wa rũrĩmĩ rwake ũkĩregera, akĩaria o wega.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akĩmakaania matikere mũndũ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao o aakĩria kũmakaania, noguo maakĩragia kũmemerekia ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũcio o mũno. Na nĩ maagegete mũno mũno, makoiga atĩrĩ: Nĩ ekĩte maũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mothe wega: arĩa mataiguaga nĩ atũmaga maigue, nao arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
