Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA ITHATU MWAKA B"},{Guid:"oOTiVFU3fkqSAm4zbwIZqg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>SOMO LA KWANZA
Mambo ya Walawi 13;1-2,44-46</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Somo katika kitabu cha Mambo ya Walawi</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Bwana aliwaambia Musa na Haruni, akasema: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Katika ngozi ya mwili wa mtu, pakitokea kivimbe,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>upele, au paku linalong'aa, yawezekana </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ni alama ya ukoma katika mwili wake.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Huyo mtu atapelekwa kwa Haruni, kuhani, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>au kwa mmoja wa wanawe, makuhani.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Basi huyo mtu ni mwenye ukoma; yeye ni najisi.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kuhani anapaswa kusema kuwa yu najisi, anao ukoma </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wa kichwani. Mwenye ukoma aliyepatwa na ugonjwa huo, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nguo zake zitararuliwa na nywele za kichwa chake </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>zitaachwa wazi, naye atafunika mdomo wake wa juu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na kupiga kelele, \"Najisi! Najisi!” Kwa kadiri ugonjwa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wake utakavyodumu, 
yeye atakuwa najisi; </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>yeye yu najisi, atakaa peke yake: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>makao yake yatakuwa nje ya kambi.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Neno la Bwana. (TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA	
Zaburi 32:1-2, 5, 11 (K. 7)</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>K. Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Heri mtu yule aliyesamehewa kosa, aliyesitiriwa dhambi yake.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Heri mtu yule ambaye Bwana hamhesabii kosa, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wala moyoni mwake hamna hila. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>K. Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nilikujulisha dhambi yangu; wala </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>sikuficha kosa langu. Nikasema,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>\"Nitamwungamia Bwana uovu wangu,” </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nawe ukaondoa ubaya wa dhambi yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>K. Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mfurahieni Bwana, shangilieni, enyi waadilifu; </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>shangilieni, enyi nyote wanyofu wa moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>K. Ndiwe kimbilio langu; wanizungushia furaha ya wokovu.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>SOMO LA PILI
1 Wakorintho 10;31-11;1.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ndugu zangu Mkila au mkinywa au mkitenda </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>lolote, fanyeni yote kwa kumtukuza Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Msiwakwaze Wayahudi wala Wagiriki wala Kanisa la Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kama nami ninavyo wapendeza wote</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>katika mambo yote. Sitafuti faida yangu, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ila faida ya wote, wapate kuokoka.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mniige mimi, kama mimi ninavyomfuasa Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Neno la Bwana.
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>SHANGILIO LA INJILI Luka 7:16</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aleluya.	Aleluya.
Nabii mkubwa ametokea kwetu, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na Mungu amewaangalia watu wake. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> INJILI	
Marko 
I; 40-45</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wakati ule: Mwenye ukoma alimjia Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akampigia magoti na kusema, ”Ukitaka, waweza kunitakasa.”</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Naye akamhurumia, akanyosha mkono wake, akamgusa </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na kumwambia, ''Nataka, takasika.” </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mara hapo ukoma ukamtoka, akatakasika. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Alipokwisha kumwonya akamwacha aende zake. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na akamwambia, ''Angalia, usimweleze mtu chochote, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>isipokuwa nenda ukajionyeshe kwa kuhani </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>utoe zaka iliyoamriwa na Musa kwa kupona ukoma wako; </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kusudi iwe ushuhuda kwao.” Huyo lakini alitoka, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akaanza kutangaza wazi na kulieneza tukio hilo,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kiasi kwamba Yesu hakuweza tena kuingia mjini. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Basi, akakaa nje mahali pa ukiwa. Hata hivyo watu </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>walimwendea kutoka pande zote.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Injili ya Bwana.
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA SITA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"Gp8kkqM6zka5VbCFHHDoow",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>UBATIZO WA BWANA YESU MWAKA B</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Isaya 55:1-11</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana asema hivi:
\"Enyi wote wenye kiu, njoni penye maji!</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hata msipokuwa na fedha, njoni:
njoni mnunue nafaka na kula;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>njoni mnywe divai na maziwa,
bila fedha na bila kulipa!</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa nini mnatoa fedha mpate kitu kisicho mkate,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa nini mnachoka mpate kitu kisichoshibisha?</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nisikilizeni mimi, mtakula vitamu,
na kufurahishwa kwa vyakula vitamu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tegeni sikio, njoni kwangu;
sikilizeni, na roho zenu zitaishi.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitafanya nanyi agano la milele,
nitasimika wema wa milele niliyomwahidia Daudi.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Angalieni, nimemweka awe shahidi kwa makabila,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kiongozi na mtawala wa mataifa.
Tazama, utaliita taifa usilolijua,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na taifa lisilokujua litakukimbilia,
kwa sababu ya Bwana, Mungu wako,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ya Mtakatifu wa Israeli aliyekukuza.
Mtafuteni Bwana akiwa anapatikana bado,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwiteni angali yupo karibu.
Mtu mbaya aache njia yake,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye mwovu aache mawazo yake;
amrudie Bwana atakayemhurumia;</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu wetu anayesamehe kabisa.
Maana mawazo yangu Si mawazo yenu,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala njia zangu si njia zenu, asema Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama vile mbingu ziinukavyo juu ya nchi,
ndivyo njia zangu ni juu kuliko njia zenu,</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mawazo yangu juu kuliko mawazo yenu.
Kama vile mvua na theluji zishukavyo kutoka mbinguni,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hazirudi huko bila kuinywesha ardhi,
na kuizalisha na kuichipusha,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikampa mtu apandaye mbegu,
na mtu alaye chakula,</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndivyo litakavyokuwa neno langu,
litokalo katika kinywa changu;</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>halitanirudia bure,
bali litatimiza mapenzi yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nalo litafanikiwa katika mambo yale niliyolituma.\"</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUTIKIZANA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Isaya 12:2-3, 4bed, 5 6(K. 3)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>K. Kwa furaha mtateka maji kwenye chemchemi za wokovu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Ndiye Mungu wa wokovu wangu;
namtumainia, wala sina hofu tena.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kuwa Bwana ni nguvu yangu na wimbo wangu,
amekuwa wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nanyi mtateka maji kwa furaha
kwenye chemchemi za wokovu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Kwa furaha mtateka maji kwenye chemchemi za wokovu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Mshukuruni Bwana, liiteni jina lake;</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tangazeni kati ya mataifa matendo yake makuu,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakumbusheni ya kuwa jina lake ni tukufu sana. K.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Kwa furaha mtateka maji kwenye chemchemi za wokovu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana, maana ametenda miujiza;
itangazwe duniani kote.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Paza sauti za furaha na shangwe, enyi watu wa Sioni.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana ametukuzwa ndani yako, Mtakatifu wa Israeli! K.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Kwa furaha mtateka maji kwenye chemchemi za wokovu</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>1 Yohane 5:1-9</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wapendwa:
Kila asadikiye ya kuwa Yesu ni Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ana asili yake katika Mungu.
Na kila ampendaye Baba, ampenda pia aliyezaliwa naye.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tutakuwa na hakika kwamba tunawapenda watoto wa Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tukimpenda Mungu mwenyewe na kuzishika amri zake.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana kumpenda Mungu ni kuzishika amri zake,
na amri zake si nzito.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana yote yaliyo na asili yake katika Mungu
huushinda ulimwengu.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ushindi ushindao ulimwengu ndiyo imani yetu.
Ni nani awezaye kuushinda ulimwengu</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>isipokuwa yeye tu asadikiye ya kuwa Yesu ni Mwana wa Mungu?</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni Yesu Kristo aliyekuja kwa njia ya maji na damu na Roho.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakuja katika maji tu, bali katika maji na damu pia.
Ndiye Roho ashuhudiaye, kwa maana Roho ni ukweli.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, kuna watatu wanaoshuhudia:
Roho, na maji, na damu; 
hao watatu hushuhudia neno moja.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikiwa tunapokea ushuhuda wa wanadamu,
basi ushuhuda wa Mungu ni mkubwa zaidi.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ushuhuda wa Mungu ndio huu: amemshuhudia Mwanawe.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Yohane 1:29</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000> Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>.
K. Yohane alimwona Yesu anakuja kwake,
akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Tazameni, Mwanakondoo wa Mungu
aondoaye dhambi za ulimwengu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Marko 1:7-11</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yohane[Yohane] alihubiri akisema,
\"Anayekuja baada yangu ni mwenye nguvu kunipita mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwake sifai hata kuinama na kufungua gidamu ya viatu vyake.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi nimewabatiza kwa maji;
lakini yeye atawabatiza kwa Roho Mtakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikatokea siku zile
