Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini hawakutambua yakuwa niliwatunza</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niliwaongoza kwa kamba ya ngozi kwa vifungo vya mapendo. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niliwainua kama mtoto mchanga mpaka shavuni, niliinama nipate </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwalisha. Moyo wangu umegeuka ndani yangu, huruma yangu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>imewaka tena. Sitatenda kadiri ya hasira yangu, sitarudi </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kumwangamiza Efraimu, kwa maana mimi ni Mungu wala </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si binadamu, ndimi niliye mtakatifu katikati yenu, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala sitaingia katika hasira</s></f>"},{ID:15,
