Isaya 12: 2-3,4bed, 5-6(K 3) </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: mtateka maji kwa furaha kwenye chemchemi za wokovu</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiye Mungu wa wokovu, namtumainia wala sina hofu tena </s></f>"},{ID:19,
