Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mshukuruni Bwana, liiteni jina lake Tangazeni kati ya mataifa matendo </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yake makuu. wakumbusheni ya kuwa jina lake ni tukufu sana. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiitikio: mtateka maji kwa furaha kwenye chemchemi za wokovu. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muimbieni Bwana, maana ametenda miujiza; itangazeni duniani kote </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Paza sauti za furaha na shangwe, enyi watu wa Sioni, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
