3: 8-12,14-19 </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu, mimi niliye mdogo kwa watakatifu wote nimepewa</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>neema hii ya kuwahubiria watu wa mataifa utajiri wa Kristu usiopima, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena kuwaangaza watu wajue jinsi fumbo la umungu lilivyotimia.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hilo lilikuwa limefichika tangu milele katika Mungu aliyeumba </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vyote. Lakini sasa , kwa ujumbe wa Kanisa, wakuu na wenye enzi wa </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbinguni wanapata kuitambua hekima ya Mungu iliyo ya namna nyingi. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivyo ndiyo alivyoazimia tangu milele na kulitimiza azimio hilo </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika Kristu Yesu, Bwana wetu. Katika huyo tunathubutu kumkaribia </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa matumaini katika nguvu ya imani tuliyo nayo. Basi nampigia </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magoti Baba wa Bwana wetu Yesu Kristu, aliye asili ya mfano wa kila </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ubaba wa mbinguni na duniani. Mungu Baba yetu asiye na mipaka katika </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utukufu wake, awajalie ninyi kuimarika kwa nguvu ya Roho </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake na kuwa watu wa kiroho, ili kwa imani ya Kristu akae mioyoni </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwenu; mkiwa na mizizi na misingi yenu katika upendo, muweze </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kupewa nguvu ya kukishika pamoja na 
watakatifu wote </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kile kilicho marefu na mapana, katika kina na kimo, na kuujua upendo huo </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>upitao ufahamu, mpate kujazwa ukamilifu wote wa Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU) </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI 
Yohane 19; 31-37 Somo la injili takatifu iliyoandikwa na Yohane </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ile ilikuwa siku ya kuaanda Pasaka. Kwa hiyo wayahudi </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>walimwomba Pilato, waliosulubiwa wavunjwe miguu na kuondolewa, ili miili </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>isikae msalabani siku ya sabato, kwa maana sabato ile ilikuwa sikukuu kubwa. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, askari wakaja wakamvunja miguu yule wa kwanza na wa pili </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliosulubiwa naye. Lakini walipomjia Yesu na kumwona </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amekwisha kufa, hawakumvunja miguu, ila askari mmojawapo </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alimchoma ubavu kwa mkuki, mara ikatoka damu na maji. Aliyeona hayo, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ameshuhudia, na ushuhuda wako ni kweli; naye anajua ya kuwa ansema </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kweli, ili nanyi pia mpate kusadiki. Maana hayo yametendeka,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili andiko litimie lisemalo, \"Hatavunjwa mfupa hatammoja.\" </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tena andiko lingine lasema,\" Watamtazama yule waliyemchoma.\" </s></f>"},{ID:61,
