Text:"SHEREHE YA MOYO MTAKATIFU WA YESU"},{Guid:"pgx2fd1JtUe4x9H2QsjURQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA MBERE        GUCOKERITHIA MAATHANI 4:1-2, 6-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guthoma kuuma ibuku ria Gucokerithia Maathani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa agigiita kiridi na akimera atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Riu inyui Aisraeli aya, ta thikiriria muigue </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>irira cia watho wa kurumiriruo, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na matuiro ma ciira maria ngumuruta murumagirire, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha mutuure muoyo, na mukahota guthii</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mutonye bururi uria muheagwo ni Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai wa maithe manyu, muwigwatire utuike wanyu. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uhoro uria ndimwathite-ri, mutikanawongerere, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana muunyihanyihie, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha mutuure mumenyereire maathani ma </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ngai wanyu, maria ngumwatha. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondu ucio mamenyagirirei o na mumekage; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni gukoruo macio nimo marionanagia uugi wanyu, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na uhoro wanyu wa uria mumenyete maundu,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makionwo ni nduriri iria iriiguaga uhoro wothe </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa irira icio cia watho wa kurumiriruo, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nacio ciugage atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kai ti-itheru ruriri ruru runene ni ruugi-i, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kai ni andu mamenyete wega maundu-i! </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni undu-ri, ni ruriri ruriko runene rwi na Ngai yaruo irukuhiriirie, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ta uria Mwathani Ngai witu atukuhagiriria </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mahinda maria mothe twamukaira? </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ningi-ri, ni ruriri ruriku runene rwi na irira </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cia watho wa kurumiriruo cia kihooto, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na matuiro ma cira ma kihooto, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ta watho uyu wothe ndiramwatha naguo umuthi?</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO      THABURI 15:2-3a; 3b-4,5</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria athaka ngoro magakaira mucii-ini wa Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na riri, ni uria wina mithiire mikinyaniru,</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uria wikaga o maundu ma uthingu,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na kwaria aaragia o uhoro-wa-ma, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O uria wa ngoro yake;</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mundu utari na njambanio rurimi-ini rwake.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria athaka ngoro magakaira mucii-ini wa Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndekaga muthiritwe uru,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kana akoya kiugo gia kumenereria </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mundu ungi wa itura.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maitho-ini make muura-huhu ni githemba kiruruke,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No aria etigiri mwathani nio ekiriire.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na aakoruo ehitite mwihitwa ungimunuha ndangigarurira.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria athaka ngoro magakaira mucii-ini wa Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndohoranagira mbia ciake ni getha one nyongeri,</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na ndangiiyukia ihaki ria</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gutuma amene mundu utari mwihia.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uria urumagirira mitugo iyo ndari hingo angienyenyeka.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria athaka ngoro magakaira mucii-ini wa Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI     JAKUBU 1:17-18, 21b-22,27</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guthoma Marua ma Muthure Jakubu:</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariu a Ithe Witu, inyui nyenda muno, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uheani o wothe wa maundu mega, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kiheo o giothe kiria kiagiriire kuna, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni ciumaga iguru, igaikuruka ciumite kuri ithe witu, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwene mootheri ma iguru, uria utagariukaga, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndari na kiiruru gia kugaruruka. </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niwe watuciarire na mugambo wa ma, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuringana na uria eyendeire we mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha tutuike ta muturio wa indo ira ombire.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nyitai na uhoreri mugambo uria uhanditwo thiini wanyu, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o uria ungohota kuhonokia mioyo yanyu. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Indi tuikai andu a gwikaga uhoro uria muiguite, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mutigatuike o a kuiiguaga mutekuwika, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mukiihenagia inyui ene.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Undini uria wonagwo ni Ngai, o we Ithe Witu, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wi mutheru, na utari muthuku niguo uyu atiri, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni guthiaga kurora ciana cia ngoriai na </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atumia a ndigwa hindi iria mathinikite, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ningi ati mundu eikaragie guku thi </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ateguthukio ni imeni iria njuru ciakuo.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RWIMBO RWA ALLELUYA     THABURI 27:11</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nyonagiriria njira yaku,</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani, ndwaraga o na uthiiro mwaraganu.</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI    MARIKO 7:1-8,14-15,21-23</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guthoma Injiri ya Muthure Mariko:</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io, Afarisai na aandiki-marua amwe </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni marurunganire kuri Yesu, moimite Jerusalem, </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na makiona ati arutwo ake amwe </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maariaga irio ciao na moko mathuku, </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>niguo matari mathambie. </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amu Afarisai, o na Ayahudi othe, </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matingiria irio mataambite gwithamba moko o wega,</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni kuigua kirira kia athuri: </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na moima king'ang'a-ini, matingiria mataambite gwithamba: </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na kwi maundu mangi maingi marutite tene-ini mekage, </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ma thambia ma ikombe na tunyungu </s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na nyungu cia muthemba wa gicango.</s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao Afarisai acio na aandiki-marua makimuria atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arutwo aku matiganite na kirira gia athuri niki, </s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makariaga irio ciao na moko mathuku? </s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akimera atiri: Isaia ni aarathire uhoro wanyu wega ma, hinga ici, </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ta haria haandikitwo atiri: Andu aya mandiaga na miromo, </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no ngoro ciao ii kuraya na nii. No kai maturagia ma andu. </s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mutiganaga na riathani ria Ngai,</s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mukagwatagirira kirira kia andu.</s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agicoka agiita kirindi githengerere hari we, agikiira atiriri: </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thikiririai inyuothe, na muigue: </s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gutiri kindu gitari thiini wa mundu,</s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kingihota kumugwatia thahu gigitonya thiini wake: </s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maundu maria moimaga thiini wa mundu nimo magwatagia thahu. </s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni gukoruo ni thiini, ni ngoro-ini cia andu, </s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuumaga meciria moru, umaraya, na uici, </s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na uuragani, na utharia, na ucumikiri, na waganu, </s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na uhenania, na uura-thoni, na ruitho, na urumani, </s></f>"},{ID:109,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mwitio, na urimu: </s></f>"},{ID:110,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mauuru macio mothe moimaga na thiini,</s></f>"},{ID:111,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makagwatia mundu thahu.</s></f>"},{ID:112,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA IGIRI MWAKA B"},{Guid:"5l0b4u4DZ0qb+UV/DBPLBQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA MBERE   JOSHUA 24:1-2, 15-17, 18b</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guthoma kuuma ibuku ria Joshua</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mithenya-ini iyo, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Joshua agishokaniriria mihiriga yothe ya Israeli kuu Shikem,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agigiita athuri a Israeli, o na anene ao, o na aciiri ao, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na anyabara ao; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao magigithii makirugama hau mbere ya Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Joshua agikiira andu acio atirii:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na riu mungikoruo ni mukuona ari uuru</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gutungatira Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thurai umuthi uria muritungatagira; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mumenye kana ni ngai iria maithe manyu maatungatagira </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>murimo ucio wa rui rwa farati, kana ni ngai cia aamori, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aria mutuuranitie na bururi wao; no riri, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ha uhoro wakwa nii mwene, na nyumba yakwa-ri,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>turitungatagira Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao andu acio magicoka makiuga atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Turoaga gukanatigana na Mwathani ati </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>niguo tutungatiri ngai ingi; </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni gukoruo Mwathani Ngai witu niwe waturutire </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>bururi wa Misri ithui ene, o na maithe maitu, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tuume nyumba ya ukombo, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na akiringa ciama icio nene tugiciyonagira na maitho maitu, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na agitumenyerera njira-ini iria yothe twagerire, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na agitumenyerera twi thiini wa andu othe </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aria twatuikaniirie kwao; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondu ucio o na ithui turitungatagira Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni undu niwe Ngai witu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO     THABURI 34:1-2, 15-16, 17-18, 19-20, 21-22</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ndirigathaga Mwathani o hingo ciothe;</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kanua gakwa kumukumia gatiri hindi gatarimukumagia</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nowe ngoro yakwa iriirahagira:</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria ahoreri mariiguaga uguo magakena.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maitho ma Mwathani merekeire na kuri aria athingu,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na matu make magategeruo kiriro kiao.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria mekaga uuru-ri,
 
uthiu wa Mwathani ni kumomira umomiire,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ati ang'urie ritwa riao ritikaririkanwo guku thii.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria athingu maakaire, nake Mwathani akiigua,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akimateithura minyamaro-ini yao yothe.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ni akoragwo hakuhi na aria athuthiku ngoro;</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> 
Acio maherete muoyoini ri, agakimahonokia.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mauuru no maingi makoraga uria muthingu,</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>indi, Mwathani niamuteithoraga hari mo mothe.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kumenyerera ni amenyagirira mahindi make mothe;</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gutiri ona rimwe ringiunika.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria aaganu-ri, uuru ni kuuraga ukamoraga;</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Andu aria mathuuraga ucio</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>muthingu ni magatuwo ehia.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ni gukuura akuuraga ngoro cia ndungata ciake;</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aria marahagira hari we gutiri ungituo mwihia.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI      AEFESO 5:21-32</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guthoma Marua ma Muthure Paul kuri andu Aefeso</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariu a ithe witu,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mukiinyihanagirie o mundu na uria ungi ni </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>undu wa uria mwitigirite Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Inyui atumia, athikagirai athuri anyu inyui ene, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ta uria mungiathikagira Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tundu mundu murume niwe mutwe wa mutumia, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ota uria Kristu nake ari we mutwe wa Kanitha, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiri o we muhonokia wa mwiri ucio. </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na riri, o ta uria Kanitha wathikagira Kristu, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o oguo noguo kwagiriire ati atumia nao maathikagire</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>athuuri ao maundu-ini mothe.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Inyui athuri-ri, endagai atumia anyu o ta uria </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristu nake endire Kanitha,</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiaya kwineana ni undu waguo; ni getha awamure autherie, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kuuthambia, guthambia kuria kwa maai hamwe na uhoro, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni getha ahote kwirehere Kanitha wa riri, </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utari na kimeni, kana handu hagutharu, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana undu o na umwe ta ucio; no utuike mutheru utari giko. </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O uguo noguo athuri nao magiriirwo</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni kwendaga atumia ao ene o tari o miiri yao ene. </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mundu uria wendaga mutumia wake niwe wendaga: </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni undu gutiri kwonwo mundu uthuire mwiri wake mwene; </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni nikuuhe auheaga irio na akauikaragia wega, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ta uria Kristu nake ekaga Kanitha: ni undu turi ciiga cia mwiri wake. </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondu ucio-ri, mundu ni atigane na ithe wa nyina, </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agwatanio na mutumia; nao eri matuike mwiri umwe. </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ucio ni uhoro wa hitho, wi bata o ma; no ngiuga uguo-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni uhoro wa Kristu na Kanitha ndiragweta.</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RWIMBO RWA ALLELUYA     JOHANA 6:63,68</s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Migambo yaku, Mwathani, iri muoyo na utuuro; </s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee wi na ndeto cia muoyo wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI     JOHANA 6: 60-69</s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guthoma Injiri ya Muthure Johana</s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io, arutwo ake aingi maaigua ndeto icio, </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magikiuga atiri: Uhoro ucio wi hinya; nu ungihota kuuigua? </s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu, tondu ni oi na ngoro ati arutwo ake </s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni marateta ni undu waguo, </s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akimera: Githi uhoro ucio ugutuma muhingwo? </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>I, mungikiona Muru wa Mundu akiambata kuria aari mbere? </s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muoyo-ri, niguo wikanagira muoyo; Mwiri nduri uguni; </s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndeto icio ndamuhe nicio muoyo na nicio utuuro. </s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No riri, inyui kuri amwe mategwitikia. Amu gwata kiambiriria, </s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu ni aamenyaga aria matetikitie, </s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na uria ukamukunyanira anyitwo.</s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agicoka akiuga atiri; nikio ndimwirire, ati; </s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gutiri mundu ungihota guuka kuri nii atari mwendithie ni Ithe Witu. </s></f>"},{ID:109,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maaigua uhoro ucio, arutwo ake aingi makihunduka, </s></f>"},{ID:110,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magitiga gucoka guthii nake. </s></f>"},{ID:111,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondu ucio Yesu akiuria aria ikumi na eri atiriri; </s></f>"},{ID:112,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni mukwenda guthii ona inyui? </s></f>"},{ID:113,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Simone Petero akimucokeria atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:114,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani, tugithii kuri u? </s></f>"},{ID:115,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee wina ndeto cia muoyo wa tene na tene. </s></f>"},{ID:116,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na ithui ni twitikitie, tukamenya niwe Mutheru wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:117,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA IMWE MWAKA B"},{Guid:"Yvmc1RxF6UGo5I7FHM8tyg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA    
YOSHUA 24:1-2a, 15-17,18b</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Yoshua aliwakusanya na kuwakutanisha </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makabila yote ya Israeli huko Shekemu. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawaita wazee wa Israeli, wakuu wao, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na waamuzi na wasimamizi na wakajipanga mbele ya Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yoshua akawaambia watu wote, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kama hampendezwi na kumtumikia Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>basi, chagueni hivi leo mtamtumikia nani:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama ni miungu ile walioitumikia</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> mababu zenu huko ng'ambo ya mto: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>au kama ni miungu ya waamori amabao nchi yao mnaikalia. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini mimi na nyumba yangu tutamtumikia Bwana.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu wale wakamjibu wakisema,\"La hasha, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iwe mbali nasi kwamba tutamwacha</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana na kuitumikia miungu miingine! </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana Bwana Mungu wetu, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeye ndie aliyetuokoa sisi na mababu zetu kutoka nchi ya Misri, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na katika nyumba hio ya utumwa; </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye ndiye aliyezifanya ishara zile kubwa</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbele ya macho yetu na kutulinda katika njia ile yote tulioyasafiria, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kati ya mataifa yote tuliyopita katikati yao. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo, nasi pia tunataka kumtumikia </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana, kwa maana yeye ndiye Mungu wetu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA    ZABURI 34:2-3, 16-17, 18-19, 20-21, 22-23</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni mwone jinsi alivyo mwema</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitamtukuza Bwana kila wakati
sifa zake zi kinywani mwangu daima.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nafsi yangu itajisifu katika Bwana
wanyonge wasikie na wafurahi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni mwone jinsi bwana alivyo mwema</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Macho ya Bwana yawaangalia wenye haki</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na masikio yake hukielekea kilio chao</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uso wa Bwana ni juu ya watendao mabaya</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili afute kumbukumbu yao duniani</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni mwone jinsi bwana alivyo mwema</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wanyofu waliitwa, Bwana akisikia 
akawaopoa katika shida zao zote.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana yu karibu nao waliopondeka moyo,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huwaokoa wenye kuvunjika roho.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni mwone jinsi bwana alivyo mwema</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mateso ya mwadilifu ni mengi</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini Bwana humwopoa katika yote.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu ailinda mifupa yake yote;
hata mmoja hautavunjika.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni mwone jinsi bwana alivyo mwema</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ubaya utamuua mwovu;</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao wenye kumchukia mwadilifu watapatilizwa.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana huwakomboa watumishi wake waaminifu;</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wote waliomkimbilia mungu hawatapatilizwa kamwe.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Onjeni mwone jinsi bwana alivyo mwema</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI   WAEFESO 5:21-32</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mnyenyekeane kwa sababu ya heshima </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mlio nayo kwa Kristu.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wanawake wanyenyekeeni waume zenu kama kwa Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana mume ni kichwa cha mke, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kama Kristu alivyo kichwa cha Kanisa,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye ndiye Mwokozi wa mwili wa fumbo.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, kama kanisa linavyonyenyekea kwa Kristu, vile vile, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake wawanyenyekee waume wao katika mambo yote. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi wanaume, wapendeni wake zenu kama</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vile Kristu alivyolipenda kanisa lake,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akajitoa kwa ajili yake, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kusudi alitakase na kulisafisha kwa mwosho wa maji katika neno, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili ajipatie kanisa tukufu lisilo na ndoa, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala kunyanzi, wala chochote cha namna hio, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali liwe takatifu bila hitilafu.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivo imepasa waume kuwapenda wake zao kama miili yao. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ampendaye mke wake ajipenda mwenyewe. </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana hakuna mtu anayeuchukia mwili wake, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali huulisha na kuutunza kama Kristo na kanisa lake, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwani sisi ni viungo vya mwili wake. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kwa hiyo mume atawaacha baba na mama </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuambatana na mke wake. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao wawili watakuwa mwili mmoja.\" </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Fumbo hili ni kubwa, lakini nasema hayo juu ya Kristo na kanisa.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI   YOHANE 6:63c, 68c</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya aleluya</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maneno yako, ee Bwana, ni Roho, pia ni uzima;</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wewe una maneno ya uzima wa milele</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya  aleluya</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI    YOHANE 6:60-69</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili Takatifu kama ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Wengi wa wafuasi wake waliposikia hayo, wakasema, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"neno hili ni gumu; nani aweza kulipokea?\" </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akajua moyoni mwake ya kuwa wafuasi </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wake wanalinung'unikia neno lake, akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Je, neno hili linawakwaza? </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Itakuwaje basi, mtakapomwona Mwana wa </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtu anapaa huko alikokuwako kwanza? Ni roho, pia ni uzima. </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini wengine wenu hawasaidiki.\"</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana Yesu alijua tangu mwanzo ni nani wasiosadiki,</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tena ni nani atakaye msaliti. </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akasema,\" Kwa sababu hiyo nimewaambia ya </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwamba hakuna mtu awezaye kuja kwangu, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>isipokuwa amejaliwa na Baba yangu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya hayo, wengi wa wafuasi wakarejea nyuma, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakaacha kuandamana naye. </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akawaambia wale kumi na wawili, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Je, ninyi pia mwataka kuondoka?\"
Simoni Petro akamjibu,\" </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana, tumwendee nani? Wewe unayo maneno ya uzima wa milele. </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nasi tumesadiki na kutambua ya kuwa wewe ndiwe Mtakatifu wa Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA MOJA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"J1dYr+uXL0OOpzniBRKVnA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
1 Samueli 3:3b-10, 19</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA MBERE RIA SAMUELI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mithenya-ini io, Samueli agikorwo akomete	</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hekaru-ini ya Mwathani thi-ini yaigitwo ithanduku ria Mwathani-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani agigiita Samueli, nake agicokia atiri: nii uyu haha. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agiteng'era kwi Eli agikiuga: nii uyu haha tondu ni wanjita</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akiuga atiri; ndiitanite coka ugakome. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aagigithii agikoma. Ningi Mwathani agiitana ringi atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Samueli nake agikiarahuka, agithii kwi Eli, akiuga atiri; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nii uyu haha, tondu ni wanjita Agigicokia atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiitanite muru wakwa, coka ugakome. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riri Samueli ndakoretwo amenyete Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hindi io, kana akaguuririo uhoro wa Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi Mwathani agigiita Samueli hindi ringi ria gatatu, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake akiarahuka, agithii kwi Eli akimwira atiri; </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nii uyu haha tondu ni wanjita. Eli agikimenya ni Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wetaga mwana ucio. Tondu ucio Eli agikira Samueli atiri:</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thii ugakome na gwakinya ati niagwita uge atiri; </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aria Mwathani niundu ndugata yaku ni iraigua. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Samueli agigicoka agithii hau hake aakomaga.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani agithii akirugama agigiita </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta mahindi maria mangi uu: 
Samueli, Samueli! </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Samueli agikiuga atiri, aria tondu ndungata yaku ni iraigua. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Samueli agigikura hamwe na nake na akiaga kureka kiugo </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kimwe giake kiage kuhingio</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiugo kia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERWO
HABURI 40: 1,3a; 6-7a,7b-9</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Nii ngenagio ni gwika uria wendaga , Wee Ngai wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gweterera ndetereire Mwathani o ngiririirie nake akiihugurira </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akinjerekera, agiitikira kuigwa kiriro giakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agiikira kanua gakwa ruimbo rweru o rwa ugooci ngocage Ngai witu naruo</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Nii ngenagio ni gwika uria wendaga , Wee Ngai wakwa </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee-ri ti magongona ma mahaki akenagira; undu wikite, ni kwega unjegete matu</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mahaki ma gucinwo, na makurutwo niundu wa mehia-ri, timo wititie</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io ngikiuga atiri: Nii uyu ndiguuka</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Nii ngenagio ni gwika uria wendaga , Wee Ngai wakwa </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nii ngenagio ni gwika uria wendaga, Wee Ngai wakwa: </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ii-ni kirira giaku kiri o ngoro-ini yakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uhoro mwega o uria wa uthingu, ni ndiwaniriire ndi kiungano-ini kiria kinene, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>miromo yakwa ndiri ndamigiririria; wee Mwathani ni uui uguo </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Nii ngenagio ni gwika uria wendaga , Wee Ngai wakwa </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI
1 AKORINTHO 6; 13- 15, 17- 20</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAULU KURI AKORINTHO MARIA MA MBERE </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariu a ithe witu, mwiri-ri ti wagutuwo wa umaraya, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tiga utwike wa Mwathani, nake Mwathani aathage mwiri ucio</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na Ngai ni ariukirie Mwathani, na ithu o na ithui ni guturiukia </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agaturiukia na uhoti wake. Kai mutoi miiri yanyu ni ciiga cia Kristu? </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kuona ati atarii uguo-ri, mugukienda njoe ciiga cia Kristu </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndicitue  ciiga cia muka wa maraya? Kuroaga gutwika uguo!</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riri mundu uria wothe ugwataine na Mwathani-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ucio nimatuika muoyo umwe nake. Uragirai umaraya. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rihia ringi o riria riothe mundu ehagia,  kihumo kia rio ki na njaa ya mwiri; </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no riri, mundu wa kuhura umaraya, ni mwiri wake mwene ekwihia</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana hihi mutikumenya miiri yanyu ni hekaru ya Muoyo Mutheru </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uria woikaraga thii-ini wanyu, uria mwaheiruo ni Ngai?</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyui-ri, mwene inyui ti inyui, niundu nikuguruo mwaguriruo, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mugikirutirwo kindu ki ngoro; tondu ucio-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maundu ma miiri yanyu gucithagiai Ngai namo</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kiugo kia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RWA ALLELUYA
1 Samueli 3,9: Johana 6;68</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. 
Aria mwathani, niundu ndungata yaku ni iraigua. </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee wi na ndeto cia tene na tene, Alleluya </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KA INJIRI
Johana 1; 35- 42</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE JOHANA</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muthenya uyu ungi Johana agikoruo arungii, me na arutwo ake eri</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agicuthiriria Yesu agicera, akiuga; Onei gaturume ka Ngai!</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na arutwo acio eri nimaiguire uguo aaria, makimurumirira Yesu</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akihuguka, akimona mamuumite thutha, akimoria: Ni atia mukwenda?</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao makimwira atiri: Rabbi(uguo naguo watauruo ni ta kuuga; mwonania) uraraga kuu?</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akimera: ukai ni mukuona. Magigithii makiona kuria araraga.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na magiikara nake muthenya ucio: kwari ta thaa ikumi.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andu acio eri maiguire Johana aaria na makimurumirira, umwe in Andera </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>muru wa nyia na Simone Petro. 
Wee akiamba gukora muru wa nyina Simone, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akimwira atiri: Turi kuona Messia (nario riu riatauruo, ni atiri: Kristu).</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akimutwara kwi Yesu. Nake Yesu akimuroora, akiuga atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee tiwe Simone, muru wa Jona? Ugutuo Cefa(riu nario riatauruo ni Petro: noguo ihiga)</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ijniri Theru ya Mwathani</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IGIRI KIA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"GbuiUaGdO0WjhKDrYP9jsw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>SOMO LA KWANZA     KUMBUKUMBU LA TORATI 4:1-2,6-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Somo katika kitabu cha Kumbukumbu la Torati</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Musa aliwaambia watu, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>\"Sasa Israeli, sikilizeni sheria na amri</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ninazowafundisha leo hivi ili mshike kwa matendo,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kusudi mpate kuishi na kuingia na kuitwa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nchi ile ambayo Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mungu wa baba zenu amewapa. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Msiongeze neno kwa hayo ninayowaagiza, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wala msipunguze kitu. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Bali, mzishike amri za Bwana Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wenu kwa jinsi ile ninayowafundisha.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Zishikeni na kuzitimiza kwa matendo, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ndio hekima yenu na uelewa wenu </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>machoni pa mataifa. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Watakapo jua sheria hizi zote, watasema, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>'Hakuna taifa jingine lenye hekima na </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>utaratibu vile kama taifa hili kuu.'</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Basi taifa jingine lipi lililo kubwa vile hata </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>miungu yake inalikaribia kama </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Bwana Mungu wetu anavyotukaribia sisi, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kila tumwombapo? </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Taifa kubwa lipi lililo na sheria na </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>amri zake zina haki kama sheria hii </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>yote ninayoiweka leo mbele yenu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Neno la Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA     ZABURI 15:2-3a, 3bc-4ab, 5</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ni mtu aendaye kwa ukamilifu,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Atendaye kilicho haki,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na asemaye ukweli kutoka moyoni;</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hasingizii kwa ulimi wake.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hamtendei mwenzake uovu,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wala hamsengenyi jirani yake;</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Machoni pake fisadi hudharauliwa,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Bali huwaheshimu wamchao Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hakopeshi fedha yake kwa riba,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wala hapokei rushwa dhidi ya mtu asiye na hatia.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Anayefanya hayo, hatatikisika milele.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>SOMO LA PILI        YAKOBO 1:17-18, 21b-22, 27</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Yakobo</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ndugu wapendwa:</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kila kipaji chema na kila kipawa kamili </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hushuka kutoka juu kwa Baba wa Mwanga, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>lakini kwake yeye mwenyewe hakuna </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ugeuzi wala kivuli cha ubadilifu. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kwa hiari yake ametuzaa kwa neno la ukweli, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>tupate kuwa kama limbuko la viumbe vyake.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Lipokeeni kwa upole neno lililopandwa ndani yenu,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ndilo neno liwezalo kuokoa roho zenu. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Muwe watendaji wa neno, si wasikiaji tu; </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kama sivyo, mnajidanganya wenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Dini safi isiyo na hitilafu kwa Mungu Baba, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ndiyo kuwatunza yatima na wajane katika shida zao, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na kujiepusha na madoa ya ulimwengu huu.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Neno la Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>SHANGILIO LA INJILI    YAKOBO 1:18</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aleluya Aleluya</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kwa hiari yake Baba ametuzaa </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kwa neno la ukweli,</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>tupate kuwa kama limbuko la viumbe vyake.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>INJILI     MARKO 7:1-8, 14-15, 21-23</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Somo la Injili Takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Wakati ule: </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mafarisayo na baadhi ya waandishi waliokuwa</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wamefika kutoka Yerusalemu walikusanyika kwake Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Waliona kwamba baadhi ya wafuasi wake </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>walikuwa wanakula mikate na mikono najisi, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>yaani pasipo kutawadha. </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>(Kwa maana Mafarisayo na Wayahudi wote </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>walishika sana desturi ya wazee wao wala </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>hawakula kitu kabla ya kunawa mikono. </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tena wakitoka sokoni, </s></f>"},{ID:78,
