itheru niï ndï ndungata yaku, ndï o ndungata yaku,</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> mwana 
wa ngombo yaku ya mundu-wa-nja;wee-rï, nï unjohorete 
muhïndo.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA : Nï nguoya gïkombe Kïrïa kïa uhonokio, 
