 </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>3 No ngurutïre magongona ma gucokia ngatho, 
ngïthathaiye rïïtwa rïa Mwathani. Ngukïhingïria</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mwathani mïhhïtwaï ïrïa ndehïtire, kuhingia ndïmïhingie 
andu ake othe marï ho.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA : Nï nguoya gïkombe Kïrïa kïa uhonokio, 
