 </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GÏTHOMO KÏA IGÏRÏ 
Ahibirania: 9: 11-15</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KURÏ 
AHIBIRANIA :</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ariu a Ithe witu, ïndï rïrïa Kristu okire, arï muruti igongona cia </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>maundu maria mega makiriï guuka-rï, nï aahungurire hema ïrïa 
nene na njagïrïru makïria,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> o ïrïa ïtarï thondeke na moko, uguo nï 
ta kuuga ndïumbïtwo mïumbïre ya thï ïno.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Agïgïtonya handu 
harïa hatheru ihinda o rïmwe rïa kuigana,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> atakuuïte thakame ya 
mburi na ya njau, no akuuïte thakame yake mwene; </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agïgïkoruo 
akuurïte andu uguo na ukuuri urïa utagathira.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Tondu 
kungïkoruo atï thakame cia mburi na cia ndegwa,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> o na muhu wa 
mori icinïtwo, ciaminjaminjïrio andu arïa me na thahu,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> nï ïhotaga kumatheria, mïïrï yao ïthahuke-rï githï thakame ya Kristu, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o we werutïire Ngai, atarï na kauugu, na undu wa Muoyo urïa 
utuuraga tene na tene-rï, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ndïngïkïria muno kumutheria thamiri 
cianyu nïguo mutigane na ciïko iria irehage gïkuu,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> na mutungatagïre Ngai urïa wï muoyo? Na tondu ucio nïwe muiguithania </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>wa kïrïkanïro kïngï kïeru, nïgetha arïa metïtwo makagaïruo igai 
rïtagathira, o rïrïa merïiruo, kuona atï nï harï na gïkuũ gïkuĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>kïrïa kïmakũũrïte mahïtia-inï marïa maahïtirie hingo ya 
kïrïkanïro kïrïa kïa mbere.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Kiugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>1. Sion kumia Muhonokia Muthamaki na Murïithi na thaburi 
na nyïmbo.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>2. Mukumie ta urïa wahota Nïakïrïte ukumio wothe, 
Ndungïmukumia kuigana.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>3. Umuthï nï tuinïre muno, Mugate urï muoyo, Na urï na ugima.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>4. Urïa kõuna Yesu aheire Atume ikumi na erï Irio-inï cia muthia.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>5. ukumio muhingu uiguo, Wa okeni na Wï riri, ucanjamure 
ngoro.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>6. Amu umuthï gwï thigukuu nene, Ya kuririkana, Ekaristi 
ya mbere, Irio-inï cia muthia.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>7. Metha-inï ya Muthamaki mweru, Paska njeru ya watho mweru, 
Yanina Paska ya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>8. Undu mweru weheria mukuru, Kïrïa kïa ma, kïeheria muhianano, Utheri weheria nduma.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>9. Urïa Kristu ekire tene, Agïtwatha twïkage guo 
Tukïmuririkana.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>10. Turutïtwo nï Kanitha, Turutaga igongona. Mugate na dibai.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>11. Wïtïkia wa Akristu nï uyu, Mugate utuïkaga Mwïrï Na dibai 
Thakame.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>12. Tutekuona kana kuhutia, Nïtwïtïkie na hinya, Kïama gïkï 
kïnene.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>13. Nï tuonaga muhuanire, Wa mugate na dibai No nï Yesu 
urï ho.</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>14. Mwïrï nï irio, Thakame gïa kunyua No Kristu eho 
mugima O thïinï wa o kïmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>15. Ndangïnyiha nï kurïo Ndegaika nï kwenyuruo Amukïruo 
e mugima.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>16. Arïo nï umwe kana ngiri, Othe marïe undu umwe Na Yesu 
ndangïthira.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>17. Marïaga ega na oru, No maciaro ti undu umwe Gïkuu kana 
ugima.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>18. Gïkuu kurï oru ugima kurï ega, No wone marïa undu umwe 
No matigana atïa.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>19. O na hostia yenyuruo, Ndukae kugïa na nganja, Ririkana 
Yesu eho Kenyu-inï e mugima.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>20. Yesu ndagayukanagio, No muhuanire guo wiki, Na uhingu 
na muigana, Wa Yesu ndunyihaga.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>21. Oneni mugate wa Araika, utuïkïte irio cia agendi Kuna 
mugate wa ciana Ndukanaheo ngui.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>22. Mugate warathiruo tene, rïrïa Isaaka arutagwo igon gona, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na ndurume ya Paska ïgïthïnjwo Na manna ma weru-
inï.</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>23. Murïithi mwega, mugate wa ma, Yesu utuiguïre tha, Wee 
turïithie no tugitïre,</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Wee tuma tukona wega, Bururi wa 
Ikenero.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>24.Wee mwene uugï, na uhoti wothe, uturïithagia ithuï andu, 
utwïte kuu gwaku muciï,</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> ututue agai na aikari, A muciï wa 
Atheru. Nï gutuïke guo. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>RUIMBO RWA ALLELUYA 
John 6,51</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Alleluya, Alleluya.
 Mwathani ekuuga atïrï, \"Niï ndï mugate urï 
muoyo urïa woimire iguru;</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> mundu urïa ungïrïa mugate uyu nï 
agatuura mïndï na mïndï, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI 
Marko 14: 12-16. 22-26</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GUTHOMA ÏNJIIRI YA MUTHURE MARKO :</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Muthenya urïa wa kwambïrïria kurïa mïgate ïtarï mïïkïre ndawa 
ya kuimbia,</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> o urïa wathïnjagwo Paska, arutwo ake makïmuuria 
atïrï:</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Nïna kuukwenda tuthiï tugathondeke nïguo ukarïre Paska 
kuo? Nake akïrekia arutwo ake erï, akïmera atïrï: </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tonyai ituura, 
na nï mugutungwo kuo nï mundu kuuïte ndigithu ïï maaï: </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mumurumïrïre; nake kurïa egutonya, mwïre mwene nyumba ïo 
atïrï: Murutani ekuuga atïrï: </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nyumba yakwa ya ageni ïï ha, ïrïa 
ngurïra Paska twïna arutwo akwa? </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake we mwene nï 
ekumuonia nyumba nene ya iguru ïïkïrïtwo indo na ïkarïkia 
guthondekwo: mututhondekere Paska yo.</s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Nao arutwo acio 
makiuma, magïtonya ituura, magïkora o ta urïa aamerïte: 
magïgïthondeka Paska.</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ningï, o makïrïaga, akïoya mugate, na 
aarïkia kurathima, akïwenyuranga, akïmane, akiuga: Oyani, uyu 
nïguo mwïrï wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Agïcoka akïoya gïkombe, na aarïkia 
gucokeria Ngai ngatho, akïmane: nao othe magïkïnyuïra. Nake 
akïmera atïrï, </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>“Ino nïyo thakame yakwa ya kïrïkanïro, ïrïa 
ïitïiruo andu aingï. Ngumwïra atïrï na ma: </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ndigacoka kunyua ya 
maciaro ma muthabibu, nginya muthenya urïa ngamïnyua ïrï 
njeru uthamaki-inï wa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na maarïkia kuina ruïmbo makiumagara, magïthiï kïrïma-inï kïa Mïtamaiyu.</s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"THIGUKU YA MWIRI NA THAKAME YA KRISTU B"}],Guid:"jGalEZMASE+BtT5hoX/lIA",
Text:"MATHOMO MA MWAKA B"}